INSERT INTO `agents_of_shield` VALUES (1,1,1,'Pilot','/rPSvrM1XEUcVE3fYpYEdEA58KvV.jpg',NULL,'In the aftermath of The Avengers\' battle in New York City, the world attempts to come to grips with the presence of superheroes, gods, and aliens in their midst. Agent Coulson is resurrected under mysterious circumstances and forms an elite team of agents from S.H.I.E.L.D. to keep track of a secret organization known as The Rising Tide. Meanwhile, they must deal with other menaces, such as a man who suddenly finds himself with vast uncontrollable power.'),(2,1,2,'0-8-4','/SCEpMJvN92A8YveMUersBtPGYt.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and his S.H.I.E.L.D. agents travel to Peru to investigate an object of unknown origin, codenamed 0-8-4. But when he runs into Comandante Camilla Reyes, more than just sparks fly at 30,000 feet.'),(3,1,3,'The Asset','/7pW5MEaKH2XIiQpzZs5YvPkbNnl.jpg',NULL,'When the brilliant scientist, Dr. Franklin Hall, is kidnapped, Agent Coulson and his S.H.I.E.L.D. agents must race against the clock to locate him. Skye is their only way in – pushing the team to their limits when the entire plan turns upside-down.'),(4,1,4,'Eye Spy','/kktpW8PXp1IDGqhegN6VjeBjzWR.jpg',NULL,'Agent Coulson and the S.H.I.E.L.D. team try to track down a mysterious woman who has single-handedly committed numerous high-stakes heists. But when the woman’s identity is revealed, a troubling secret stands to ruin Coulson.'),(5,1,5,'Girl in the Flower Dress','/sDMJIpguu44lmkOijDYriy35SIg.jpg',NULL,'An elusive girl in a flower dress may hold the key to the mystery that brings Coulson and his team to Asia to rescue a young man with an unusual and dangerous power; and Skye has a secret that jeopardizes her relationship with the team right when they need her most.'),(6,1,6,'F.Z.Z.T.','/76wPCJLUem56l2kXCWgZGjjK9WB.jpg',NULL,'When mysterious floating bodies turn up, Coulson and his team must hunt down an elusive killer before they strike again, everyone at risk.'),(7,1,7,'The Hub','/dPzdZsaCpOf7D0jwdPhQ4VKAMc3.jpg',NULL,'Dangerous secrets are being kept from Coulson’s team, and he works the system to save Ward and Fitz when they are sent on a Level 8 classified mission that may end in tragedy.'),(8,1,8,'The Well','/rpEiSVzyGSOASPBp412ihmUy3jZ.jpg',NULL,'In the aftermath of the events chronicled in the film \"Thor: The Dark World\", Coulson and his team pick up the pieces - one of which threatens to destroy them.'),(9,1,9,'Repairs','/pE0BahwXnO4VFnDIqzGkwVutpoK.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and his team are haunted by a mysterious force that threatens to destroy them all, and only a secret from May\'s past can save them.'),(10,1,10,'The Bridge','/6OM6zhwbOlCzfvosuwnUVOMEVhM.jpg',NULL,'In a shocking cliffhanger episode, Coulson takes the war back to Centipede, and this time he brings in Mike Peterson for some super-soldier support. As they get closer to the truth, startling secrets are revealed and an unexpected twist threatens the team.'),(11,1,11,'The Magical Place','/qrU3hSvSgoSqhsPMezyOMgS3G9V.jpg',NULL,'S.H.I.E.L.D. organizes a full scale hunt for Coulson. Centipede tries to resurface the memories on what happened after Coulson died.'),(12,1,12,'Seeds','/kG3fG2zxL6VFyiiQA8cEELFS74N.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and May uncover startling information about Skye\'s past, while the team is swept into a storm at S.H.I.E.L.D. Academy.'),(13,1,13,'T.R.A.C.K.S.','/6WUHYcORomqYVB2X4wEyh7W3Eh0.jpg',NULL,'The team tries to confiscate an important device on a train.'),(14,1,14,'T.A.H.I.T.I.','/2as6borZDLGfPGlbN1tjuMWDfVO.jpg',NULL,'Coulson goes on the attack to save Skye--enlisting the aid of Ward\'s former S.O. John Garrett and uncovers shocking truths about his own life and S.H.I.E.L.D.'),(15,1,15,'Yes Men','/1cbprhHboBNuSo9XjQa5GevgXwt.jpg',NULL,'Lady Sif arrives on a hunting mission sent by Odin to find her arch-enemy Lorelei and bring her back to Asgard. It throws the team for a loop when they find themselves in a fight right alongside this powerful powerful Asgardian warrior woman.'),(16,1,16,'End of the Beginning','/nCPwZ6LCFBqa0q5KNxBRBU9ZvCn.jpg',NULL,'Agents Garrett (Bill Paxton) and Triplett are back to help Coulson\'s team track down S.H.I.E.L.D.\'S nefarious enemy--the Clairvoyant. But will Deathlok destroy them all to protect his master\'s identity?'),(17,1,17,'Turn, Turn, Turn','/qNa7fZSpGqKxt2TXN4DbcTNhb01.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and his team find themselves without anyone they can trust, only to discover that they are trapped with a traitor in their midst.'),(18,1,18,'Providence','/h7ocEHAdOYxX9JZznwDNwd768SV.jpg',NULL,'With Colonel Glenn Talbot now on their trail, Coulson and his team seek refuge in the last place anyone would look, where they begin to uncover S.H.I.E.L.D.\'s most dangerous secrets--secrets that could destroy them all.'),(19,1,19,'The Only Light in the Darkness','/q6dKYi7TXghZ2NFNMB9nXlbREh7.jpg',NULL,'With their WORLD turned upside down, Coulson races to save the life of his one true love as the mystery of \"The Cellist,\" which began in Marvel\'s The Avengers, is finally revealed on Marvel\'s Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D'),(20,1,20,'Nothing Personal','/8PmnWZgtau5OKyKw238WT2HRMH4.jpg',NULL,'With no one left to trust, Agent Maria Hill (Cobie Smulders) teams up with Coulson while S.H.I.E.L.D. is being destroyed.'),(21,1,21,'Ragtag','/pfBh1cYuDrRG992WBeGVzzkXUFn.jpg',NULL,'Ward\'s betrayal and Hydra\'s shocking secrets are revealed as Coulson\'s team goes undercover on a mission that leaves no one unscathed.'),(22,1,22,'Beginning of the End','/voa5ohZnf9uJqHhJPnb8RN6SxB0.jpg',NULL,'Dark secrets are revealed as Coulson and his team put everything on the line to stop Garrett and the forces of Hydra. But when the dust settles, Coulson will find that no one’s leaving this battle unscathed. And just when all hope seems lost, they’re joined by the one man who may be able to turn the tide–Nick Fury.'),(23,2,1,'Shadows','/eJZNrkgak779R7nNQq5gtPhp9B7.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and his team are now wanted fugitives with limited resources – but that\'s not stopping them from keeping the world safe from powerful and unseen threats everywhere. However, with new members they hardly know, will S.H.I.E.L.D. ever be trusted again?'),(24,2,2,'Heavy is the Head','/i6aFip25JEmTALK3SC6kQ1pYkBN.jpg',NULL,'Hunted and running out of solutions, Coulson puts his team right in the line of fire, with General Talbot, Hydra and Creel all on the attack. A mysterious Doctor harbors some dangerous secrets that could destroy one of our core team members.'),(25,2,3,'Making Friends and Influencing People','/palTIsaUYl2bD5mIkxJajAJAL5A.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and his team race against HYDRA to get to Donnie Gill – a dangerous gifted with the ability to freeze objects – while Simmons is caught in the crossfire.'),(26,2,4,'Face My Enemy','/flfsBKpKasUYn4bblmCXH8wL42Q.jpg',NULL,'While on a mission to learn more about the secrets of the mysterious writing, Coulson finds himself attacked by the only person he can trust: Agent Melinda May. The rest of the team is trapped in an explosive situation, and it\'s up to Fitz to save them.'),(27,2,5,'A Hen in the Wolf House','/mAwq8xSiOPmYDELe0c52XY4PdyH.jpg',NULL,'Coulson\'s team is up against the beautiful and deadly Bobbi Morse – Security Chief for Hydra. Skye\'s father forces Raina to reunite him with his daughter at any cost.'),(28,2,6,'A Fractured House','/up1Ybt3PKzBeG0E3i8DDfXD0tRG.jpg',NULL,'The world turns against S.H.I.E.L.D. when Hydra impersonates them to attack The United Nations, and an unexpected enemy leads the charge to bring about their downfall.'),(29,2,7,'The Writing on the Wall','/4C6MvPI0xz19GcewXvLzIpcGohZ.jpg',NULL,'The team discovers murder victims with the alien glyphs on them that Coulson\'s been etching. All of Coulson\'s secrets and lies come to a head.'),(30,2,8,'The Things We Bury','/s7OrDYK6R5HHWMvggAlQE3EoScF.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and team find themselves in an epic face-off against Hydra to uncover an ancient secret, while Ward kidnaps his brother, Senator Christian Ward, for a violent trip down memory lane.'),(31,2,9,'...Ye Who Enter Here','/indskjNWgOKTOubAzvS83E3ygxb.jpg',NULL,'SHIELD discovers the ancient city before Hydra, but uncovering the secrets may require one of Coulson’s team to make the ultimate sacrifice. Meanwhile, May and Skye race to get to Raina before Whitehall takes her.'),(32,2,10,'What They Become','/k9YZOR6h6WxZqpeFVpUSU8W8Qft.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and Whitehall\'s forces meet in an explosive confrontation that dramatically alters everyone\'s fates. Meanwhile, Skye discovers shocking secrets about her past.'),(33,2,11,'Aftershocks','/o2telKzPQh7GT4ZORIAQYWDIEHO.jpg',NULL,'Coulson\'s team must deal with the consequences of their war with Hydra as shocking revelations threaten to tear them apart, and Hydra makes a dangerous move that may involve a traitor in S.H.I.E.L.D.\'s midst.'),(34,2,12,'Who You Really Are','/pDM3YGuGv7Q8ItjAH2lYJS9NVxA.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and team come to the aid of a confused Lady Sif, who has lost her memory after fighting with a mysterious warrior whose true mission will send shockwaves through S.H.I.E.L.D. Meanwhile, Bobbi and Mack continue to hide their true mission from everyone close to them.'),(35,2,13,'One of Us','/tsMTa4PPElkIeHjaQ9kNHCH2KX2.jpg',NULL,'Cal seeks revenge on Coulson by assembling a team of Super Villains to destroy S.H.I.E.L.D. Meanwhile, May calls on renowned Dr. Andrew Garner, her charismatic ex-husband, with a crisis that threatens to tear the team apart.'),(36,2,14,'Love in the Time of Hydra','/cT8aZQuXgvBkCo5AADOecepPQeh.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and his team are still reeling from a shocking revelation that leaves the team fractured as they must decide what to do with one of their own. Meanwhile, Bobbi and Mack reveal their true allegiance to Hunter, while elsewhere, Ward and Agent 33 embark on a personal mission.'),(37,2,15,'One Door Closes','/qZRYuoffjQyWKEEkbkjX7R4RWLc.jpg',NULL,'War comes to Coulson’s doorstep in a way he never anticipated as shocking revelations are brought to light, and Skye struggles to control her new abilities but will soon make a decision that irrevocably changes her life.'),(38,2,16,'Afterlife','/AayVjfLOD6WArU7W4QeL4zII9KW.jpg',NULL,'As Robert Gonzalez makes his move, Coulson must do whatever it takes to protect the future of S.H.I.E.L.D. Meanwhile, Skye’s journey to control her powers takes a surprising turn when she meets the enigmatic Inhuman named Lincoln.'),(39,2,17,'Melinda','/gSzZN6ny97GTVwMWzYpr1r8YlFt.jpg',NULL,'The story of Melinda May’s transformation into “The Cavalry” is revealed as she finds herself at a crossroads in the war between Coulson and Gonzales. As Skye learns more about her true heritage from Lincoln, the truth about the Inhumans will send her in a new direction.'),(40,2,18,'The Frenemy of My Enemy','/Aee9QirIdV1FhvjS3qb8Y9YDdTC.jpg',NULL,'A dangerous new alliance is formed as Coulson and Hunter turn to the last person anyone would expect, Grant Ward! As the war between S.H.I.E.L.D. factions continues, Skye and Lincoln will find themselves drawn into this conflict.'),(41,2,19,'The Dirty Half Dozen','/rDg9pnfESdzclvx32uvGys7ChAh.jpg',NULL,'Gonzales and Coulson must find a way to put their differences aside and work together against Hydra, even if it means teaming up with someone they don\'t trust.'),(42,2,20,'Scars','/p9TviWcFl2dLPDBc9yL8cd3WoWx.jpg',NULL,'As tensions rise between S.H.I.E.L.D. and the Inhumans, Skye finds herself torn between the groups. Coulson reveals a secret he’s been hiding from even those closest to him.'),(43,2,21,'S.O.S. (Part One)','/4vGEZa48pqth01TuRTuToQx4yxj.jpg',NULL,'S.H.I.E.L.D. puts everything on the line to survive a war that blurs the line between friend and foe. Coulson and his team will be forced to make shocking sacrifices that will leave their relationships and their world changed forever.'),(44,2,22,'S.O.S. (Part Two)','/7TwQSk5ZjAQ0pY3IrihkKOyEOrJ.jpg',NULL,'S.H.I.E.L.D. puts everything on the line to survive a war that blurs the line between friend and foe. Coulson and his team will be forced to make shocking sacrifices that will leave their relationships and their world changed forever.'),(45,3,1,'Laws of Nature','/1P0eP5p1bwhlE83qy9IEkL8dCwy.jpg',NULL,'When Coulson and the team discover a new Inhuman, S.H.I.E.L.D. comes face to face with another organization searching for powered people. And still reeling from Simmons’ dramatic disappearance, Fitz goes to extreme lengths to try to learn how to get her back.'),(46,3,2,'Purpose in the Machine','/xAFplFckAJpNNM5xi8foc4hQBNZ.jpg',NULL,'Fitz and the team enlist the aid of an Asgardian to unlock the secrets of the ancient monolith that swallowed Simmons, and Agent May is at a crossroads in her personal and professional life.'),(47,3,3,'A Wanted (Inhu)man','/jNbTGZr1LtdVgZDIsnPfUCXLBW6.jpg',NULL,'Daisy, Mack and Coulson race to protect Lincoln as Rosalind’s team hunts down the Inhuman in their quest for powered people. Meanwhile, Hunter proves that there is no line that he will not cross to exact his revenge against Ward and Hydra.'),(48,3,4,'Devils You Know','/1N6dqmP0o8368hWGERNKyepY9Rg.jpg',NULL,'Having reluctantly agreed to share information with Rosalind and the ATCU, Coulson and the team go in search for the Inhuman who is killing off other Inhumans, and May feels that Hunter’s mission to take down Ward is getting too personal.'),(49,3,5,'4,722 Hours','/wn7kQONtnDCcQl85D4bYMjOPeYS.jpg',NULL,'After her dramatic rescue from another planet, Simmons is still reeling from her ordeal and reveals how she had to fight for her life in a harsh new world.'),(50,3,6,'Among Us Hide...','/ihMfiBtCSlqfe0gdUY3cuJgwW5P.jpg',NULL,'The stakes get even higher as Hunter and May continue to go after Ward and Hydra, and Daisy and Coulson begin to suspect that the ATCU may be keeping a big secret from S.H.I.E.L.D.'),(51,3,7,'Chaos Theory','/6Ydnnge97ilgurECKJ2uLvEHtEn.jpg',NULL,'As Daisy and the team fight to protect Inhumans, S.H.I.E.L.D. discovers the shocking truth about one of their biggest foes. Meanwhile, Fitz helps Simmons recover information that could lead them back through the portal.'),(52,3,8,'Many Head, One Tale','/8ppTWzuj3okBFrWBQFumY89vUhQ.jpg',NULL,'The S.H.I.E.L.D. team discovers dangerous truths about the ATCU, and Ward’s plans to destroy S.H.I.E.L.D. take a surprising twist.'),(53,3,9,'Closure','/uhWfOBXqj9rEP1mvKTotVn9qBPq.jpg',NULL,'Ward’s campaign for revenge brings the S.H.I.E.L.D. team to their knees, and Coulson proves he will do anything to settle the score.'),(54,3,10,'Maveth','/sDFiKs9N8riEJrj1CFwzHPyFcJA.jpg',NULL,'S.H.I.E.L.D. and Hydra go head-to-head in a battle that will change Coulson’s world forever. While Daisy and her team of Inhumans fight to keep Hydra at bay, Coulson and Fitz take the ultimate risk.'),(55,3,11,'Bouncing Back','/kYcByOG1WiEO2wvJhZic2hGudG7.jpg',NULL,'In the aftermath of his trip to Maveth, Coulson is more determined than ever to get to Gideon Malick and put an end to Hydra once and for all. Daisy and the team encounter more Inhumans who have powers like they\'ve never seen before, but will they be friends or enemies of S.H.I.E.L.D.?'),(56,3,12,'The Inside Man','/i4pHnhWmM4ypoCuTnvXsburpj97.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and General Talbot suspect Malick of having an inside man at the worldwide symposium on Inhumans and the team discover the presence of a traitor.'),(57,3,13,'Parting Shot','/rM2YhjtgdpiuY2CRHQunuvv2ruw.jpg',NULL,'Bobbi and Lance follow Gideon to Russia, and discover that he and a secret Inhuman are planning a coup. To stop them, the couple must make the ultimate sacrifice for the good of S.H.I.E.L.D.'),(58,3,14,'Watchdogs','/etpZGj19Gwh23i5zHwv8uA6QLhk.jpg',NULL,'Agent Mack and his brother step in when a radical group called the Watchdogs plan to eliminate the Inhumans; Simmons finds a powerful chemical compound.'),(59,3,15,'Spacetime','/xwNhM9XUCqamdiGlcGS2psKwBzO.jpg',NULL,'The S.H.I.E.L.D. team tries to prove that fate is not fixed after Daisy is horrified by a glimpse of the future.'),(60,3,16,'Paradise Lost','/yfqapN4fL5ntUPm6HX8ZhJ9PsqO.jpg',NULL,'S.H.I.E.L.D. hunts for information on their dangerous new enemy, and a shameful secret from Malick’s past is exposed, threatening to destroy his Hydra legacy.'),(61,3,17,'The Team','/j2TisbyaE9EJTszqdE2OSSbjrQA.jpg',NULL,'Agent Daisy Johnson must call upon the Secret Warriors for an inaugural mission that will leave no member unscathed, and S.H.I.E.L.D. learns more about Hive’s powers, forcing them to question everyone they trust.'),(62,3,18,'The Singularity','/GymiH9tWXI4ddgyswa2nN3JBKD.jpg',NULL,'The team reels from their losses as Hive continues to draw Inhumans to his side; Agents Fitz and Simmons get a lead that could stop the maniacal Inhuman forever.'),(63,3,19,'Failed Experiments','/cmkPSkX78l1BcoNhr6Z04f2pIVc.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and his team race to combat Hive’s control over the Inhumans, as their enemy’s deadly plan for the human race is revealed.'),(64,3,20,'Emancipation','/vqFiwpphngTGMQDYlsamuofs7cS.jpg',NULL,'Daisy’s prophecy ticks closer towards a major loss, as the aftermath of the events of “Marvel’s Captain America: Civil War” force S.H.I.E.L.D. to register the Inhumans. But with the stakes higher than ever and Hive growing stronger, the team is tested in ways they could never anticipate.'),(65,3,21,'Absolution','/tIZdzqLQviPhff6FezM1RKIcfXs.jpg',NULL,'Clark Gregg as Director Phil Coulson Ming-Na Wen as Agent Melinda May Brett Dalton as Grant Ward Chloe Bennet as Agent Daisy Johnson Iain De Caestecker as Agent Leo Fitz Elizabeth Henstridge as Agent Jemma Simmons Nick Blood as Agent Lance Hunter Adrianne Palicki as Agent Bobbi Morse Henry Simmons as Agent Alphonso “Mack” MacKenzie  Luke Mitchell as Lincoln Campbell. By Abimanyu'),(66,3,22,'Ascension','/tvyesxa1nV8CFBhxYhMfyeCL2l1.jpg',NULL,'It\'s a showdown a season in the making as S.H.I.E.L.D. takes on Hive. With Hive\'s master plan finally revealed, the team must spring into action. Who will live and who will die?'),(67,4,1,'The Ghost','/jZqFpmLdNplNUItksydNW00B2wd.jpg',NULL,'In the aftermath of their journey to another planet, Director Phil Coulson and the rest of the team were driven more than ever to put an end to the Hydra organization. Little did they know that they were up against the deadliest threat they’ve ever faced – an extremely powerful Inhuman, Hive, who was transported back from Maveth in the body of their worst enemy, Grant Ward. The team was able to thwart and kill Hive and take down Hydra, but they are all still mourning the death of fellow agent and Inhuman Lincoln Campbell.'),(68,4,2,'Meet the New Boss','/lxX96x4hJwOtU9CF99raMPszHJf.jpg',NULL,'Following Coulson\'s stepping down as Director, Jeffrey Mace is made the new Director of S.H.I.E.L.D. and it\'s public face. Daisy meets with Robbie at his place of work, saying she knows about his history but is surprised to find he isn\'t Inhuman like her. May\'s exposure from the specter last episode gets out of hand where Mace, revealing he\'s a super strong Inhuman, knocks her out and sends her to an undisclosed location. Mack & Fitz investigate the specter and encounter Ghost Rider. Meanwhile, the specter who infected May releases her compatriots who were in similar containers for years due to using the \"Darkhold\".'),(69,4,3,'Uprising','/iKJWzNLHS7p0sKIp2jwNhl4pPze.jpg',NULL,'Coulson, Mack and Fitz try to locate and neutralize a rogue group looking to stop Inhuman Registration worldwide; Simmons and Dr. Radcliffe have only a short time to save May before she succumbs to her illness.'),(70,4,4,'Let Me Stand Next to Your Fire','/QugHbmCLsceETZRhipojLjme1i.jpg',NULL,'As Ghost Rider’s quest for vengeance brings him into an explosive confrontation with S.H.I.E.L.D., Coulson and Mack must rely on an unlikely ally in their time of desperate need; and Daisy reunites with a familiar face to stop the Watchdogs.'),(71,4,5,'Lockup','/wMOSwONwzrxqKd7K8t62gHvXYod.jpg',NULL,'As Robbie Reyes struggles to control The Ghost Rider, S.H.I.E.L.D. infiltrates a high-security prison to unravel the secrets that haunt them all.'),(72,4,6,'The Good Samaritan','/oOxPd63MZaQ2dSIKqw0xoHIypPz.jpg',NULL,'The shocking origin story of Robbie\'s transition into Ghost Rider is revealed as the lives of Coulson and the team hang in the balance.'),(73,4,7,'Deals with Our Devils','/xsWH8UxtkpXdqFusf5sqNrgjNq2.jpg',NULL,'After losing half their team, the remaining members look for answers as time begins to run out for Ghost Rider.'),(74,4,8,'The Laws of Inferno Dynamics','/9AXiOfCn7rt7JHAjybGfcjr85fy.jpg',NULL,'S.H.I.E.L.D. and Ghost Rider find themselves unlikely allies when the lives of all of Los Angeles hang in the balance.'),(75,4,9,'Broken Promises','/wV1SEHFumP1JqA0MkCymp6oxcfP.jpg',NULL,'Though Coulson and May are growing closer, Coulson remains unaware of the dark secret May is hiding beneath the surface. Meanwhile, Aida is unrelenting in her search for the Darkhold.'),(76,4,10,'The Patriot','/3Btxu8GBP52xlfkbuVXQGf8a9d.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and Mack discover a shocking secret about Mace, which leaves all of S.H.I.E.L.D. in a dangerous position.'),(77,4,11,'Wake Up','/AbjNrMXLJZW08CMgCbb4Hh6dYX4.jpg',NULL,'May races to find the truth about what happened to her, while Aida’s next move could mean the death of them all.'),(78,4,12,'Hot Potato Soup','/gnZKKsBZICeNEGUotnjKxD79Zck.jpg',NULL,'Agents Sam and Billy Koenig are hunted down to get at the Darkhold book, and only Coulson and the team can save them before the clock ticks out.'),(79,4,13,'BOOM','/5Wpk9n2p4aNnQyluFmlwvhjEd6u.jpg',NULL,'An explosive Inhuman surfaces and the team are tasked with containing it. Elsewhere: Coulson and Mack encounter Radcliffe\'s inspiration for Aida.'),(80,4,14,'The Man Behind the Shield','/xm31pDIoYM4GliRM0iB9f7DRA7P.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and the team engage in a deadly cat-and-mouse game as they work to rescue Director Mace, who is fighting for his life.'),(81,4,15,'Self Control','/ne8HjEI78M76ss4IT9CCN0YYCKq.jpg',NULL,'Aida continues to go crazy. And with 4 LMDs in the base cans Fitz and Jemma survive?'),(82,4,16,'What If...','/4Jx8jFi2ktUN7JnK241Lfxa9hAA.jpg',NULL,'Hail the New World Order! Daisy and Simmons are the only hope to save everyone in a world controlled by Hydra.'),(83,4,17,'Identity and Change','/dezSHDhYkcELCokuJrodGiWGlOj.jpg',NULL,'As Daisy and Simmons struggle to discover an escape route to the real world, the identity of the Inhuman leader of the Resistance is revealed.'),(84,4,18,'No Regrets','/ghV30AN3fXLyoJNJA6SVw0tj5du.jpg',NULL,'The truth behind Fitz’s turn could bring down all of S.H.I.E.L.D.'),(85,4,19,'All the Madame\'s Men','/hQobjT6HTH2IWudF0VU6YrG03TS.jpg',NULL,'Daisy finds herself teamed up with an unlikely partner. Meanwhile, Aida prepares to put her ultimate end game into effect.'),(86,4,20,'Farewell, Cruel World!','/kzme3TmWPS7OqK1aFXw8fFIQZeA.jpg',NULL,'Daisy and Simmons race against the clock to get the team out of the Framework, but not everyone is ready to leave.'),(87,4,21,'The Return','/q9lYYFeTx7coNawd3YymCTie0cJ.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and the team\'s victory in the Framework is short-lived, revealing an even deadlier enemy looming against them all.'),(88,4,22,'World\'s End','/si1rzZskavyY6jSedZCtqq5AdU5.jpg',NULL,'With the surprising emergence of Ghost Rider, Coulson and the team attempt to stop Aida from ending the world.'),(89,5,1,'Orientation, Part One','/h7D0iGgcZXDqOmzYv7GJt2JfBFx.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and the team find themselves stranded on a mysterious ship in outer space, and that’s just the beginning of the nightmare to come.'),(90,5,2,'Orientation, Part Two','/ck6j5jj1C6SH2is9l10p0Ni12JE.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and the team find themselves stranded on a mysterious ship in outer space, and that’s just the beginning of the nightmare to come.'),(91,5,3,'A Life Spent','/xCCJIOinkAuArDa361aZa7iHq8w.jpg',NULL,'Daisy decides she will rescue Simmons – even if it means risking everything to do it.'),(92,5,4,'A Life Earned','/6Gk8HjK9eW2Ii22ULwgCytDpzQj.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and the team discover what their captors’ true intentions are; and in space, escape is not an option.'),(93,5,5,'Rewind','/aTygSKD0IkETonRQ14IEvl250C4.jpg',NULL,'With help from Lance Hunter, nothing will stop Fitz from finding the lost team as his secret journey is revealed.'),(94,5,6,'Fun & Games','/2lk9fcC6TeWZY8rvMRjNduJtCXB.jpg',NULL,'With Daisy’s life on the line, an unexpected friend attempts to rescue her.'),(95,5,7,'Together or Not at All','/xubuyzhtX4myRiWQo7L23HObEq0.jpg',NULL,'Just as the team reunites, they become prey to an undefeated Kree warrior bent on killing them all.'),(96,5,8,'The Last Day','/xiqibJ71ol4y5szOkokqIILnZPx.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and the team discover that the most unexpected person from S.H.I.E.L.D.\'s past may hold the key to preventing Earth\'s destruction.'),(97,5,9,'Best Laid Plans','/2OeRXC93EVGdfIVSQCeLNgz6nGE.jpg',NULL,'Mack, Yo-Yo and Flint fight to keep everyone alive by starting a revolution against the Kree.'),(98,5,10,'Past Life','/a6PT1YU8NRjsszYl6Zgo7tkZBx2.jpg',NULL,'The team has one final chance to return to the timeline, but their actions may have deadly consequences.'),(99,5,11,'All the Comforts of Home','/siOkSTI24kb32GGbf1y5vSAjMGC.jpg',NULL,'Coulson and the team set out to rewrite the course of humanity\'s fate; they\'re unaware that their efforts will dramatically change one S.H.I.E.L.D. agent\'s life.'),(100,5,12,'The Real Deal','/kVfCJC68yBKnLQuDueif0ReUFoG.jpg',NULL,'Coulson finally reveals the mysterious deal he made with Ghost Rider, which will impact everyone on the S.H.I.E.L.D. team.'),(101,5,13,'Principia','/ai9kXmJonEpPHopdGXAAA44lqpD.jpg',NULL,'The team goes in search of Gravitonium in order to save the world.'),(102,5,14,'The Devil Complex','/nL0nBxllWTYicvbv6brgcOFYMkT.jpg',NULL,'As Fitz and Simmons race to find a way to seal the Rift, they are faced with one of their greatest fears manifested.'),(103,5,15,'Rise and Shine','/qHSFnkrBOKk4MO0h8Iyk1qorrG1.jpg',NULL,'Coulson uncovers General Hale\'s true agenda; it could be the end of the world if S.H.I.E.L.D. doesn\'t help her.'),(104,5,16,'Inside Voices','/dKoRC5MvQja9AESNXorEKbhTftI.jpg',NULL,'Coulson is forced to team up with surprising allies to save the world, while the S.H.I.E.L.D. team attempts to track down and rescue him.'),(105,5,17,'The Honeymoon','/9FOoE8Gnd17e44nWuNUs5EclQ3v.jpg',NULL,'While an agent’s life hangs in the balance, Fitz, Simmons and Yo-Yo attempt to neutralize a weapon that could play a role in Earth’s destruction.'),(106,5,18,'All Roads Lead…','/nwtsHAl6ZzAbsGHU8ZFzxLwHpas.jpg',NULL,'The team must find a way to stop Ruby before the prophesied chain reaction that can destroy the Earth is put into motion.'),(107,5,19,'Option Two','/nEkUod26K6PWb8XCWpxiS7YAUWn.jpg',NULL,'The team finds themselves trapped and under siege at the Lighthouse.'),(108,5,20,'The One Who Will Save Us All','/a1XMqzJmxyqrvcgntfzIF6PBPee.jpg',NULL,'A newly determined Talbot takes Coulson to meet the enemy and attempts to avert Earth\'s destruction.'),(109,5,21,'The Force of Gravity','/kBuVPnqm1RDOSNDyFNiOEquerHS.jpg',NULL,'Daisy\'s future as the destroyer of worlds could take a critical change.'),(110,5,22,'The End','/iGmakkW8rZsjYicxkwhdXdXoBHw.jpg',NULL,'Coulson\'s life or death is the challenge the team finds themselves in, as the wrong decision will cause the destruction of Earth.');
