INSERT INTO `american_horror_story` VALUES (1,1,1,'Pilot','/8ukRobobOtjYH1sRwn7iYvwbPYf.jpg',NULL,'A therapist and his family move across the country to escape their troubled past but quickly discover that their new home comes with its own horrific baggage.'),(2,1,2,'Home Invasion','/24ugyFFz3CD9g6t7jEbdXLiUmro.jpg',NULL,'Vivien and Violet get themselves caught in a dangerous situation. Meanwhile, Ben goes back to Boston to fix a mistake that he made.'),(3,1,3,'Murder House','/qYZj2000oVgQvL2qWGZbm1Z2LYX.jpg',NULL,'Vivien learns the horrific truth about the house\'s first residents and Ben\'s visitor causes him to further unravel about what really happened in the haunted house. Constance and Moira have their history revealed.'),(4,1,4,'Halloween, Pt. 1','/wEyVM1QLBAqTLGxxSQWi5wsc0FD.jpg',NULL,'The line between the living and the dead blurs on Halloween. Two of the house\'s previous residents give the Harmons decorating advice.'),(5,1,5,'Halloween, Pt. 2','/u9P51AgyvsaoKVlqDyUBC00yw65.jpg',NULL,'Tate comes face to face with his past, and Ben and Vivien are haunted by a new houseguest before Halloween night comes to an end.'),(6,1,6,'Piggy, Piggy','/2ZfgFdAnPLw264NiIpob6ODNR2L.jpg',NULL,'Constance enlists Violet\'s assistance with Tate. Ben helps a new patient confront his fears.'),(7,1,7,'Open House','/6T68vdGMpTZCghaMZMpNZytxwPc.jpg',NULL,'Moira persuades a buyer to make an offer while Constance and Larry work against her efforts.'),(8,1,8,'Rubber Man','/mzPkqJq3NANEGz7wH73VDysOjnj.jpg',NULL,'The man in the rubber suit is revealed.'),(9,1,9,'Spooky Little Girl','/uyvewdpjODNcfyYMSBQ3B9aDccP.jpg',NULL,'One of history\'s most famous murder victims pays the house a visit. Constance discovers more of Tate\'s bad behavior.'),(10,1,10,'Smoldering Children','/8iKtNib84Iy6ASU3xfElZz0V5Ae.jpg',NULL,'Violet learns about the rules of the house. The truth about Larry\'s condition is explained. Constance is interrogated by the police.'),(11,1,11,'Birth','/9f5IUfiUHQuTsyB0is1jlXXuunq.jpg',NULL,'Vivien gives birth. Tate and Violet attempt to rid the house of some of its ghosts for good.'),(12,1,12,'Afterbirth','/ywCn7yLpBpH56aDsl05S8yMnF54.jpg',NULL,'In the aftermath of family tragedy, Ben tries to take his child out of the Murder House. Meanwhile, Violet and Vivien accustom themselves to their new living arrangements, Constance raises Tate\'s child as her own and a new family buys the house.'),(13,2,1,'Welcome to Briarcliff','/3KcfZimaWyolcBt8DxpnWuehDmZ.jpg',NULL,'Terrifying evils blur the boundaries between reality and insanity at the Briarcliff Manor.'),(14,2,2,'Tricks and Treats','/rKBnKQFnqxxNa5alMyzTYvaLc7A.jpg',NULL,'An exorcist is called to Briarcliff to help save a troubled farm boy; Sister Jude\'s darkest secret is revealed.'),(15,2,3,'Nor\'easter','/lv6WuYXMUqJjUXwQwaDRhgzmUPC.jpg',NULL,'A violent storm allows a group of patients to plan a daring escape; Sister Jude is haunted by her past.'),(16,2,4,'I Am Anne Frank, Pt. 1','/cf9MPvTzmlOXYQsU0o0NjnJLfKe.jpg',NULL,'A new patient exposes Arden\'s past; Kit learns why Grace was admitted to Briarcliff.'),(17,2,5,'I Am Anne Frank, Pt. 2','/viadz8P4ASoDipnkRYDW0e1q3DP.jpg',NULL,'Sister Jude employs a renowned Nazi hunter to gather evidence against Arden; Kit makes a surprising confession; Bloody Face is unmasked.'),(18,2,6,'The Origins of Monstrosity','/bVE5WEmqQ0K5x4gF2gpVLluYAOR.jpg',NULL,'A mysterious little girl is abandoned at Briarcliff; the Monsignor makes a Faustian pact with Dr. Arden; the origin of Bloody Face is revealed.'),(19,2,7,'Dark Cousin','/lW9LmEvOco6Wiz1kYzD5sPVFiZ0.jpg',NULL,'Sister Mary Eunice is terrified to discover a dark angel at Briarcliff; Kit makes a bold move to be reunited with Grace.'),(20,2,8,'Unholy Night','/ldjL9mHJDPXHyXCiuYhOnYvYg0w.jpg',NULL,'A murderous Santa wreaks havoc on Briarcliff; Sister Jude faces off with the devil; Arden has a shocking encounter in the death chute.'),(21,2,9,'The Coat Hanger','/rpXHrb7v3NPBVtXODmbmwdJI3SO.jpg',NULL,'The Monsignor takes an unlikely convert under his wing; Lana secures a new piece of evidence that can exonerate Kit; Dr. Arden witnesses a miraculous return.'),(22,2,10,'The Name Game','/aqPKymR0geUeNJyrJ3kiundKpJP.jpg',NULL,'The Monsignor confronts the Devil. Dr. Arden’s experiments reach a shocking conclusion. Dr. Thredson facilitates a surprising reunion for Kit.'),(23,2,11,'Spilt Milk','/sHNJ80ckTANQ5fVL0bStr91akxi.jpg',NULL,'Grace tells Kit devastating news about the aliens\' experiments on Alma; Dr. Thredson receives an unexpected visitor; the Monsignor goes to extreme lengths to silence Jude.'),(24,2,12,'Continuum','/dPjE3K5jSQOkxdo9H7bx0gY25qy.jpg',NULL,'A deadly new inmate threatens Sister Jude\'s chance of release; Grace\'s obsession with the aliens turns violent.'),(25,2,13,'Madness Ends','/bYHlSbp3HMAF8jAmT90wsePDMJx.jpg',NULL,'Johnny sets out to complete his father\'s work; Lana leads the charge to finally shut down Briarcliff.'),(26,3,1,'Bitchcraft','/67RIyfKHPZxi96kpDufRFlDTVbN.jpg',NULL,'A young girl discovers she possesses a strange genetic affliction tracing back to the dark days of Salem; Fiona Goode returns to town.'),(27,3,2,'Boy Parts','/wtpfsxhFqQAbk17pvLaUpT1Hxqs.jpg',NULL,'Fiona helps Zoe and Madison deal with a horrible tragedy; Delphine LaLaurie struggles to adjust to modern life; Cordelia faces a dark decision about her family.'),(28,3,3,'The Replacements','/wKw0kdTel5qwuBKf464Iaxr4J7V.jpg',NULL,'Fiona takes on an unlikely protégé; a guilt-ridden Zoe tries to give Kyle his old life back; Madison has a fiery exchange with Joan Ramsey.'),(29,3,4,'Fearful Pranks Ensue','/rs3VgNjPrYtmAklYWnsFBmVPR4v.jpg',NULL,'Fiona\'s choices rattle a decades-long truce between the Salem witches and Marie Laveau; the Council of Witchcraft pays a surprise visit to the academy with disturbing allegations.'),(30,3,5,'Burn, Witch. Burn!','/pC5E5whPyU5N4UGTdliutSCdEFX.jpg',NULL,'Besieged by Marie Laveau\'s army, Zoe unleashes a new power; Fiona and Myrtle clash over control of the coven; Madame LaLaurie is confronted by old ghosts.'),(31,3,6,'The Axeman Cometh','/9s2ihbFkazJ8IICagmEDIMfBTnV.jpg',NULL,'Zoe, Queenie and Nan make contact with a dark spirit trapped in the academy; Cordelia\'s new power brings on a heartbreaking revelation.'),(32,3,7,'The Dead','/3k4ZSPPChsEyExEpnlMNnQDzn01.jpg',NULL,'Fiona finds purpose in a dangerous love affair; Queenie questions her place in the Coven; Cordelia makes a decision about her mother.'),(33,3,8,'The Sacred Taking','/6JzYxiQjVEhsb2hzZub1jzPBZnh.jpg',NULL,'Cordelia rallies the girls in the fight to stop Fiona; a dangerous new enemy puts Misty in the cross hairs; the rivalry between Marie Laveau and Delphine comes to a head.'),(34,3,9,'Head','/6QPoHRATOHCRmnkbI4Y1Mg145MH.jpg',NULL,'Cordelia’s attacker is revealed. Fiona looks to form an alliance with Marie Laveau. Nan learns a disturbing truth about Luke’s past.'),(35,3,10,'The Magical Delights of Stevie Nicks','/323bxodJTRE3AfvMaRyecRwuyHr.jpg',NULL,'Fiona attempts to out the new supreme with a visit from Stevie Nicks; Cordelia learns the truth about Hank and the witch hunters; Madison tries to eliminate her competition for the supremacy.'),(36,3,11,'Protect the Coven','/hNgAAaTwEEE9e9N13Gfu6F1Mv9r.jpg',NULL,'Fiona and Laveau have a deadly face off with The Corporation; Cordelia makes a desperate sacrifice.'),(37,3,12,'Go to Hell','/puhw3QYUgRYqZ1SyiX9U9Vqbgyn.jpg',NULL,'Cordelia\'s latest vision puts the coven\'s future in question; the girls manifest powerful new gifts; Queenie\'s search for Marie Laveau leads her to hell and back.'),(38,3,13,'The Seven Wonders','/3TDHOFauAvIv1IDGO9njRqarMS0.jpg',NULL,'A new Supreme rises.'),(39,4,1,'Monsters Among Us','/8YThWwnZVGIilHRy2Q1fnJErokN.jpg',NULL,'One of the only surviving sideshows in the country struggles to stay in business during the dawning era of television; police make a terrifying discovery at a local farmhouse.'),(40,4,2,'Massacres and Matinees','/2LeplBcsALBpvTYyZhXphLSg2gK.jpg',N