ow. Desiree grows suspicious of Maggie.'),(49,4,11,'Magical Thinking','/iC8Va2UVW4RX0Uzs4dEanzUMNGc.jpg',NULL,'Elsa prepares for her move to Hollywood. The Twins grow enamored with a traveling salesman. Dell plots Jimmy’s escape from police custody.'),(50,4,12,'Show Stoppers','/mxbYAKo5Y129hsXluiOulpmY58I.jpg',NULL,'Dandy gives the Twins troubling information about Chester. Maggie vows to prove her loyalty to Jimmy. The Freaks enforce their harsh code of justice.'),(51,4,13,'Curtain Call','/dMSh9Ru2JSKFYrIuDPadDQN1UwJ.jpg',NULL,'The Freaks rebel against new management. Dandy prepares for his debut performance. Elsa arrives in Tinseltown.'),(52,5,1,'Checking In','/7155fYTBpgD40d9wsZnkpzUvmHg.jpg',NULL,'Detective and family man John Lowe investigates a chain of gruesome murders in Los Angeles. A mysterious tip points him to the enigmatic Hotel Cortez.'),(53,5,2,'Chutes and Ladders','/mPEGkMr1HMsLqGytZl0UQMG6qss.jpg',NULL,'Fashion mogul Will Drake brings couture to the Hotel Cortez. A model catches The Countess\'s eye. John learns about the hotel\'s sadistic first owner.'),(54,5,3,'Mommy','/1cspMmNUr5AwIVqcBfui3s5cON0.jpg',NULL,'Alex is pushed to her breaking point after Scarlett stirs up memories of Holden. Donovan is targeted by a dangerous rival of The Countess.'),(55,5,4,'Devil\'s Night','/h3Mg3TjUn33HhqJ2j8BOYPQXZKA.jpg',NULL,'John receives an invitation to attend an exclusive Devil\'s Night Soiree. Alex tries to diagnose Holden\'s strange condition.'),(56,5,5,'Room Service','/7a1g2fs8vOR5THMHHL9Pg1QsX1W.jpg',NULL,'Alex uses an unconventional treatment to save a dying patient. A Halloween-hating couple tests Iris’s limits.'),(57,5,6,'Room 33','/kYj8fTlvgS7PyQtAeB3vkIga4ew.jpg',NULL,'Ramona and Donovan enact their plan for revenge. Liz Taylor finds true love. The resident of Room 33 is revealed.'),(58,5,7,'Flicker','/jvTvsErxd6pVaEVq4inbY6cHTDZ.jpg',NULL,'Will Drake’s renovations uncover one of the Hotel’s greatest secrets. John undergoes psychiatric evaluation. The Countess learns the fate of her first love.'),(59,5,8,'The Ten Commandments Killer','/j75cyPWx1pmYsid11FiUAsOserM.jpg',NULL,'John closes in on The Ten Commandments Killer. Sally’s arrangement with March is revealed.'),(60,5,9,'She Wants Revenge','/ppih0fbnhUesTL6ycMBkcHYE99H.jpg',NULL,'The Countess is reunited with her one true love. Donovan and Ramona take another stab at revenge. A careless decision lands Alex in hot water.'),(61,5,10,'She Gets Revenge','/lsUFCJAFIW2nprghNpqoNoeLIyA.jpg',NULL,'Alex enlists John\'s help to contain an outbreak. Donovan learns the Countess\' true intentions. Liz and Iris plan to leave the hotel for good.'),(62,5,11,'Battle Royale','/uacbm3cpIdeTV6FWdBHQiXcv6Gl.jpg',NULL,'Ramona draws vitality from an unlikely source. Sally uses her past to negotiate her future. Scarlett learns the truth of her family\'s affliction.'),(63,5,12,'Be Our Guest','/5DImPlCtApJbKGfnp96Tn9skQ9F.jpg',NULL,'Iris and Liz oversee a new era at the Cortez. John and Alex struggle to adapt to life outside the hotel.'),(64,6,1,'Chapter 1','/coYQadKVYgRoAK0MhOq2iyr1BTF.jpg',NULL,'A young interracial couple move into a farmhouse in North Carolina after purchasing it with their life savings. However, unearthly phenomena begin occurring and things are not what they seem.'),(65,6,2,'Chapter 2','/i23I9r1BnDAh9AT08zH7BxB15Bk.jpg',NULL,'While the Millers discover some of their house\'s history, Lee falls into old habits and her daughter, Flora, makes a new friend.'),(66,6,3,'Chapter 3','/i3tZLifkEREKbUXMCJE3gekjZAC.jpg',NULL,'Nightmares become an inescapable reality as unique stories of people\'s lives in America reveal the astonishing power of the supernatural.'),(67,6,4,'Chapter 4','/Y5x8Rp3SXAk6JpCiaMueeooXzg.jpg',NULL,'Scathach presents herself for the first time and reveals what she wants. However, Tomasyn and the ghost settlers have other plans.'),(68,6,5,'Chapter 5','/rl3jfR1VV6uSyKZ0pxMUT6B7yE7.jpg',NULL,'The mob comes for Shelby, Matt and Flora, but they get help from a new face to escape the Butcher\'s wrath.'),(69,6,6,'Chapter 6','/2Z5qQaJzGoO5ws7ib0TzzyRWTDs.jpg',NULL,'After the wrap of the show My Roanoke Nightmare, the producer creates a follow up show called Return to Roanoke, bringing the actors of the previous show and the real Shelby, Matt, and Lee, back to the house.'),(70,6,7,'Chapter 7','/qVO1V0ZEFYMwWgzaM8C8hvEAe5j.jpg',NULL,'Audrey, Lee, and Monet find themselves in grave danger as they search for Rory; Agnes comes back for revenge; Matt and Shelby deal with the ramifications of their situation.'),(71,6,8,'Chapter 8','/9JN15dfe6VDHYaSDnwmJ4J3eNCo.jpg',NULL,'Audrey, Monet, and Lee remain hostages of the Polks, while Shelby and Dominic try to think of a way to escape the wrath of The Butcher back at the house.'),(72,6,9,'Chapter 9','/mI1HUrCERaj6pkNVrKwSwuLwHRn.jpg',NULL,'A new actor shows up to the house per Sidney\'s request; three young adults enter the woods to shoot footage of the blood moon and the history of the house for the web. Meanwhile Lee, Monet, and Audrey remain on the run.'),(73,6,10,'Chapter 10','/yt20DnQEQdLvSL8x46KxQ5JN9Id.jpg',NULL,'Lee Harris, the lone survivor of Return to Roanoke: Three Days in Hell, agrees to an interview live on television, the Lana Winters Special.'),(74,7,1,'Election Night','/60MOcspNqCGXeqrt7VINftwYtDm.jpg',NULL,'After Trump is elected President, Ally Mayfair-Richards is beset by all of her old phobias... and they appear to be coming to life.'),(75,7,2,'Don\'t Be Afraid of the Dark','/8eNfm1AyjFpFClFLRclDmnjv24T.jpg',NULL,'Ally, Ivy and Oz meet the new neighbors. Kai runs for city council. Detective Samuels investigates a murder. A blackout terrorizes Ally.'),(76,7,3,'Neighbors from Hell','/6AgjhdihfefZjQQeRe0CPpcO4qP.jpg',NULL,'The community turns on Ally after she shoots and kills a Hispanic man. At home tensions between Ally and Ivy grow worse, and Kai may be Ally\'s only hope.'),(77,7,4,'11/9','/oAHH3GUm2jeRwTZ7CrQ8b30WyEN.jpg',NULL,'Kai gathers familiar faces to join his cult as the events surrounding 11/8/17 are explored.'),(78,7,5,'Holes','/wQqgOSFnvzo7cn5uDscSYB6t4js.jpg',NULL,'Kai asks for the cult members to prove their loyalty against one of their own. Meanwhile, Ally meets with Rudy to tell him about her problems dealing with Ivy\'s departure.'),(79,7,6,'Mid-Western Assassin','/dxzSTxe1jljaXLRK9QlZZb9LbWU.jpg',NULL,'Ally takes Meadow to Rudy in the hopes that she will confirm her story about the cult. However, Meadow has a change of heart. Meanwhile, an unexpected opponent runs against Kai in the city council election.'),(80,7,7,'Valerie Solanas Died for Your Sins: Scumbag','/5KQq2XUaG2jzmaxMVKmqBBtoOPQ.jpg',NULL,''),(81,7,8,'Winter of Our Discontent','/qTEwBNs5Y6bwt8Dxfiv8Q2vMF3o.jpg',NULL,'Ally confronts Kai meanwhile Winter must choose between Kai and Beverly when he makes a questionable decision.'),(82,7,9,'Drink the Kool-Aid','/oUwMMTCNZCUI5OwlbD4cxODv2d0.jpg',NULL,'Kai seeks to test the loyalty of his cult. Ally seeks revenge. Oz learns about his parentage.'),(83,7,10,'Charles (Manson) in Charge','/la4PoRvC3JYdZQvk3IQBhUaJNm8.jpg',NULL,'Kai receives visits from Charles Manson as he begins to question everyone around him.'),(84,7,11,'Great Again','/dKg3dmQO90O9Iyxi9u3cKKKm9FP.jpg',NULL,'Kai sets his master plan into motion as Ally\'s true intentions are revealed.'),(85,8,1,'The End','/9iF5k6AvKfnK4JAcz5Tjxy6labY.jpg',NULL,'The end of the world happens when the bombs drop, and the survivors wonder if surviving is worth it after the Cooperative gives them shelter.'),(86,8,2,'The Morning After','/zZ0Tp8uEp923Lwf0dWgymqPJNsV.jpg',NULL,''),(87,8,3,'Forbidden Fruit','/zVGGEnjhHVWuefHUFwcF452nkAn.jpg',NULL,''),(88,8,4,'Could It Be... Satan?','/omteWisCkikQeGEHS3s9B3WHV7T.jpg',NULL,''),(89,8,5,'Episode 5',NULL,NULL,'');
