INSERT INTO `better_call_saul` VALUES (1,1,1,'Uno','/kXPlwZm3RefxpSU5E3Mu4Yyvn40.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy works his magic in the courtroom. Unexpected inspiration leads him to an unconventional pursuit of potential clients.'),(2,1,2,'Mijo','/8XFhyx4xFCY2nZPThgOUF42G4fI.jpg',NULL,'As his troubles escalate to a boiling point, Jimmy finds himself in dire straits. An act of carelessness puts Chuck at risk.'),(3,1,3,'Nacho','/xF1LKhLd0xAcddb9HrgAJ2W6gav.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy pulls out all the stops to prove that his dangerous client is innocent, even though it causes some friction with Kim.'),(4,1,4,'Hero','/rXNmF84z0YOpuO7Uqm38ii3Taxe.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy devises a bold plan to obtain new clients, but must face consequences when his relationships become strained.'),(5,1,5,'Alpine Shepherd Boy','/iDW7BZtI7M1xIzL4vGG637EzbPT.jpg',NULL,'Alarming news disrupts Jimmy\'s efforts at drumming up new business, forcing him to make a difficult choice.'),(6,1,6,'Five-O','/1hapaqrgQsbvFqgCLSTjVQlvHdZ.jpg',NULL,'Mike\'s tragic past comes back to haunt him, and he\'s forced to seek help from an unusual source. Jimmy\'s moral compass is put to the test.'),(7,1,7,'Bingo','/hyGwjiq1Snmabd7IfHzGXOIwug9.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy meets with potential new clients. Then, when given the opportunity to do the right thing, he cashes in a favor from an unlikely ally.'),(8,1,8,'RICO','/iZtSa0MDIiowvV2mDPMi04aGZip.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy shows Chuck that he\'s willing to do almost anything to win a case, even if it means getting his hands dirty.'),(9,1,9,'Pimento','/yR7wVgQ7aqUfiYgmRdKhH9EEXat.jpg',NULL,'Chuck urges Jimmy to accept a harsh truth. Meanwhile, a deal threatens to go off the rails when Mike\'s ability to complete a job is called into question.'),(10,1,10,'Marco','/bZzkmEYEu88QoSzz0Mgz5YYd7n3.jpg',NULL,'In the aftermath of recent events, Jimmy seizes an opportunity to reconnect with an old friend. Chuck adjusts to a new way of life.'),(11,2,1,'Switch','/zT2i7XBvXCnyCnBSEOf2EbGEsuN.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy and Kim\'s relationship takes a new turn. Mike decides it\'s for the best to sever his affiliation with an unrestrained associate.'),(12,2,2,'Cobbler','/9SXC0BMRAt5OHWZFqXESkOGLRhO.jpg',NULL,'To keep a potentially messy situation from unraveling, Mike brokers a deal. Jimmy works to exonerate an eccentric client.'),(13,2,3,'Amarillo','/o3euy8qB8AErKQcVHRrGWV1Xtiq.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy\'s client outreach efforts thrive, and he exhibits new heights of showmanship. Mike is perplexed by daughter-in-law Stacey\'s troubling news.'),(14,2,4,'Gloves Off','/rtVuaHImiLxvnffNASJbF4Q3F89.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy\'s actions unexpectedly create waves for Kim. Mike cautiously weighs a lucrative proposal that might bring about dire consequences.'),(15,2,5,'Rebecca','/lGyroPKe9IexyGMUotJW7LRiBsh.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy becomes frustrated with his restrictive work environment. Kim pulls out all the stops to dig herself out of a seemingly bottomless hole at HHM.'),(16,2,6,'Bali Ha\'i','/iKvrkFvAFPW4C8JV498UqV4YcLT.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy finds comfort in familiarity. Kim receives a life-changing proposal. When he is threatened, Mike finds himself pushed to the limit.'),(17,2,7,'Inflatable','/1RumrNbk6ZAGB5U1YqQR6h96u77.jpg',NULL,'Mike\'s growing frustration shows when his hand is forced, but with Jimmy\'s help, he works to keep the peace. Meanwhile, Jimmy boldly forges a new path forward.'),(18,2,8,'Fifi','/43SruAr8U7y2qteRb9OaSTesQzy.jpg',NULL,'Mike aims to settle the score with an enemy; an unexpected opportunity presents itself to Jimmy.'),(19,2,9,'Nailed','/tuYPo6zuzyVHezXcq3KukGZi5uJ.jpg',NULL,'Mike takes a methodical approach to his mission. Someone questions Chuck\'s capabilities. Jimmy faces a personal dilemma.'),(20,2,10,'Klick','/zit4sAsSYOnpk5MOcceRiQf0VTj.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy must make a hard choice. Mike takes control of matters. Hamlin delivers shocking news.'),(21,3,1,'Mabel','/aG3q36NweQneIsYG74LaOYB3ubv.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy and Chuck\'s relationship deteriorates. Kim feels the pressure of running her own firm. Mike investigates the note left on his car.'),(22,3,2,'Witness','/buKhfwuOyXv5ZbZSlkWz0pR6Il5.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy and Kim hire an assistant. Mike seeks out a mysterious acquaintance. Chuck uses the law to gain an advantage over Jimmy.'),(23,3,3,'Sunk Costs','/jlAfOz1zVFrL6wYeCjT875AfOV6.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy decides to represent a new client to Kim\'s dismay. Mike meets a formidable ally who gives a tempting offer.'),(24,3,4,'Sabrosito','/pFjMOyhgP8HCwkRG34ZD8C0VTDz.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy asks a favor of Mike; new complications disrupt Salamancas\' business. Chuck and Jimmy struggle with a compromise.'),(25,3,5,'Chicanery','/fBJZXkXcHZ6Oytyn9AW8yljk45K.jpg',NULL,'Kim and Jimmy face off with an adversary. Jimmy looks to Chuck\'s past to secure his future. Jimmy loses an ally and gains another.'),(26,3,6,'Off Brand','/lAEikpCAspgsGAaNpnbyxXHO6nj.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy has a new endeavor. Chuck pushes himself to the limit. Nacho finds himself in a power struggle.'),(27,3,7,'Expenses','/jqVsNTUU6uhgjIpxzTgOa8U1teK.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy tries to settle debts. Nacho reunites with an acquaintance. Mike helps Stacey with a project and makes a connection.'),(28,3,8,'Slip','/fksW2qNAxoe2jP9kL4y1RU3Xj7a.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy is pushed to desperate measures. Nacho picks up a new skill. Mike explores an alliance. Kim stands up to Hamlin.'),(29,3,9,'Fall','/1I5fgW7h62PsDmMGpThHJ0tSdg3.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy visits an old friend and takes up a new pastime. Chuck and Hamlin spar over the future of the firm. Kim faces challenges at work.'),(30,3,10,'Lantern','/atvS6hAaSZhROAGjYSHjVsVUT58.jpg',NULL,'Kim takes time off. Jimmy tries to make amends. Nacho gambles with his future. Hamlin pushes Chuck to make a decision.'),(31,4,1,'Smoke','/gcG57V96qWemZYCwfW7osDXl4f2.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy struggles to cope with Chuck\'s tragic death. Mike ponders his role at Madrigal. Howard makes a startling confession.'),(32,4,2,'Breathe','/lozKaJD6hNLqG7dPmxucU2d4bZ2.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy seeks new employment. Gus navigates the fallout from Hector\'s collapse. Kim endeavors to support Jimmy in the wake of Chuck\'s death.'),(33,4,3,'Something Beautiful','/bkvPvenDuk7IqBMi0dFqi3RH2Dp.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy puts a risky plan into motion. As alliances shift, Nacho finds himself in the crosshairs. Kim contemplates her future.'),(34,4,4,'Talk','/vo8wNDe1HfWIY1Pf1pPg10lchT5.jpg',NULL,'A restless Jimmy embarks on a new endeavor while Mike burns bridges. Kim pursues her bliss. Nacho tries to survive a turf war.'),(35,4,5,'Quite a Ride','/UGAuIjCv23Gov61fdhN9UC0XF8.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy identifies a new market for his talents. Mike vets a potential partnership. Kim drives a hard bargain.'),(36,4,6,'Piñata','/rxUlt3SaaVGgkGHSsll2guEGDI8.jpg',NULL,'While Jimmy dreams of Wexler-McGill, Kim makes a bold move. Mike puts a plan into motion for Gus.'),(37,4,7,'Something Stupid','/4rBmCkV4tyFr9RLgNzl2EkepSq5.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy expands his business, but runs into a problem that only Kim can solve. Gus intervenes in Hector\'s medical care. Mike deals with a setback.'),(38,4,8,'Coushatta','/prdfPctjYisErdRPE9MY5lhFaYt.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy goes to great lengths to right a wrong, as Kim pulls out all the stops for a case. Mike lets his team blow off steam. Nacho receives a visitor.'),(39,4,9,'Wiedersehen','/dsZZClwZHFqAUK6VjVIuPOwtxfS.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy and Kim unburden themselves, risking their relationship in the process. Nacho is forced to make the rounds with Lalo. Mike has cause to worry.'),(40,4,10,'Winner','/kRuY3CTfw9usFljGV7rDYRbe2aZ.jpg',NULL,'Jimmy turns the page on his reputation. Lalo tracks a loose end in Gus\' operation. Mike is forced to make a difficult decision.');
