INSERT INTO `bloodline` VALUES (1,1,1,'Part 1','/k9dcZnv7tHeGZF6LWBVdzm4B3E3.jpg',NULL,'Trouble starts when oldest son Danny Rayburn comes home for the 45th anniversary celebration of his parents\' hotel in the Florida Keys\' Islamorada.'),(2,1,2,'Part 2','/jVKLhrjFRdq8m3Vt9yJeKzRoRD4.jpg',NULL,'An accident exposes old wounds, complicating the already difficult situation between Danny and his family.'),(3,1,3,'Part 3','/rdLr7UoEiAfbrAzh9DEvCJ76Ngb.jpg',NULL,'With Robert’s condition uncertain, Danny re-considers staying in Islamorada. Meg’s personal and professional obligations become overwhelming.'),(4,1,4,'Part 4','/yN0g44bBNJhOkqO4OzQQg9xLjg7.jpg',NULL,'The family adjusts to Danny’s new role at the inn. John and Marco discover a burned boat connected to their murder case.'),(5,1,5,'Part 5','/4q5I42uGd5A57gT2LO5KIU6pOqC.jpg',NULL,'A sudden tragedy unsettles the Rayburn clan. While searching for evidence in his case, John finds something disturbing from the family’s past.'),(6,1,6,'Part 6','/iPc3M7kQC0T6r0GHKRyi2pmH0bE.jpg',NULL,'John wants to keep Danny in the fold, but Danny learns an awful truth about the past. Meg takes on a new client. Kevin\'s personal life takes a turn.'),(7,1,7,'Part 7','/h6sitdmYIka5slKCbGsMb4KsDa.jpg',NULL,'John and Marco get a lead in their investigation. Meg does her best to help Carlos. Kevin comes clean with Danny.'),(8,1,8,'Part 8','/i1IXfZsWuiFbECe5mFOnsVik1wx.jpg',NULL,'Kevin recovers at Sally\'s house after he\'s robbed. Danny makes a deal with Carlos. John and Marco identify one of the murdered girls.'),(9,1,9,'Part 9','/fl4gBPR07I7klcIBtafwUteH3DI.jpg',NULL,'The DEA gets involved in John\'s murder case. Tensions rise between Meg and Danny. John digs into Danny\'s past. Sally reminisces.'),(10,1,10,'Part 10','/bAXhcs0k0JZXVywe9PdwaDBqg44.jpg',NULL,'As Meg and Sally move forward with the wedding plans, John and Marco\'s investigation points them in Danny\'s direction.'),(11,1,11,'Part 11','/m06XO2pIzG1ygNM1kG7tM0KiEAR.jpg',NULL,'After John confronts Carlos about Danny’s illicit behavior, John, Kevin and Meg figure out a plan to save the family.'),(12,1,12,'Part 12','/33ZIy1iu3KZlIW5dOCeMdEc2RCz.jpg',NULL,'Danny’s past and present troubles became a threat to the Rayburns. Sally confronts her family.'),(13,1,13,'Part 13','/m7uMTE8EbjimiiLZkTDDoz9lpdw.jpg',NULL,'John, Kevin and Meg try to get their lives back in order as the family comes to grips with the truth about Danny.'),(14,2,1,'Part 14','/kxYllrBjXmCvNDjeSdIKQbhoZwN.jpg',NULL,'Meg learns her father kept a secret from the family for years. A voice from the past threatens John\'s plan to frame Wayne Lowry.'),(15,2,2,'Part 15','/zdQdG4UoLvjtOEtXlIpmBdToMcz.jpg',NULL,'John decides to run for sheriff. While meeting with a business prospect, Kevin finds an unexpected moneymaking opportunity. Sally learns about Nolan.'),(16,2,3,'Part 16','/obRSMEAac1xcgsujR327FDTCcOp.jpg',NULL,'Kevin\'s first transaction goes smoothly; his second is a disaster. John hunts for Eric in order to force Lowry to propose a plea deal to the police.'),(17,2,4,'Part 17','/yrRIefDHPwKMm3bN8xeGPRXSzzZ.jpg',NULL,'Kevin\'s actions loosen John\'s hold on Lowry. Sally gets a visitor from her past. John decides whether to help or hinder a bust on Lowry\'s operations.'),(18,2,5,'Part 18','/k2m3yD2fbfFSytMGkSaAYdV12D4.jpg',NULL,'Danny\'s old partner in crime in Miami is determined to make the Rayburns pay. Investor Roy Gilbert agrees to fund John\'s campaign, on one condition.'),(19,2,6,'Part 19','/YaEmoLQtAxO0Na96ET7ew1gQnB.jpg',NULL,'Eve reveals family secrets to Janey. Ozzy continues to provoke John. Meg finds a link between Aguirre\'s shady past and someone close to her.'),(20,2,7,'Part 20','/rlSz9LR6PZTUD2C7YkVji4aJuKF.jpg',NULL,'At Aguirre\'s insistence, Marco questions Kevin and Meg about the time frame following the Red Reef Inn murder. Diana comes to a horrible realization.'),(21,2,8,'Part 21','/56CE78G90PLvYepJUQiGDDSJLOA.jpg',NULL,'Kevin finds a possible solution to his financial problems. Marco checks up on Meg\'s explanation for her suspicious behavior. Sally makes Eve an offer.'),(22,2,9,'Part 22','/1jtVMpZ5fmIGVDGVlzbzrOJcvgc.jpg',NULL,'John finds evidence that refutes his alibi. Eric makes a remark that catches Marco\'s attention. Meg must decide whom to protect: Marco or her family.'),(23,2,10,'Part 23','/cc0QbXhjgNY8MZuVYDWIrS3W3AX.jpg',NULL,'Marco scrambles to get Eric immunity. Nolan recalls meeting Robert. Meg and Kevin turn against John, who pursues the one man who can alter his fate.'),(24,3,1,'Part 24','/3va0x8wtN8hKIdA9KkjcuzfJYsG.jpg',NULL,'While fleeing the Keys, John hits a roadblock. In the wake of his confessional meeting with Marco, Kevin is forced to get help from a shady character.'),(25,3,2,'Part 25','/qcx90i0dUQESIfgS5Umh1PWHl3j.jpg',NULL,'Kevin finally reaches John on his phone. Eric calls Ozzy about an opportunity. Things go wrong while Kevin and Roy\'s man set up a plausible scenario.'),(26,3,3,'Part 26','/7MhZK00R9HAbJmP6zv9GH5DPY7M.jpg',NULL,'Kevin\'s account of his injury gives Aguirre more questions than answers. Searching alone, John tries to find Eric before the police or Roy\'s men do.'),(27,3,4,'Part 27','/7SvzpFT0xI7pPY9MC0kKOconCfg.jpg',NULL,'Kevin and Belle become parents. John grows suspicious when Roy asks Kevin to sign a letter supporting Eric\'s petition to attend his mother\'s funeral.'),(28,3,5,'Part 28','/tt4thkwiHE2OhiyDno9yRB8IzNl.jpg',NULL,'While the Rayburns try to persuade the Diazes to accept a plea deal, Eric is advised to reconsider going to trial. Kevin falls in with a bad crowd.'),(29,3,6,'Part 29','/kuVoOcBmuRDUdGbEauwJP6UNaAZ.jpg',NULL,'On the day John testifies in court, he\'s visited by someone from his past. After catching John in a lie, Chelsea approaches the legal team with info.'),(30,3,7,'Part 30','/5dWEoagmlySfxUG6r5NG0kHItao.jpg',NULL,'Kevin takes the witness stand. John tracks down Meg. Sally agrees to testify against allegations that her family has a history of covering the truth.'),(31,3,8,'Part 31','/kAanbX6CXza6cq5QlXT1zirmFYO.jpg',NULL,'Kevin finds himself in over his head with the Cubans. Sally makes plans for the future of the inn. John grows wary when a retired cop buddy visits.'),(32,3,9,'Part 32','/prccEpYPNSn15yawLOzGbsXKS41.jpg',NULL,'A disoriented John finds himself in the hospital and proceeds to experience a series of surreal encounters that meld the past with the present.'),(33,3,10,'Part 33','/mjnz5apOQ2fvUPK7HiSXAZJu0DG.jpg',NULL,'Kevin learns one of the Cubans isn\'t who he claims to be. Sally gets devastating news. John faces what he must do to put the matter of Danny to rest.');
