INSERT INTO `breaking_bad` VALUES (1,1,1,'Pilot','/ydlY3iPfeOAvu8gVqrxPoMvzNCn.jpg',NULL,'When an unassuming high school chemistry teacher discovers he has a rare form of lung cancer, he decides to team up with a former student and create a top of the line crystal meth in a used RV, to provide for his family once he is gone.'),(2,1,2,'The Cat\'s in the Bag','/tjDNvbokPLtEnpFyFPyXMOd6Zr1.jpg',NULL,'Walt and Jesse attempt to tie up loose ends. The desperate situation gets more complicated with the flip of a coin. Walt\'s wife, Skyler, becomes suspicious of Walt\'s strange behavior.'),(3,1,3,'...and the Bag\'s in the River','/2kBeBlxGqBOdWlKwzAxiwkfU5on.jpg',NULL,'Walter fights with Jesse over his drug use, causing him to leave Walter alone with their captive, Krazy-8. Meanwhile, Hank has a scared straight moment with Walter Jr. after his aunt discovers he has been smoking pot. Also, Skylar is upset when Walter stays away from home.'),(4,1,4,'Cancer Man','/i5BAJVhuIWfkoSqDID6FnQNCTVc.jpg',NULL,'Walter finally tells his family that he has been stricken with cancer. Meanwhile, the DEA believes Albuquerque has a new, big time player to worry about. Meanwhile, a worthy recipient is the target of a depressed Walter\'s anger, and Jesse makes a surprise visit to his parents home.'),(5,1,5,'Gray Matter','/82G3wZgEvZLKcte6yoZJahUWBtx.jpg',NULL,'Walter and Skyler attend a former colleague\'s party. Jesse tries to free himself from the drugs, while Skyler organizes an intervention.'),(6,1,6,'Crazy Handful of Nothin\'','/hyYwqbmcHn3fuxWE3h4IhZZbkU3.jpg',NULL,'The side effects of chemo begin to plague Walt. Meanwhile, the DEA rounds up suspected dealers.'),(7,1,7,'A No-Rough-Stuff Type Deal','/1dgFAsajUpUT7DLXgAxHb9GyXHH.jpg',NULL,'Walter accepts his new identity as a drug dealer after a PTA meeting. Elsewhere, Jesse decides to put his aunt\'s house on the market and Skyler is the recipient of a baby shower.'),(8,2,1,'Seven Thirty-Seven','/7vVujNqjP23MtPqUTBNITIW3DDA.jpg',NULL,'Walt and Jesse are vividly reminded of Tuco’s volatile nature, and try to figure a way out of their business partnership. Hank attempts to mend fences between the estranged Marie and Skyler.'),(9,2,2,'Grilled','/vWcFcwMUfeBN8FZEdSSPHGQYrna.jpg',NULL,'Walt and Jesse find themselves in close quarters with an unhinged Tuco. Marie and Hank comfort Skyler, who is distraught over Walt’s disappearance. Hank pays a visit to Mrs. Pinkman on some not-so-official business.'),(10,2,3,'Bit by a Dead Bee','/p69fPkpnnxUmevhupJiDeYfQxxl.jpg',NULL,'Walt and Jesse become short on cash when they try to cover their tracks. Meanwhile, the DEA has a lead that could them straight to Walt and Jesse.'),(11,2,4,'Down','/9xi18yhtCLrrJ2plZjXgfGqeTjU.jpg',NULL,'Walt attempts to reconnect with his family, while Jesse struggles to rebuild his life.'),(12,2,5,'Breakage','/gkr2GptPkAoDavt71rJd3A4FFZ0.jpg',NULL,'Hank suffers from the aftermath of his encounter with Tuco. Meanwhile, Jesse hires a crew to get their product out on the streets.'),(13,2,6,'Peekaboo','/avu1h4hzWumE9B0nTo14Lfp4E9i.jpg',NULL,'Walt\'s secret is in jeopardy when Skyler thanks Gretchen for paying for his treatment.'),(14,2,7,'Negro Y Azul','/ng5NKNLM3mEUxHKN3Ava1PcZhSs.jpg',NULL,'Jesse and Walt discuss expanding into new territories; Hank struggles to fit in; Skyler pursues a new job opportunity; Jesse gets to know his landlord.'),(15,2,8,'Better Call Saul','/itKNfQ3Nm6Qkjdp0hew5jvqbB8p.jpg',NULL,'Walt and Jesse seek advice from a shady attorney when Badger gets in trouble with the law; the DEA believes they have caught up with \"Heisenberg\" ; Hank returns.'),(16,2,9,'4 Days Out','/j92CoMwArTeQwnGVl12SJaKlI0J.jpg',NULL,'Walt and his family wait for news after he undergoes a PET-CT scan. Walt follows Saul\'s advice; Jesse\'s relationship with Jane is put on hold when he and Walt head to the desert for a marathon of cooking.'),(17,2,10,'Over','/qJvm57aPMMEraJ62bDb79O0XXG9.jpg',NULL,'Walt and Hank get into a heated argument at a party. Skyler opens up to her boss. Jane hides her relationship with Jesse from her father.'),(18,2,11,'Mandala','/yeQAQsV4WPTmKWTyuDhF3DAna1x.jpg',NULL,'When unforeseen circumstances cause Walt and Jesse to lose some dealers, Saul suggests they add a new business partner. At work, Skylar confronts Ted about the unnerving information she had uncovered. Jane learns what Jesse does for a living when he opens up to her, which ends in disastrous results.'),(19,2,12,'Phoenix','/m2fzm9JKgaLPL2U01xROTpBXE4m.jpg',NULL,'As Walt explores money laundering options, he and Jesse spar over the profits from their latest deal. Jesse and Jane clash with her father. Walt makes a fatal decision.'),(20,2,13,'ABQ','/xdSWJjptnLAvFnh5Is6iJPlH1ds.jpg',NULL,'Skylar confronts Walt about his secrecy; Jesse falls apart; and Jane\'s grief-stricken father takes action that results in further tragedy.'),(21,3,1,'No Mas','/gOevWiZjFEeZgJBCQnWySzd6no9.jpg',NULL,'Walt faces a new threat on a new front and deals with an increasingly angry Skyler, who must consider what to do next with her life and the kids\'. Meanwhile, Jesse comes face-to-face with some startling self-revelations.'),(22,3,2,'Caballo Sin Nombre','/h3k5PoJ0RuKBH7OLnT8IbcFWz80.jpg',NULL,'Despite ever-increasing tension between Walt and Skyler, he pulls out all the stops in an effort to reconcile with the family. Elsewhere, Saul is instrumental in getting Jesse involved in a most-unusual investment opportunity.'),(23,3,3,'I.F.T.','/jH2nkMFxuX5tXc832jyDNU4AjKq.jpg',NULL,'Walt ignores Skyler\'s demands, furthering the rift between them and pushing her to break bad. Still suffering from panic and anxiety attacks, Hank crosses a line at work.'),(24,3,4,'Green Light','/1Se5PpvIgUey9MgXmrKkgO8HVye.jpg',NULL,'Walt loses control as he reacts to Skyler\'s news, endangering his job and relationships with Saul and Jesse. Hank throws himself into his blue meth investigation. Jesse enacts a new plan.'),(25,3,5,'Mas','/m2cipfAKEdLR4MIZKA3EiOcTYiZ.jpg',NULL,'Gus increases his efforts to lure Walt back into business, forcing a rift between Walt and Jesse. Skyler doubts her new relationship. Marie confides in Skyler about her concern for Hank\'s well-being.'),(26,3,6,'Sunset','/sl5zRr0u0kYcIyCdQjOTsexq4bL.jpg',NULL,'Walt settles into his new surroundings; Walt, Jr. wants answers about his parents\' relationship; Hank\'s investigation causes problems for Walt and Jesse.'),(27,3,7,'One Minute','/AoRbX7ezyWTA6kADtQlL4cyRuLd.jpg',NULL,'Hank\'s increasing volatility forces a confrontation with Jesse and trouble at work. Skyler pressures Walt to make a deal. Gus\' actions have severe consequences.'),(28,3,8,'I See You','/edBDR59bzVWdMtCawimRzOMgrlW.jpg',NULL,'The family waits for news about Hank. While Jesse covers at the lab, Walt attempts to placate Gus. After witnessing a disturbing outburst, Walt worries he and his family are in danger.'),(29,3,9,'Kafkaesque','/zfUECD3RhKQ72cXE3JZTpPW5lEL.jpg',NULL,'As Hank\'s hospital bills stack up, Skyler hatches a plan. Walt and Gus come to a better understanding. Jesse, looking for more independence, pursues a new opportunity.'),(30,3,10,'Fly','/gRLuy1Qd6RHxCTFxK2WBQwo5CGQ.jpg',NULL,'Walt becomes obsessed with a contaminant in the lab and refuses to finish the cook until it is eliminated. A frustrated Jesse attempts to get Walt back on track.'),(31,3,11,'Abiquiu','/llw7fwOmOMs6OSqwK96XrPPQZD3.jpg',NULL,'Skyler gets involved with Walt\'s business while Hank struggles with recovery. Jesse has a startling discovery after meeting a girl at group therapy.'),(32,3,12,'Half Measures','/eO3zAuQzIU6yCLrr2GUh8943jyr.jpg',NULL,'Against Walt\'s advice, Jesse lashes out . Fearing for Jesse\'s safety, Walt takes drastic action to intervene. A tragic event leads to a shocking confrontation.'),(33,3,13,'Full Measure','/mDUs18asTVVfqd56scRQ7W9r781.jpg',NULL,'With Jesse on the run and Mike in hot pursuit, Walt negotiates a bargain with Gus and concocts a disturbing plan to provide for his and Jesse\'s safety.'),(34,4,1,'Box Cutter','/2g6dLvOrLE7tpJatonCchLDkDyF.jpg',NULL,'Walt and Jesse face the deadly consequences of their actions. Skyler deals with a puzzling disappearance, as Marie struggles to help Hank with his recovery.'),(35,4,2,'Thirty-Eight Snub','/ozWpAgU14sMmjliqPtBG5gN0yJd.jpg',NULL,'Walt attempts to form a new alliance as he plans his next move. Skyler pushes Walt towards a business opportunity, in hopes of protecting the family.'),(36,4,3,'Open House','/Ac0wu93r4LaZk07wa7PiWpNOOru.jpg',NULL,'Events spiral out of control at Jesse’s place. Skyler reluctantly asks for Saul’s help. Marie returns to an old pastime and a friend asks Hank for help.'),(37,4,4,'Bullet Points','/1yxpr4hff0HpblG9ZW5DQQbImQ2.jpg',NULL,'The Cartel takes steps to gain the upper hand. Walt and Skyler share an embarrassing secret with the rest of the family. Jesse’s activities draw unwanted attention.'),(38,4,5,'Shotgun','/fG0B2tcRYR60JzmKaPUGl8RYDrq.jpg',NULL,'When Jesse goes missing, Walt fears the worst. Skyler has an unlikely reunion. Hank shares some bad news with Detective Tim Roberts.'),(39,4,6,'Cornered','/9noIu7JCbpfNrENPD3G2qeylllC.jpg',NULL,'Skyler makes an unsettling discovery. Walter, Jr. pushes his dad into a questionable purchase. Jesse offers Mike some unexpected help.'),(40,4,7,'Problem Dog','/duDEbjD1ZCs1eH74QkzJhSSwNLk.jpg',NULL,'A frustrated Walt gambles on a risky new plan.  Skyler\'s business venture hits a snag.  Hank recruits Walter, Jr. for an unusual outing.'),(41,4,8,'Hermanos','/kWtsoaPAdfPXEfqufwA44tr9bp6.jpg',NULL,'Skyler develops an unusual solution to her money troubles. Hank enlists Walt to investigate a theory. Walt’s impatience with Jesse grows.'),(42,4,9,'Bug','/bIU8FJxe1yXvMm7yREwj138Z6x8.jpg',NULL,'Skyler\'s past mistakes come back to haunt her. Gus takes action to thwart his rivals. Jesse seeks Walt\'s help, with mixed results.'),(43,4,10,'Salud','/j2B7GOepMIHz8ayuwm1xAULjlyw.jpg',NULL,'Walt\'s family worries when he doesn\'t turn up for Walter, Jr.\'s 16th birthday.  Jesse is forced to put his lab skills to the test without Mr. White\'s help.'),(44,4,11,'Crawl Space','/iFMq8Rn1jFMy5Pm5yWl2T2yuFd0.jpg',NULL,'Walt takes drastic action to protect his secret and Gus. Skyler\'s efforts to solve Ted\'s financial problems hit a wall.'),(45,4,12,'End Times','/vFdRtTqVsQBCp24B7CHue423StJ.jpg',NULL,'Hank pushes Gomez to pursue one last lead, while Walt struggles to protect the family. Jesse gets alarming news and rushes to meet with Mr. White.'),(46,4,13,'Face Off','/lR3VqqvDuP83j0F36AhreVA4soD.jpg',NULL,'Walt and Jesse team up to take on Gus. With Saul\'s help, Walt finds an unexpected ally.'),(47,5,1,'Live Free or Die','/uShB5dWoA3xIivZ9jvwWnGCVvt4.jpg',NULL,'As Walt deals with the aftermath of the Casa Tranquila explosion, Hank works to wrap up his investigation of Gus\' empire.'),(48,5,2,'Madrigal','/9WIzJqqUthdASBRE1Ts8ymrDhIv.jpg',NULL,'Walt and Jesse pursue an unlikely business partner. The DEA filters through various leads in hopes of finding something.'),(49,5,3,'Hazard Pay','/l84H1dZVkQGgFVomKHc67RKaEC2.jpg',NULL,'Walt and Jesse formulate a new business plan. Walt shares a secret with Marie.'),(50,5,4,'Fifty-One','/vH91E7z5Ma5yLOoi5xU5x6Bcos3.jpg',NULL,'Walt celebrates another birthday. Skyler contemplates her options, and an associate puts a crimp in Walt and Jesse\'s business strategy.'),(51,5,5,'Dead Freight','/plpcwk5rmet1G0mL3z3HkeKl5JX.jpg',NULL,'Walt\'s team gets creative to obtain the methylamine they need to continue their operation.'),(52,5,6,'Buyout','/vleQ03cr0fb5DBmvLY0WGxfs8wj.jpg',NULL,'Walt, Jesse, and Mike struggle over the future of their business, as occupational hazards weigh on Jesse.'),(53,5,7,'Say My Name','/2NA7ti9jsWnG4xreMEFwbq4DH1f.jpg',NULL,'Walt takes control of business matters; Mike deals with the consequences of his actions.'),(54,5,8,'Gliding Over All','/uTAPBgAah14jQbV98Sw7iqJD4W7.jpg',NULL,'Walt takes care of loose ends; Walt makes a dangerous decision.'),(55,5,9,'Blood Money','/jKohdOg1yVjXNNyxbAGX27vchIq.jpg',NULL,'As Walt and Jesse adjust to life out of the business, Hank grapples with a troubling lead.'),(56,5,10,'Buried','/b0aRvTXslQgJpCmmcmoYqS9MsIB.jpg',NULL,'While Skyler\'s past catches up with her, Walt covers his tracks. Jesse continues to struggle with his guilt.'),(57,5,11,'Confessions','/75lrTEzbUh4iZlMs0aN4mKisD4C.jpg',NULL,'Jesse decides to make a change, while Walt and Skyler try to deal with an unexpected demand.'),(58,5,12,'Rabid Dog','/5VkI8lm7Xcmlxk92pWRyW341d70.jpg',NULL,'An unusual strategy starts to bear fruit, while plans are set in motion that could change everything.'),(59,5,13,'To\'hajiilee','/z2E4Rq7D5TmAdzS9D6Wije3sGI3.jpg',NULL,'Things heat up for Walt in unexpected ways.'),(60,5,14,'Ozymandias','/s9QORY5rrwzQpTCTgNdBRyKehtL.jpg',NULL,'Everyone copes with radically changed circumstances.'),(61,5,15,'Granite State','/yxldDE4a2NZa9vrBWvTa9OAZpVc.jpg',NULL,'Events set in motion long ago move toward a conclusion.'),(62,5,16,'Felina','/pA0YwyhvdDXP3BEGL2grrIhq8aM.jpg',NULL,'All bad things must come to an end.');
