INSERT INTO `cheers` VALUES (1,1,1,'Give Me a Ring Sometime','/47OHTuom2EDdXbeKsbeY3EtTeca.jpg','70174844','Bride-to-be Diane Chambers becomes the center of attention at a cozy bar called Cheers.'),(2,1,2,'Sam\'s Women','/mkVFlhbVJOB35tJXYG5mVkwiC2s.jpg','70174845','Diane\'s teasing about his airhead women sends Sam looking for a date of a higher cerebral plane and an old customer insists he must see the former owner to discuss his personal problems.'),(3,1,3,'The Tortelli Tort','/8l307XokLZMFrdzlVFwPNjlXQU5.jpg','70174846','Carla\'s fiery temper almost costs Sam the bar when she attacks an obnoxious Yankees fan.'),(4,1,4,'Sam at Eleven','/gfiI2uXfvIJuReIA3RorlHPDQ2y.jpg','70174847','Sam realizes how much he misses his former sports celebrity status when a local newscaster asks to interview him again.'),(5,1,5,'Coach\'s Daughter','/kNelZxWRwHevPUpB2zZUVvMPhHR.jpg','70174848','Coach\'s daughter brings the obnoxious lout she plans to marry to meet her father.'),(6,1,6,'Any Friend of Diane\'s','/a2o9WSPZvWsVDH32iAWRtljk76U.jpg','70174849','Diane becomes upset when Sam hits on an old friend of hers who\'s on the rebound from an unhappy love affair.'),(7,1,7,'Friends, Romans, Accountants','/sGw8yDKz9mSDG3ODY3j097alya5.jpg','70174850','Norm tries to make points with the boss by planning the annual office party at Cheers and arranging for Diane to be the old man\'s \"date\".'),(8,1,8,'Truce or Consequences','/7KU83r7JLfDMf7igsSdZkNAxGsA.jpg','70174851','Diane and Carla decide to bury the hatchet over after work drinks, which lead to a startling confession from Carla about her youngest child.'),(9,1,9,'Coach Returns to Action','/1A3doHzUltA8wErccbW5XJCfDHF.jpg','70174852','Coach and Sam become unlikely romantic rivals for Coach\'s new neighbor.'),(10,1,10,'Endless Slumper','/8stBHCvcjevDk1cfJrmfwIqha0y.jpg','70174853','Rick Walker, a friend of Sam, seeks his advice on how to end a losing streak.'),(11,1,11,'One for the Book','/dyiY7AsPeFbm9R2kLONTHLXGv6q.jpg','70174854','While Diane keeps notes on bar conversation, a novice comes in for one final fling before entering a monastery and a World War I doughboy shows up for a very small reunion.'),(12,1,12,'The Spy Who Came In for a Cold One','/r4mAQIoVhV8qLRjR4jWfRc00U3c.jpg','70174855','The bar patrons are all enthralled by the mysterious gentleman who claims to be a secret agent.'),(13,1,13,'Now Pitching, Sam Malone','/shQi9T7CpuflR6hxh6C5EIsBrHE.jpg','70174856','Sam lets the sexy appeal of an agent and the glamour of the public spotlight lure him into being a TV pitchman.'),(14,1,14,'Let Me Count the Ways','/ftbM2dYlePMZQf9wVP8Q5INeDvc.jpg','70174857','Diane looks to her friends for comfort when her cat dies, but finds everyone too enthralled by a Celtics game to notice.'),(15,1,15,'Father Knows Last','/aV9uVrQM1MikjsicGY68eqfo4ao.jpg','70174858','Carla has a secret that\'s about to be revealed:she\'s five months pregnant.'),(16,1,16,'The Boys in the Bar','/clRjQiPN5EURRPUP8PLOqWCohqu.jpg','70174859','Cheers\' regulars fear the place may become a gay hangout after an old friend of Sam\'s reveals his homosexuality on TV.'),(17,1,17,'Diane\'s Perfect Date','/5zXl1CgD4FVt4Xl4q3Nlw0Ri71K.jpg','70174860','Sam and Diane dare each other to find the other\'s perfect date, but Sam\'s last minute choice doesn\'t quite measure up.'),(18,1,18,'No Contest','/6GRDvKHhxAvHcFhrUTvCiC3ZYgG.jpg','70174861','Sam enters Diane in the \"Miss Boston Barmaid\" contest without telling her.'),(19,1,19,'Pick a Con...Any Con','/a3Jgai2SLJmTa7YDe9fd6UBZsjY.jpg','70174862','Sam enlists Harry the conman to help fleece a card shark who cheated Coach out of a lot of money.'),(20,1,20,'Someone Single, Someone Blue','/kg0cdpCc3JqYzb3nPAJolIX1WST.jpg','70174863','Diane\'s mother turns up at Cheers with the news that Diane must marry before the next day or her mother will lose her share of Diane\'s father\'s estate.'),(21,1,21,'Showdown, Part I','/pbK7STeh0CUC6yeqWq4HGRBL1GB.jpg','70174864','Diane\'s fascination with Sam\'s older brother brings their long simmering relationship to a boil when the sibling asks Diane to go to Paris with him.'),(22,1,22,'Showdown, Part II','/s7gbFN3weo42ESOSDbg9ICgbbdN.jpg','70174865','Diane\'s fascination with Sam\'s older brother brings their long simmering relationship to a boil when the sibling asks Diane to go to Paris with him.'),(23,2,1,'Power Play','/mw1yZ0HS9ClicZ2FzFZGFsXIZRh.jpg','70174866','The regular gang finds Sam and Diane\'s romance hard to believe, a view apparently shared by Diane, who throws Sam out of her apartment after only five minutes.'),(24,2,2,'Little Sister Don\'t Cha','/nU1L0ukWp8FyysnzmTDFuSIEin7.jpg','70174867','Carla goes on a maternity leave and is replaced by her supposedly shy and innocent sister.'),(25,2,3,'Personal Business','/2r0Hzg8LyFQ9Eg3H0WceF5s7T1i.jpg','70174868','Diane, angry at the implication that she couldn\'t hold a job anywhere but Cheers, leaves for better position and Norm leaves Vera.'),(26,2,4,'Homicidal Ham','/a2pkx2TBIcmNcGxHQGi5JBHgT83.jpg','70174869','Andy, the ex-con Sam arranged as a blind date for Diane, returns to Cheers to show off his acting ability.'),(27,2,5,'Sumner\'s Return','/giTFerZuatuYWcD4oQqM3Tcl7GW.jpg','70174870','Diane\'s intellectual former fiance returns to reclaim her and puts Sam into an anxiety attack when he tries to measure up by reading Tolstoy.'),(28,2,6,'Affairs of the Heart','/4LS8INmAlTslsOZzbh3xP7qfnCN.jpg','70174871','Carla rejects a man interested in her romantically, convinced that he must have some \"\"fatal flaw\"\" to find her attractive.'),(29,2,7,'Old Flames','/c7wNlzdCWFjlMpKqthynIzcERe2.jpg','70174872','Sam\'s old buddy Dave Richards bets Sam he can break up his romance with Diane within 24 hours and it looks like a sure thing when Diane learns he still has his little black book.'),(30,2,8,'Manager Coach','/iTypd7pp6aNtYsfuBXXIbIlgK5L.jpg','70174873','Coach becomes a slave driver when he\'s put in charge of Little League team.'),(31,2,9,'They Called Me Ma