isappearance,'),(219,10,9,'Fate','/1YpUMnSLK4hMkpjCElFW6YhyZcg.jpg',NULL,'The BAU investigates random murders in northern Virginia and searches for a conflicted UnSub who has an uncontrollable urge to kill but is also filled with remorse. Rossi receives a visit from a woman who could hold a secret from his past.'),(220,10,10,'Amelia Porter','/AgnpDIgtpNNZSBZw6LKCvQwc6t6.jpg',NULL,'When the BAU is called to Salt Lake City Utah to investigate a triple homicide, the search for a connection among the victims could lead them to a fugitive who could have ties to the UnSub.'),(221,10,11,'The Forever People','/zQ2Nvuwe30tNgic6v1TfzTN6j1a.jpg',NULL,'When frozen bodies are found in Nevada floating in water, the BAU’s investigation leads them to suspect that the victims were part of a cult that could be behind the deaths. Also, JJ confronts old demons from her abduction and torture last year.'),(222,10,12,'Anonymous','/eJ6owBJP3JsdnproGj3bLDfVsWX.jpg',NULL,'The BAU searches Tallahassee for a serial killer who calls the authorities to report the crimes prior to committing murder. Also, as Rossi prepares for a weekend visit with his daughter, Joy, he receives startling news about the death of a comrade in Vietnam.'),(223,10,13,'Nelson\'s Sparrow','/4YBOSxsEUFeynrAlylN7PGaDNJx.jpg',NULL,'The BAU revisits its origins when they look at one of Rossi and Gideon’s old cases to track a killer that got away.'),(224,10,14,'Hero Worship','/wIvasZ7uR77WAz1vJpa93RZUrhw.jpg',NULL,'When an Indianapolis coffee shop is blown up and a hero emerges from the wreckage, the BAU tries to protect that person and his family while searching for the UnSub before more incidents occur.'),(225,10,15,'Scream','/3ijm7vFf9e9ykyCxAwswSw2Jhat.jpg',NULL,'Victims in California have the BAU searching for an UnSub who may have witnessed abuse as a child. Meanwhile, Kate shows parental concern when her niece, Meg, makes a date with a friend to meet a boy they met online.'),(226,10,16,'Lockdown','/t9Rk0NE3mSLZ4wMkACD3