r a vigilante UnSub.'),(233,10,23,'The Hunt','/uapdvp24cSBZQHZTs3yIZyzN0G6.jpg',NULL,''),(234,11,1,'The Job','/lhcXuprZz7ZUL1fH4HS4ZFWoWEP.jpg',NULL,'The BAU is interviewing different candidates to join their ranks in the wake of Kate’s departure, including a forensic psychologist, Dr. Tara Lewis, who is eager to assist their efforts. Also, the BAU hunts for a serial killer who leaves behind distinctive evidence that points to someone intent on revenge.'),(235,11,2,'The Witness','/keKcwaX0lvVmmRSMzsKvcqYM35E.jpg',NULL,'When a Los Angeles bus is attacked with sarin gas, the BAU must act quickly to find the suspect before a larger-scale incident occurs.'),(236,11,3,'\'Til Death Do Us Part','/e4J1oijBRtiDk52LBAB9NQEqlSC.jpg',NULL,'When brides-to-be in Savannah are killed on the eve of their nuptials, the BAU suspects a jilted UnSub is at work.'),(237,11,4,'Outlaw','/vmeUnG4IfFDhLCiNXFRIrr3KQZn.jpg',NULL,'When three restaurant workers are killed in a robbery/homicide in Las Vegas, N.M., the BAU looks at a cold case that happened in the town six years ago for leads.'),(238,11,5,'The Night Watch','/uRb2HxHyKKSKoTIdGVGkTPPtm0P.jpg',NULL,'When the BAU investigates incidents of bodies being incorporated into macabre graffiti art in Detroit, they suspect an elusive-yet-notorious street artist could be the UnSub.  Also, Dr. Lewis struggles to balance her relationship with her fiancé and her work.'),(239,11,6,'Pariahville','/fpAhzmlj1aQewcxsA8im8NrlSFI.jpg',NULL,'When a woman is murdered in a small town in Florida inhabited entirely by sex offenders, the BAU faces a community full of suspects. Also, Lewis receives a career opportunity that may take her away from the BAU.'),(240,11,7,'Target Rich','/buFV82IgiPav8IwJgCojtuGHmxd.jpg',NULL,'The BAU helps Rossi’s journalist daughter, Joy, investigate the disappearance of a college student. Also, the team is alarmed when Giuseppe Montolo dies in prison after he warns Morgan about the “Dirty Dozen,” an underground group of hitmen, and