INSERT INTO `daredevil` VALUES (1,1,1,'Into the Ring','/8PRQB2C6qbnqySbMWC9C9QduVRk.jpg',NULL,'Murdock\'s vigilante crime fighting and his new law practice find equally dangerous challenges in a murder case tied to a corporate crime syndicate.'),(2,1,2,'Cut Man','/u6qLlpPbeNnOwzS7xJhIEmIT7Fq.jpg',NULL,'Murdock makes a near fatal error while trying to save a kidnapped boy, and finds an unlikely ally when he needs saving himself.'),(3,1,3,'Rabbit in a Snow Storm','/rR7TblWNCynvfpnh5VhUWwRhkp.jpg',NULL,'Murdock and Foggy take on a mysterious wealthy client, but Murdock is convinced that there\'s more to the case than just the facts.'),(4,1,4,'In the Blood','/dJSVmTKLesxL4kpD8uzbGqHSTQu.jpg',NULL,'Two vicious Russian brothers working for Fisk strike back against Daredevil. Fisk moves to further consolidate his power in the criminal underworld.'),(5,1,5,'World On Fire','/vif8R3u4lakvK5GAtXNzpZij9Jo.jpg',NULL,'Fisk moves forward with plans that threaten to rip Hell\'s Kitchen apart. Murdock and Foggy take on a case helping tenants victimized by a slumlord.'),(6,1,6,'Condemned','/dNYqdGWMz8IznCWDueRR3FIhif1.jpg',NULL,'Daredevil finds himself trapped in the fallout of Fisk\'s plan to take control of Hell\'s Kitchen. Ben Urich digs closer to the truth.'),(7,1,7,'Stick','/mqdOJ2gmzZ2pzitw1YvU1pf8aFt.jpg',NULL,'An important figure from Murdock\'s past reemerges seeking his help to battle a new enemy threatening Hell\'s Kitchen.'),(8,1,8,'Shadows in the Glass','/y2ldwFJXg3IQDYebdZrOketnhBN.jpg',NULL,'While Murdock, Foggy and Karen\'s mission becomes clearer, Fisk\'s world spins further out of control in his battle for Hell\'s Kitchen.'),(9,1,9,'Speak of the Devil','/o20FQresv5qUlOAiqRvIH07jZr2.jpg',NULL,'When Fisk gains the upper hand, the goal to destroy him becomes even more difficult, while Daredevil faces his own demons.'),(10,1,10,'Nelson v. Murdock','/8uF3DKFmx0qrOmtYsRPgtmP6Pia.jpg',NULL,'Murdock and Foggy\'s relationship is put to the ultimate test while a new enemy against Fisk emerges.'),(11,1,11,'The Path of the Righteous','/bQVrn5Eq9vQAPDc7fh5aaqmWPBk.jpg',NULL,'Fisk and Murdock wrestle with the consequences of their chosen paths, while Ben and Karen get closer to Fisk\'s true past.'),(12,1,12,'The Ones We Leave Behind','/nwcmjyS5NPJ9viSqtrQhwoY7I7n.jpg',NULL,'Fisk seeks revenge while Karen is haunted by recent events. Daredevil makes a startling discovery about Fisk\'s financing.'),(13,1,13,'Daredevil','/nSCJMlJkGULVKHuisKeH9Crguy8.jpg',NULL,'In the season finale, a boxed-in Fisk and a desperate Murdock, Foggy and Karen are forced to play their end games.'),(14,2,1,'Bang','/oiDSkY2h8OGeitwHC0diCy4VllX.jpg',NULL,'Hell\'s Kitchen has calmed, but it\'s not out of the fire yet. When an unknown vigilante begins to take the fight to the streets in a big and bloody way, Matt Murdock must don the mask of Daredevil to stop him before innocent people end up in the crossfire.'),(15,2,2,'Dogs to a Gunfight','/xe3jmTRJF1UyW2V4lXlN3hEfliC.jpg',NULL,'As Murdock recovers from an attack, Foggy and Karen fight to protect their new client from both the law and the Kitchen\'s newest vigilante.'),(16,2,3,'New York\'s Finest','/ru6Toc8IcS6FMYaJiBIbqlhi0e1.jpg',NULL,'Trapped face-to-face with the Punisher, Daredevil wrestles with the morality of vigilante justice. Meanwhile, Foggy and Karen work to save the firm.'),(17,2,4,'Penny and Dime','/gEXMxGecxREbRbxUwMBJPlMlVLq.jpg',NULL,'Karen uncovers shocking facts about the Punisher, who finds himself hunted by a powerful force in Hell\'s Kitchen. Daredevil ponders his next moves.'),(18,2,5,'Kinbaku','/o6rrjZRkefL9zdaX1x5BuAfHaNX.jpg',NULL,'A former lover arrives in Hell\'s Kitchen and turns Murdock\'s world upside down. Karen digs for the truth about the Punisher.'),(19,2,6,'Regrets Only','/3Caj3W6tfllb9vFvTJmOc0ZlnIW.jpg',NULL,'A lethal foe returns with a vengeance, Foggy and Murdock risk the firm to ensure justice, and Karen sees a different side of the Punisher.'),(20,2,7,'Semper Fidelis','/vWpizkHpQ5zKDdUQlW0V5ytKiyO.jpg',NULL,'Murdock and Foggy take on the DA in the trial of the century, but their client refuses to play along. Murdock struggles to balance his dual identities.'),(21,2,8,'Guilty as Sin','/Av47v8LCU6NqVqfC6buKhEYBRzH.jpg',NULL,'As the firm\'s trial spins out of control, a figure from Murdock\'s past returns to deliver shocking revelations about the future of Hell\'s Kitchen.'),(22,2,9,'Seven Minutes in Heaven','/xxUl1nRdB2W8LnZS4ZY3uQe1a7E.jpg',NULL,'Castle gets an offer he can\'t refuse. Foggy and Murdock question the future of their firm, but Karen won\'t give up so easily.'),(23,2,10,'The Man in The Box','/fK5MNDW7sglOPc7CpKYPtf4hgAj.jpg',NULL,'Murdock and Foggy get caught in the crossfire of the Punisher\'s revenge. Karen and Murdock dig for the truth in very different ways.'),(24,2,11,'.380','/mBUA05Rv15ASG7lRyRlQfqKJppl.jpg',NULL,'The Punisher\'s war continues, and so does the body count in Hell\'s Kitchen. Murdock tries to finish what the DA started.'),(25,2,12,'The Dark at the End of the Tunnel','/9ZTRTJvTbEqlFeOIONlbdao4UnR.jpg',NULL,'Daredevil goes underground to save an old friend. Karen follows a dangerous lead. The law firm of Nelson &amp; Murdock may have reached its final chapter.'),(26,2,13,'A Cold Day in Hell\'s Kitchen','/elTucMpUqGnrz7aZJuV0uFvTMt3.jpg',NULL,'In the season finale, Daredevil is backed into the ultimate showdown for his own life -- and the future of Hell\'s Kitchen.'),(27,3,1,'Episode 1',NULL,NULL,'');
