INSERT INTO `fuller_house` VALUES (1,1,1,'Our Very First Show, Again','/kaDQaO55HHkcHAdf3UMLN7UqGp5.jpg','80057197','The entire Tanner clan comes together for a final reunion before the family home is sold, but parting turns out to be tougher than expected'),(2,1,2,'Moving Day','/3ta5oISPOgy5MCTPMOkrDv87A6B.jpg','80057198','When the big day comes for Stephanie and Kimmy to join the Fuller house, Jackson feels outnumbered and takes drastic action'),(3,1,3,'Funner House','/yrJyWx01XQdqNThCTYQKpEFmLx8.jpg','80057199','When Stephanie, Kimmy and DJ have a girls\' night out and leave Joey in charge of the kids, things get wild out on the town and at home.'),(4,1,4,'The Not-So-Great Escape','/5jyjlncgUhBPpK8hrO3TepCgR9k.jpg','80057600','Jackson tries to help Ramona at school but that lands them both in trouble and leads to a disagreement between DJ and Kimmy over parenting styles.'),(5,1,5,'Mad Max','/3LSOiNolRybPDjefsy4Y45Iafvu.jpg','80057601','When an old friend whisks her away for a concert and after-hours fun, Stephanie realizes how much her nephews mean to her. Kimmy finds DJ a date.'),(6,1,6,'The Legend of El Explosivo','/rD67R26gu85poAPSBy4gtXLP2TJ.jpg','80057602','DJ punishes Jackson, causing him to muss his favorite Mexican wrestling league, Lucha Kaboom. But only leads to more action for the fans.'),(7,1,7,'Ramona\'s Not-So-Epic Party','/hubbSJh92mSc7hMcEH4ecEU8Lv4.jpg','80057603','Steve tries setting up DJ\'s handsome coworker with Kimmy, and Ramona\'s much-anticipated 13th birthday party doesn\'t turn out as planned for anybody.'),(8,1,8,'Secrets,Lies and Firetrucks','/yoerAj0P42YePcdG0Tr1BHYPvs0.jpg','80057604','When Max learns to lie, he also learns that lies can backfire. Meanwhile, the ladies of the house fall in love with secrets.'),(9,1,9,'War of the Roses','/e5NQxP9LEv1yEtdhXEet8zCzeQr.jpg','80057605','After 1,000 roses show up without a card, DJ, Kimmy and Stephanie must figure out which one of them has a secret admirer.'),(10,1,10,'A Giant Leap','/i7owl1Ff84EWFhtuPpGceqAJ3NC.jpg','80057606','Things get out of hand when Stephanie\'s new boyfriend, Hunter Pence of the San Fransisco Giants, invites everybody to one of his baseball games.'),(11,1,11,'Partnership in the Night','/tIpJCJmkd497xGfAQGnqJlHGJpC.jpg','80057607','Stephanie and Kimmy form a strange partnership. DJ\'s boss retires, and Max has Jackson and Ramona right where he wants them.'),(12,1,12,'Save the Dates','/fz0Pf7BYCkXNJXocCDn0qRA9Bwt.jpg','80057608','DJ has a date with her past that catches get off guard, and Kimmy\'s date with Fernando is nothing but surprises.'),(13,1,13,'Love is in the Air','/r24ItY7B4KRCgZOVnFUxoAy5N7x.jpg','80057609','When Jesse and Becky return to renew their vows, a bachelorette party leads to trouble for DJ, who is forced to make a decision.'),(14,2,1,'Welcome Back','/sDjRDSaH80tw2YBZ3eCLntk1gHs.jpg','80104071','DJ finally decides between Matt and Steve, but they throw her a curveball before her annual back-to-school barbecue. A homeless Fernando moves in.'),(15,2,2,'Mom Interference','/3mwDqXNYh06KWjCFzpiWx47wvet.jpg','80104072','It\'s a full house for game night when Steve and Matt bring uninvited guests. Jackson decides to join the football team.'),(16,2,3,'Ramona\'s Not-So-Epic First Kiss','/7LmsmkY89YcpcKHNKhgXvcKKsqE.jpg','80104073','Ramona\'s first kiss leads to a heartbreaking lesson in love. A memorable \"Sister Night\" makes wedding crashers out of DJ and Stephanie.'),(17,2,4,'Curse of Tanner Manor','/ajaJZpuu5mKuoPGTfEn5C866Sed.jpg','80104074','Jackson and Ramona would rather die than go to DJ\'s \"scary\" family Halloween party, where Fernando and Kimmy pull off the ultimate couples costume.'),(18,2,5,'Doggy Daddy','/8066fbczEGt2m62BcY3MHpE9o5s.jpg','80104075','A not-so-typical day involves a dance audition, a toddler play date, four chickens and a vet emergency. Matt comes to an important realization.'),(19,2,6,'Fuller Thanksgiving','/8Z38fugaKLdH8QHy1zBiXVJtmh3.jpg','80104076','The house feels overstuffed when the entire Tanner family shows up for Thanksgiving, pushing DJ\'s organizational skills into overdrive.'),(20,2,7,'Girl Talk','/hklgjmMSPbEPy0iRAmA3BdWaAag.jpg','80104077','Kimmy hatches a plan to get the girls\' childhood band, Girl Talk, back together. A vengeful video making fun of Ramona goes viral.'),(21,2,8,'A Tangled Web','/36sFxYyf4m6AhGYQ1h4UXEY0nM.jpg','80104078','While Jackson pet-sits for Lola, DJ works overtime to help Max ace a school project. Jimmy makes a music video for Stephanie\'s latest song.'),(22,2,9,'Glazed & Confused','/mYalrY9C4h4E7ncLRj5UYVLQBXJ.jpg','80104079','With out-of-town trips planned for the adults, Uncle Joey delivers doughnuts -- and unexpected drama. Stephanie\'s nervous about singing on television.'),(23,2,10,'New Kids in the House','/qMVzZWqlokzUJmqLCm9L1zPZNQA.jpg','80104081','Kimmy and Stephanie have an epic surprise planned for DJ\'s 39th birthday, but Max cooks up a painful twist that changes everything.'),(24,2,11,'DJ and Kimmy\'s High School Reunion','/99Hjhl3tQhShKpFahwniqs3PsNY.jpg','80104083','A high school reunion leaves DJ wondering whether she still has feelings for Steve, while a hapless Kimmy is trending for all the wrong reasons.'),(25,2,12,'Nutcrackers','/wk2ApBVKhtvSR1Uam5dklgyEDTR.jpg','80104080','\'Tis the season to be in love, but Stephanie doesn\'t want to hear it. Max gets a girlfriend for Christmas, and Ramona suits up for \"The Nutcracker.\"'),(26,2,13,'Happy New Year Baby','/gZ0ihMabEAjbTOwZmoFKTAqUZXf.jpg','80104082','Steve comes to DJ for help with an important proposal. Jesse and Becky\'s new addition brings Danny and Joey home -- and has Jimmy spouting baby talk.'),(27,3,1,'Best Summer Ever','/7xHwwTeZeDH4uwXywAGxtxANgmt.jpg','80147424','Steve and CJ announce plans for a destination wedding, and DJ sends Jackson to summer school. Stephanie and Jimmy suspect Fernando is up to something.'),(28,3,2,'Break A Leg','/r4S7BglH4s92Z9NHOXHoEdeOUtF.jpg','80167462','Wedding planner Kimmy works overtime to earn Steve and CJ’s business, and DJ signs on as Stephanie’s life coach. Jimmy and Fernando move in together.'),(29,3,3,'Declarations Of Independence','/ufxrNiLbiTLe6O1wUhdIn28ZGOQ.jpg','80167463','The Danny Tanner Annual Fourth of July Barbecue brings everyone home for some star-spangled fun. But heartbreak might be on the menu.'),(30,3,4,'My Little Hickey','/3vGW987hZXHraRqxBbXWxrcNUf3.jpg','80167464','While Steve samples wedding cakes, Ramona goes to great lengths to hide a hickey from her mother. Jackson\'s study group takes over the house.'),(31,3,5,'Uncle Jesse\'s Adventures In Babysitting','/kc8XXNYxoE9hazMWH17e9nOFkEN.jpg','80167465','While the ladies are out for the night, Uncle Jesse is left in charge, putting out fires left and right. Fernando restores Kimmy\'s childhood home.'),(32,3,6,'M-M-M-My Ramona','/9Vby1VuWIF1OEJNoBW3oMRJkA7V.jpg','80167466','DJ\'s thrilled when Jackson agrees to shadow her at the office. Fernando builds Ramona a lavish bedroom -- complete with a frozen yogurt bar.'),(33,3,7,'Say Yes To The Dress','/y887vJpKft3avyefxVVisgXJsMs.jpg','80167467','A bridal shop mishap leaves DJ doubting the future of her friendship with Steve. Gia\'s daughter comes over to study and winds up spending the night.'),(34,3,8,'Maybe Baby','/42RAbn1BdQ70EH7i4EV0wHHdy1n.jpg','80167468','Becky takes Stephanie to the doctor to find out whether she\'s got a shot at motherhood. Kimmy helps Joey show his kids who\'s boss.'),(35,3,9,'Wedding Or Not Here We Come','/5XKaLJRKw3Cv6OXiZ7XsbRYlNVX.jpg','80167469','The gang is flying coach for Steve and CJ\'s wedding -- but Max and Fernando plan to sit in first class. Stephanie starts her search for sperm donors.'),(36,3,10,'My Best Friend\'s Japanese Wedding','/8aGDCcPoR9SuEaCGhNGaMvMAnlm.jpg','80167470','In Japan, Steve and CJ\'s wedding dishes up one disaster after another -- from a maid of honor who\'s MIA to a talking toilet with an alarming appetite.'),(37,3,11,'Troller Coaster','/wNZrdxFwFJn1GYzrwwydnkT9Ef.jpg','80167471','A letter prompts Ramona to reconsider her future, and Max tempts fate on the \"Troller Coaster.\" Steve and DJ have an important talk.'),(38,3,12,'Fast Times at Bayview High','/uhVzEb4punn2BEmTu3u3OAzZwv8.jpg','80167472','Jimmy and Steph visit the fertility clinic, and Jackson and Ramona start high school. A big surprise at work brings Matt and DJ closer together.'),(39,3,13,'A Tommy Tale','/fOnOxKdv6dFiTJlJRyIIOq7Gmzg.jpg','80167473','DJ pulls out all the stops to get Tommy into a prestigious preschool. Jackson and Ramona unplug for \"Pioneer Day\" -- so Kimmy decides to join them.'),(40,3,14,'Surrogate City','/feKm0uSjClrL4T3wWVMge1Q7fct.jpg','80167474','Steph and Jimmy launch their search for a surrogate mother. A rebellious Jackson\'s \"cool\" new look pushes all of DJ\'s buttons.'),(41,3,15,'Soul Sisters','/lV7zeycnStcipwUHZ6atLzgwZM9.jpg','80167475','Kimmy snags Steph for some \"soul sister\" bonding while DJ attempts a day off. Max breaks a Tanner family heirloom and tries to hide the evidence.'),(42,3,16,'Happily Ever After','/7Gxycz2HVXjrUyyz1oaFMVWJEBk.jpg','80167476','The She-Wolves suit up to help when Ramona\'s \"Best Homecoming Dance Ever\" ... isn\'t. Kimmy and Steph cater to a demanding client.'),(43,3,17,'Fullers in a Fog','/yjIYkSX8wE0CJaxTwrGOQMEbI4I.jpg','80167477','Bad karma clouds the house when Danny, Jesse and Joey come home to celebrate their 30-year “Dad-iversary\" while DJ preps for an important date.'),(44,3,18,'Here Comes the Sun','/A7WEmcP2XAzHJFye1VBRb6Zgxr8.jpg','80167478','With big things hanging in the balance, the gang tries to revive the Tanner-Fuller magic with an \'80s -- themed bash -- complete with costumes.');
