 needed makeover, his success also has a troublesome impact back in Lima.'),(70,4,4,'The Break-Up','/lrpFKMOrRym0F6UUttMrFmdE9Zh.jpg',NULL,'Rachel and Kurt are caught off-guard when they get unexpected visits in New York City. Meanwhile, Santana and Brittany deal with the long distance between them, and Will and Emma disagree on a new job offer.'),(71,4,5,'The Role You Were Born to Play','/yZOuCrMSjKOtPyhKDDx2bYU7VvC.jpg',NULL,'Hopes and schemes play out as the Glee Club holds auditions for the school’s musical.'),(72,4,6,'Glease','/78hh2MiZXJO1gQflGcfWCWxp2kb.jpg',NULL,'Rachel and Kurt pay a visit to Lima as the glee club launches its production of \"Grease\". Meanwhile, Cassandra July returns to shake things up in Rachel\'s life, and Santana comes back to lend a helping hand.'),(73,4,7,'Dynamic Duets','/Aop13IizpBB0pRmo4dqpwXbPKrn.jpg',NULL,'A love triangle heats up among Marley, Jake and Ryder, and Blaine has a run-in with the Warblers.'),(74,4,8,'Thanksgiving','/pksHyue3PrIbwENDUcjzU7HoRp6.jpg',NULL,'It\'s time for Sectionals, and New Directions receives guidance from some of the recent McKinley graduates who volunteer to mentor the glee club during their Thanksgiving breaks. Meanwhile, Rachel and Kurt have a non-traditional holiday dinner in the Big Apple.'),(75,4,9,'Swan Song','/ann6XtmF3LTWRs66NF4ZtU0Ssax.jpg',NULL,'Finn thinks about his future with the glee club after Sectionals are over. Elsewhere, Rachel gets ready for NYADA\'s winter showcase; and Kurt gets a second chance at an audition.'),(76,4,10,'Glee, Actually','/hEuVOR7Br2N5FVHZ36qfYKAla5p.jpg',NULL,'A tribute to the film \"Love, Actually\" with different storylines all dealing with the holidays. Sam and Brittany live as if it\'s the end of the world as the Mayans know it. The Puckermans, including half-brothers Puck and Jake and their mothers, come together for Hanukkah. Artie has an epiphany through a dream sequence. Kurt has an unforgettable Christmas.'),(77,4,11,'Sadie Hawkins','/tfI0gitWXcMFZVZKNWVoG2LVVoS.jpg',NULL,'McKinley’s Sadie Hawkins dance offers several gleeks a rare chance to feel empowered. Sam and Blaine investigate a possible cheating scandal at Sectionals. Kurt makes a new friend at NYADA.'),(78,4,12,'Naked','/zSaO1w9unOD6MsgsQjXoSVs116o.jpg',NULL,'New Directions produces a sexy calendar to raise money for their trip to Regionals. Rachel is faced with a personal dilemma when she’s cast in a student film. Finn and Sue go toe-to-toe.'),(79,4,13,'Diva','/YN4DLpdQWEK2PJw9qUsySuq3lF.jpg',NULL,'Finn encourages the glee-club members to channel their inner divas. Elsewhere, Rachel\'s arrogance causes Kurt to reach a breaking point; and Emma throws herself into wedding preparations.'),(80,4,14,'I Do','/1dON8NrQNHoA4C5XfOrDQUbV5jd.jpg',NULL,'Will and Emma get ready for their Valentine\'s Day wedding with the help of past and present New Directions members.'),(81,4,15,'Girls (and Boys) on Film','/nuYLZ403c9X4mskNz78FST3EiaX.jpg',NULL,'The kids of New Directions go head-to-head in their annual boys vs. girls mash-up competition, this time using the music of the movies. Meanwhile, in New York, Santana makes herself at home in the loft a little too quickly for Rachel and Kurt\'s comfort.'),(82,4,16,'Feud','/hpOZIQd8YkijfjeKpeTldYlBMYX.jpg',NULL,'Blaine and Sue will have a sing-off, while Ryder has a scary story coming.'),(83,4,17,'Guilty Pleasures','/cJwzIUd2MM4jSOuNuWsQoqidGIS.jpg',NULL,'The New Directions tackle an assignment, meaning the songs as well as  groups that everyone is too embarrassed to admit that they love.'),(84,4,18,'Shooting Star','/pvIeZQmkER0SbK92qolGaVKgqYN.jpg',NULL,'The members of New Directions are prepping for regionals, but when an unthinkable event occurs at McKinley High, perspectives are put into order.'),(85,4,19,'Sweet Dreams','/jso4gLU9G1wbyp8cJ6ljzrTexMO.jpg',NULL,'When Mr. Schuester comes up with the setlist for regionals, the New Directions are not pleased, Rachel sings an unexpected song for her \"Funny Girl audition\", and Marley writes an original song.'),(86,4,20,'Lights Out','/nRdqxpQ0gBS8rUCI0sGz30O4bnA.jpg',NULL,'When the power goes out at McKinley High, Will and Finn enlist the members of New Directions to \"unplug\" and perform acoustic numbers. Meanwhile, Isabelle Wright asks Kurt to volunteer at the Vogue.com charity event, with Rachel and Santana in tow.'),(87,4,21,'Wonder-Ful','/f4sSZ1tgbrAaSMBncc6GEslS8Hz.jpg',NULL,'The members of New Directions take on the greatest hits of music icon Stevie Wonder. Meanwhile, Artie receives news that could affect his future and his mom. In New York, Rachel prepares for her \"Funny Girl\" callback.'),(88,4,22,'All or Nothing','/EvABnjpNZ2Hzv2NhQsRZ7T7INi.jpg',NULL,'It\'s finally time for Regionals, and the glee club is more determined than ever to advance to Nationals. Brittany returns from her MIT trip with a new attitude and Ryder finally has a lead on who is \"catfishing\" him.'),(89,5,1,'Love, Love, Love','/jurKl53vAzRowonV2oh02xXYYhV.jpg',NULL,'The members of New Directions are back in action and take on their biggest assignment yet: the Beatles! As Will enlists the kids to pay homage to the classic song catalog from the Fab Four, Blaine and Kurt attempt to answer questions about their future together. Meanwhile, Rachel\'s New York ambitions take an unexpected turn.'),(90,5,2,'Tina in the Sky with Diamonds','/qPFIDLvKCmELfI0WZifOLY1RFoF.jpg',NULL,'As the Prom approaches, the race for Prom Queen brings out the best and the worst in candidates Tina and Kitty. Meanwhile, Sam tries to make a connection with a new school nurse, an increasingly discouraged Rachel waits for word on her Funny Girl callback, and Santana makes a new friend at work.'),(91,5,3,'The Quarterback','/AhdQrjiyOrAQV9sb0rP3ymIyDvS.jpg',NULL,'The New Directions remember Finn.'),(92,5,4,'A Katy or a Gaga','/8cqYDgQsE6gB7beVQXGUlGGFfSN.jpg',NULL,'The members of New Directions tackle their assignment of getting out of their comfort zones and determining whether they\'re more like \"Katy\" (Perry) or (Lady) \"Gaga.\" Kurt holds auditions for his new band and must decide if he\'ll let in the overly bold performer, Starchild. Meanwhile, Jake gets closer to Bree as he and Marley grow apart.'),(93,5,5,'The End of Twerk','/lPOIe7l4efqH0lu76WxQPEM1R44.jpg',NULL,'The glee club learns the dance of the hour: twerking. Meanwhile, Marley discovers Jake\'s relationship with Bree, and Rachel tries to convince Kurt they both should get tattoos.'),(94,5,6,'Movin\' Out','/2wT9pElnGV98H52rTWnWtsNRof2.jpg',NULL,'The New Directions pay homage to the Piano Man: Billy Joel. As graduation looms closer, the seniors make plans for their futures beyond the halls of McKinley.'),(95,5,7,'Puppet Master','/hUNF6Gaftj0zcy8N02npgiB3KrT.jpg',NULL,'Blaine believes he has the best plan to win nationals, but the other club members think he\'s too controlling; members of Kurt\'s band disagree over the venue of their first gig; Sue gets in touch with her feminine side.'),(96,5,8,'Previously Unaired Christmas','/qq3Y8YbNSLUgSHaq6EPi47vlb8p.jpg',NULL,'Sue Sylvester introduces the episode as a Christmas special that FOX did not allow to air from last year. The members of New Directions audition for roles in McKinley\'s living Nativity Scene. Meanwhile in New York, Rachel, Kurt and Santana work as Santa\'s elves at a mall.'),(97,5,9,'Frenemies','/fqJ9BCRUdefHun1ofa3Zea1dvWH.jpg',NULL,'Santana auditions and snags the role of Rachel’s understudy in “Funny Girl,” causing a feud between the roommates. Meanwhile, back in Lima, Tina and Artie compete against each other to be the class valedictorian.'),(98,5,10,'Trio','/y3L24J4GhOJjBjVVb1CVpueYl6a.jpg',NULL,'When Sam, Tina and Blaine plan a lock-in at the school, Becky unexpectedly joins in; Elliot (Adam Lambert) gets caught in Santana and Rachel\'s feud.'),(99,5,11,'City of Angels','/jizn6mSkXq6xhg2znAjiam98rRW.jpg',NULL,'The glee club -- and two special guests -- travels to Los Angeles to compete in nationals.'),(100,5,12,'10