INSERT INTO `grace_and_frankie` VALUES (1,1,1,'The End','/mXHhWuOJ6EI0PHHHSeNVqxsdqcG.jpg',NULL,'Grace and Frankie are stunned when their husbands inform them that they want divorces. They\'re even more stunned when they find out why.'),(2,1,2,'The Credit Cards','/fy9NvIJSzjihRqD0dwKWkb3XxLy.jpg',NULL,'The messy realities of divorce start to sink in for Grace, Frankie, Robert, Sol and their equally frazzled adult children.'),(3,1,3,'The Dinner','/2OtJJq4Q0QwjIW2dJGWhYT5dvLh.jpg',NULL,'Grace and Frankie decide to go back to work. Robert and Sol have an awkward dinner party for their children.'),(4,1,4,'The Funeral','/gyvPrRFovUyM7ys4zbf2Mj8Ioz5.jpg',NULL,'Emotions run high when a funeral throws Grace, Frankie, Robert and Sol together in public for the first time since the split.'),(5,1,5,'The Fall','/oFCY9GZMH9vuohovtPkxl7nQPz5.jpg',NULL,'Grace has an eye-opening experience when she goes out for frozen yogurt with Frankie and Briana on a Saturday night.'),(6,1,6,'The Earthquake','/gU2kl90UJeplbp4VX9dpHmHQ1pT.jpg',NULL,'Sol takes care of Frankie after she has an earthquake freak-out, while Grace goes on her first date. Coyote pays Mallory a surprise visit.'),(7,1,7,'The Spelling Bee','/u7p9J54P58EO8UsKyeFed1eUkMO.jpg',NULL,'Frankie, Grace and Briana have unexpected encounters when they try new ways to deal with being single.'),(8,1,8,'The Sex','/kABIScfCFIdJPPByhtBXXo7PTO.jpg',NULL,'Frankie takes a new look at her Yam Man Jacob, while Grace and Guy get closer. Bud and Coyote have a brotherly talk. Sol is terrified of Briana.'),(9,1,9,'The Invitation','/7nxJTwzl6dznwx7WoADt04o3pwC.jpg',NULL,'Briana tries Frankie\'s homemade organic beauty product. Robert finds out about Guy and Grace. Frankie tries to set boundaries with Sol.'),(10,1,10,'The Elevator','/48072o3AkTfbzb2fiy1JWOr508q.jpg',NULL,'After they sign the divorce papers, Frankie, Grace, Sol, Robert and Bud remember a pivotal weekend from five years before.'),(11,1,11,'The Secrets','/eRB0hJsFqLURSElcMgNB7ediJgC.jpg',NULL,'Grace tells Frankie a secret that Frankie shares with Sol, setting off multiple arguments in both houses. Briana gets closer with a co-worker.'),(12,1,12,'The Bachelor Party','/noHwdFIhEMBZ8mnLWC0uuter1gL.jpg',NULL,'Bud and Coyote ask Briana and Mallory to help them throw Sol and Robert\'s bachelor party. Grace offers to do ANYTHING to cheer up Frankie.'),(13,1,13,'The Vows','/wgRLXAnVEh42ql960JPrhcGy1P5.jpg',NULL,'As the wedding day approaches, Grace and Robert have problems expressing themselves, while Sol and Frankie finally clear out their old house.'),(14,2,1,'The Wish','/4339Bm8f90IHXixfxz0ykVx8fiE.jpg',NULL,'Sol plans to tell Robert about his betrayal. Frankie is determined to finally separate emotionally from Sol, but events pull her back in.'),(15,2,2,'The Vitamix','/zYTTPkn8gmBMzCFSTslNqKHllD1.jpg',NULL,'Brianna, Mallory and Bud help Sol deal with wedding details. A visit to Robert and Sol\'s house brings up strong emotions for Grace and Frankie.'),(16,2,3,'The Negotiation','/oL7Iptf0XZS8ZCjK0l8IeU5uk45.jpg',NULL,'Brianna wants to produce Frankie\'s organic yam lube. Grace competes for her grandchildren\'s affection. Frankie reconnects with her Yam Man, Jacob.'),(17,2,4,'The Road Trip','/99r5bALCPRuyUNwhjnfwJBJPtQB.jpg',NULL,'Frankie tracks down Grace\'s former love Phil on the internet, and the two set off to find him. Tensions arise between Sol and Robert.'),(18,2,5,'The Test','/qLQASrCDaeRWhbCg3g0a83lVsw2.jpg',NULL,'Frankie has difficulty passing the test to renew her driver\'s license. Grace attempts to amp up her social life by reconnecting with old friends.'),(19,2,6,'The Chicken','/kdH67qiY4jK9qJsEsdt0h3Kffbw.jpg',NULL,'While Grace mentors a young woman seeking a new career, Frankie has conflicted feelings for Jacob, who wants more than a business relationship.'),(20,2,7,'The Boar','/sZwyub3SVbGryMTI8uLKhiKgXEi.jpg',NULL,'Grace intervenes after Robert and Sol\'s big fight. Frankie opens up to Jacob. An online friend request from Phil surprises Grace.'),(21,2,8,'The Anchor','/v2NDcbwJrN3auEYnW4yAJpw0jlm.jpg',NULL,'Frankie has issues with Brianna\'s ideas for her yam lube and makes a stand. Phil asks Grace out for lunch. Sol tries to work things out with Robert.'),(22,2,9,'The Goodbyes','/fDYgWHuY66CD3GgJa0azJfAVeCN.jpg',NULL,'Coyote shares some surprising news. Things go awry when Frankie and Sol host a family brunch. Grace must make a difficult decision about Phil.'),(23,2,10,'The Loophole','/wg3hV3yYukiYNjsgPFtwumzutxZ.jpg',NULL,'Grace and Phil get closer, but complications arise. Sol and Robert square off on opposite sides of the conflict between Frankie and Brianna.'),(24,2,11,'The Bender','/drUSVMzwnzM9tG9cFGVx7jNLdYu.jpg',NULL,'Grace and Frankie nurse their emotional wounds: Frankie performs a ritual on the beach, and Grace goes out drinking. Bud and Coyote meet Jacob.'),(25,2,12,'The Party','/uZb52xm33NoTplIBqY4d1bcrVX.jpg',NULL,'As Frankie helps her old friend Babe plan a big bash, she\'s faced with a troubling decision. Grace tries to make amends to Frankie.'),(26,2,13,'The Coup','/4QD6FqLsc4Cnq4nqWVNQnCdL8Zy.jpg',NULL,'Frankie and Grace receive surprise gifts from Babe that open new horizons for each of them. Sol reveals a long-held secret at Bud\'s birthday party.'),(27,3,1,'The Art Show','/sQO3ASCMsvXjUUwlEJHRixxKalR.jpg',NULL,'Grace and Frankie try to get a bank loan to help start their new business. Frankie\'s art show is rife with family tensions and minor dramas.'),(28,3,2,'The Incubator','/6xCF6J9aiU7RTiOxcCJak6EphaO.jpg',NULL,'Grace and Frankie pitch their business plan at a hip startup incubator. Grace fights with Jacob. Sol and Robert play hooky from work.'),(29,3,3,'The Focus Group','/kbliVv5muM35HD2wDThthaMIbuX.jpg',NULL,'Grace and Frankie put together a focus group to test their vibrator prototype, but things go awry. Robert and Sol audition for a play.'),(30,3,4,'The Burglary','/5QQhfHFMJruX7NjldRggwYNExOv.jpg',NULL,'After they\'re robbed, Frankie is rattled, but Grace has a secret. With Robert in rehearsals and making new friends, Sol feels left out.'),(31,3,5,'The Gun','/sdhkTat8K8h1BIC5CEY1VbGS0X8.jpg',NULL,'Furious about Grace\'s revelation, Frankie refuses to make up with her. In the wake of his fight with Sol, Robert decides to come out to his mother.'),(32,3,6,'The Pot','/ntFMdZlU2Xuy8dgCRMqR0j9zUhh.jpg',NULL,'Frankie refuses to go home, and all the kids are dragged into Grace and Frankie\'s fight. Grace, Brianna and Mallory smoke Frankie\'s pot together.'),(33,3,7,'The Floor','/qwXOEn4DdwxP21ANQ7ZoWlSpL4T.jpg',NULL,'The ladies hurt their backs and can’t get off the floor. Coyote looks for a new home. Robert frets over unresolved issues with his mom.'),(34,3,8,'The Alert','/u57saV2UBleEeIGzyEFrAwsytSG.jpg',NULL,'Grace and Frankie launch their business, and Bud brings gifts they\'re reluctant to accept. Sol is upset that Bud wants to fire a longtime employee.'),(35,3,9,'The Apology','/bn5pHAOQnoSNTy3x0Tuf0a4AH7H.jpg',NULL,'Jacob shares something with Frankie that upsets her. Everyone rallies around Robert when his mother dies. Mallory confides in Brianna.'),(36,3,10,'The Labels','/Ap5PRmmJjcl8rs2brH47ygFR7xp.jpg',NULL,'Sol and Robert pitch in when Grace and Frankie are overwhelmed with orders. Bud is thrown for a loop by his girlfriend’s interest in the Ménage à Moi.'),(37,3,11,'The Other Vibrator','/wSLzXMnLJA2dlyTSb0R7vP5ZVMx.jpg',NULL,'Grace and Frankie send a cease and desist letter to the company that stole their idea. A homophobic church group protests Robert\'s play rehearsals.'),(38,3,12,'The Musical','/3iBvhbTJtkYCzs5KcT6MKwap4D6.jpg',NULL,'Grace wants Frankie to go to the hospital after a medical incident, but Frankie insists on alternative healing. The protests disrupt Robert\'s play.'),(39,3,13,'The Sign','/jj6dVsFarZPMHIqz1u3QS3aMoPP.jpg',NULL,'Grace and Frankie face a lawsuit. Sol fights back against the homophobic play protesters. Frankie mulls over a move that would change everything.'),(40,4,1,'The Lodger','/7TCoCxPedv2lxIuCoKej3x2LLCQ.jpg',NULL,'Frankie feels left out of Grace\'s new friendship with Sheree, her new lodger. Sol and Robert are arrested. Bud and Allison throw a gender-reveal party.'),(41,4,2,'The Scavengender Hunt','/m0k8PfUNHZYNJ7EDkosXhekH1iU.jpg',NULL,'Frankie shares what she discovered about Sheree to a skeptical Grace. Bud sends everyone on a scavenger hunt. Frankie makes a big decision.'),(42,4,3,'The Tappys','/h3cwdQMwkYGcneeDKivXcGwj0lp.jpg',NULL,'Grace and Frankie try to help Sheree get her house back... using both legal and illegal methods. Robert is nominated for a Tappy acting award.'),(43,4,4,'The Expiration Date','/dFMsGtvJmtNzOb6VX2yP8htTI9E.jpg',NULL,'Grace fears her relationship has reached its expiration date. Frankie faces an existential crisis when she learns she\'s been declared legally dead.'),(44,4,5,'The Pop-Ups','/vwkWoEa8ZVjvC60UQ84otVfIsJ1.jpg',NULL,'Grace and Frankie hold vibrator pop-up sales at a senior center and a college. Sol and Robert have a disagreement. Bud and Allison hit a roadblock.'),(45,4,6,'The Hinge','/vSTi3rRr41rONzKodu2Tfj7NywM.jpg',NULL,'Frankie reconnects with someone important from her past. Despite problems with her knee, Grace refuses to slow down. Robert tries to make amends.'),(46,4,7,'The Landline','/weT0m2jyLEGAAxAnQw3wwKhDjHI.jpg',NULL,'Frankie and Sol have a blast devising a plan to get Frankie declared legally alive again. Grace faces some truths at a funeral she attends with robert.'),(47,4,8,'The Lockdown','/ikIpWYC2x4LanyyxFXfnSNZO9gY.jpg',NULL,'Frankie convinces Allison to have a home birth. Grace and Frankie wind up stuck with a bickering Robert and Sol when there\'s a neighborhood lockdown.'),(48,4,9,'The Knee','/d8qjPanFHttKEXarnW0ZBWuwLJk.jpg',NULL,'Nick helps Grace while she\'s recovering from surgery. Jacob gets upset with Frankie because she wants to spend all their couple time with the baby.'),(49,4,10,'The Death Stick','/r7VNXubLfjUqk9c1I56TUDLDl5n.jpg',NULL,'Robert and Sol begin therapy. Grace and Frankie get a surprise when they bring gifts to a fan of their vibrators. Brianna\'s nemesis makes an offer.'),(50,4,11,'The Tub','/jhNzQ2Rpw0PI1wMuzYZyg9ylGg5.jpg',NULL,'Grace hires a contractor to fix an issue at the beach house. Sol\'s new friendship makes Robert uncomfortable. Frankie gets lost with the baby.'),(51,4,12,'The Rats','/9pL174aIfE4lIu4ITgpceatnSP9.jpg',NULL,'As Grace and Frankie deal with a major disaster in their home, they each keep secrets from other family members. Everyone attends Robert\'s play.'),(52,4,13,'The Home','/qSGMS5vIOIMJpzljgb9BchjsgOx.jpg',NULL,'Prompted by their children, Grace and Frankie make a change. Robert and Sol channel some fresh energy into their marriage.');
