INSERT INTO `house_of_cards` VALUES (1,1,1,'Chapter 1','/6sAKJySMV5VlrlBs6q9V8FjkwQd.jpg',NULL,'When the newly elected President reneges on a promise, Francis and Claire decide to sever all allegiances and toss the rules out the window.'),(2,1,2,'Chapter 2','/1vjZa5tTaz86kKKBhiYBWnkRlQl.jpg',NULL,'Francis and Doug plan to frame Secretary of State nominee, Michael Kern. Meanwhile, Zoe\'s popularity at the Washington Herald continues to grow.'),(3,1,3,'Chapter 3','/vMXqVtz5ZBR4xuWFTRBJtj0DvSl.jpg',NULL,'Francis heads for his hometown to deal with a crisis. Zoe negotiates the politics of being a journalist on the rise. Claire finds herself a new business partner.'),(4,1,4,'Chapter 4','/1BseCNuPiQHWChHbxGDz5WaBoxG.jpg',NULL,'Francis shakes down the Congressional leadership. Zoe is offered the promotion of White House Correspondent and doesn\'t know if she should take it or not.'),(5,1,5,'Chapter 5','/33pCcjWAYRcgXWKhWk0wPXp5Mfe.jpg',NULL,'A feud starts between Francis and Marty Spinella. Russo goes into depression about the job losses at the shipyards.'),(6,1,6,'Chapter 6','/6cXGqA2XqnuAREg6z3VvErifu5I.jpg',NULL,'The strike between Frank and Marty starts to get out of hand. Russo has decided to run for Governor of Pennsylvania.'),(7,1,7,'Chapter 7','/vj7hlPqAKTHrQxCMmp74G04VPPY.jpg',NULL,'Frank helps Peter get ready for his governor race, but Peter is starting to have second thoughts. Doug tries to help a young hooker in trouble.'),(8,1,8,'Chapter 8','/aQjFqJtsyySgtOt5273N2GAQIaJ.jpg',NULL,'Frank has a library named after him at his old military school. Peter tries to win back the support of his hometown.'),(9,1,9,'Chapter 9','/zgZg8gzvDa0yqvagURKSA706FvX.jpg',NULL,'Frank tries to do whatever it takes to get the new bill passed in Congress. Russo goes on a bus campaign with the Vice President, but the VP is not making it an easy trip for him. Zoe\'s relationship with Frank gets a little bumpy.'),(10,1,10,'Chapter 10','/v3jUPbKmVpaH8a6Qv295qkEdhVm.jpg',NULL,'Claire fuels an old flame. Peter wrestles with his demons. Francis crosses the point of no return.'),(11,1,11,'Chapter 11','/tVxl2dA9O8ajENIaHhwHo69fk5y.jpg',NULL,'Zoe extends her time away from The Hill while Francis tracks down Russo and engages in damage control.'),(12,1,12,'Chapter 12','/nV48z5uXfJH2DIGim4eRSldd02C.jpg',NULL,'The President sends Frank to St. Louis to persuade Raymond Tusk into becoming the new Vice President. Zoe and Janine investigate Peter Russo\'s death.'),(13,1,13,'Chapter 13','/vsuWBB8cF18VKfCAIei1htFGKkf.jpg',NULL,'Frank scrambles to keep his plan on track. Gillian is planning to sue Claire. Zoe, Janine, and Lucas investigate Rachel Posner and her relationship with Peter Russo.'),(14,2,1,'Chapter 14','/z91LQoFwhVcpeu3bZAQVIQ8B7kS.jpg',NULL,'The Underwoods tackle two threats that could bring their plans to ruin. Francis grooms his replacement as Whip. Claire goes on the offensive.'),(15,2,2,'Chapter 15','/3CTVNSqSBE6wl2MTd0kCLPpfzeO.jpg',NULL,'Amid turmoil in the home, Frank takes office. Foreign relations become entangled as Durant\'s team bungles a meeting. As foes negotiate to thwart her, Jackie maneuvers to strengthen her position. Lucas acquires new skills in order to pursue his secret investigation.'),(16,2,3,'Chapter 16','/rXXh4m1daaLSC6p5iVDrljnkUKT.jpg',NULL,'Tension rises between Francis and Raymond Tusk as the situation with China deteriorates. A battle in the Senate pits Francis against the Republicans.'),(17,2,4,'Chapter 17','/lPprjEmxdRE2nNQy1AzG8tFEAh1.jpg',NULL,'A terror scare at the Capitol traps Francis with a resentful Donald Blythe. Claire gives a live interview that rocks the media.'),(18,2,5,'Chapter 18','/3d9v7vXp1e9EoVKB3mwZc3mXBih.jpg',NULL,'Francis back-channels with a Chinese billionaire. Lucas uses extreme measures to expose the Vice President. A shadowy figure joins Team Underwood.'),(19,2,6,'Chapter 19','/mtgMfDZ6ljzYMIqzaojoZTzhKol.jpg',NULL,'Amidst an energy crisis, Francis and Tusk end their shaky alliance. Lucas must make a difficult choice. Stamper grows closer to Rachel.'),(20,2,7,'Chapter 20','/ic09rdouhfHbbxb7tQNaDeRwhgY.jpg',NULL,'Despite some friction, the Walkers deepen their friendship with the Underwoods. But it\'s all-out war between Francis and Tusk.'),(21,2,8,'Chapter 21','/7rvGPOhfKWOUSQRl96OGtE0SmWh.jpg',NULL,'The war with Tusk intensifies. Claire influences Tricia Walker politically and domestically. Francis has a show-down with Linda Vasquez.'),(22,2,9,'Chapter 22','/nLfMbhVy4iucq2fUN039roQfUOd.jpg',NULL,'Things get personal when Tusk blindsides the Underwoods with a scandal. Freddy and his BBQ joint get caught up in the mix.'),(23,2,10,'Chapter 23','/9ZSl47CVSQMmbeau7ghQdWyRk7C.jpg',NULL,'With a military stand-off overseas and potential violence at home, Francis wants to finish off Tusk for good. Claire and Jackie Sharp collide.'),(24,2,11,'Chapter 24','/grwrv79vDn0w8UrQhcBNe9kTTK7.jpg',NULL,'A Special Prosecutor interrogates Francis. Remy Danton tries to keep his options open. Stamper wrestles with his demons.'),(25,2,12,'Chapter 25','/4sTmsXEM7SMYqZg8qF9o8FRLlGG.jpg',NULL,'Francis finds himself shut out and Claire makes a difficult sacrifice. Stamper tries to regain control.'),(26,2,13,'Chapter 26','/eED02PqgQFR9aePrwfm5J24bfEw.jpg',NULL,'Francis faces annihilation while the nation is in an uproar. Stamper must tie up loose ends. Claire feels the cost of ruthlessness.'),(27,3,1,'Chapter 27','/uMHBlf6kYYRxGGmZhvCJQT7pNW6.jpg',NULL,'A rocky start for the Underwood Presidency. Frank wants to introduce an ambitious jobs program, while Claire sets her sights on the United Nations.'),(28,3,2,'Chapter 28','/9wF8NpqsHl1CI8Th2RVq0MLDX6f.jpg',NULL,'Claire\'s U.N. bid runs into trouble. Frank fights off mutiny with a bold address to the country.'),(29,3,3,'Chapter 29','/394ReRMqzcX2CN0NAPq6SLci9qp.jpg',NULL,'The Russian president\'s state visit becomes a cold war of wills, and some punks heat things up.'),(30,3,4,'Chapter 30','/P3fbW8FKj2UrJYv3jtiYrQg63D.jpg',NULL,'Claire bypasses Russia at the U.N. Frank tries to outmaneuver a potential challenger and ends up face to face with a higher power.'),(31,3,5,'Chapter 31','/4n2b5xWMdRqwF42dWHvx1AlhY6p.jpg',NULL,'Frank declares war on Congress to jump-start his jobs program. Claire spars with the Russian Ambassador.'),(32,3,6,'Chapter 32','/zk7ZKFzaetHCpj1fN96PYXnJ8E1.jpg',NULL,'Frank and Claire travel to Moscow to negotiate the return of an imprisoned U.S. citizen. Claire takes a stand that jeopardizes their plans.'),(33,3,7,'Chapter 33','/wyYtFGv8athHOkadbrD4kfr3J48.jpg',NULL,'The damage is done and the Underwoods must repair it. But deep wounds don\'t heal fast, and sometimes not at all.'),(34,3,8,'Chapter 34','/wQmxJCDMDb85IRmxk9ilkvOY7XS.jpg',NULL,'A hurricane endangers more than just the entire East Coast and Frank must make a difficult choice.'),(35,3,9,'Chapter 35','/pCNZMCI3J51O2HfJdjk81ctihSO.jpg',NULL,'The Jordan Valley erupts in chaos as Frank\'s campaign is picking up steam. Claire gets distrubing intel and counsels him.'),(36,3,10,'Chapter 36','/hQWoj3JHqfAcUl3EX6WutF8Rj9f.jpg',NULL,'Frank needs to deal with Petrov one on one while Claire tries to preserve the peace-keeping mission. Sacrifices must be made.'),(37,3,11,'Chapter 37','/n32TwwAv6Tplb3AsHz4dA0KUSAD.jpg',NULL,'Things turn ugly when Frank, Jackie, and Heather square off during their first debate. Tom joins Claire on the campaign trail.'),(38,3,12,'Chapter 38','/uj78KJ8K9SyMYgSMdxCFhky1pqm.jpg',NULL,'Heather Dunbar goes for the jugular, forcing Claire to confront her worst fears. The rift between Frank and Claire widens.'),(39,3,13,'Chapter 39','/s9TwFkEx8arMPwalN3wKs8Rx7N5.jpg',NULL,'In the midst of the Iowa caucuses, Frank and Claire must confront hard truths about each other.'),(40,4,1,'Chapter 40','/cYFDcXovJN8PA8I9mWRnsGCrHND.jpg',NULL,'Claire\'s absence causes problems for Frank on the campaign trail amid rumors of a marital rift. Claire tries to strike out on her own.'),(41,4,2,'Chapter 41','/kLB9Qv4iTYCewVf6F38ISmU633z.jpg',NULL,'As Claire begins exploring a campaign of her own, she and Frank engage in backdoor political maneuvering. But this time they\'re not on the same side.'),(42,4,3,'Chapter 42','/xodFyCDBVa4zjzEf37poflRSk4N.jpg',NULL,'Claire joins Frank as he stumps in South Carolina, but he doesn\'t trust her. A disastrous scandal blindsides Frank\'s campaign on primary day.'),(43,4,4,'Chapter 43','/qq8upbp6c7wCYPMXGK7J2uJouQA.jpg',NULL,'Claire threatens Frank. Frank makes a politically bold move that may provoke Russia. An event at a campaign stop changes everything.'),(44,4,5,'Chapter 44','/fuQLG08nhwpH9doMadv4ly5Ccg5.jpg',NULL,'Claire advises Donald Blythe on dealing with Petrov. Further investigations of Lucas Goodwin dredges up his accusations against Frank.'),(45,4,6,'Chapter 45','/zN2DH6xZdy3QBFfAlXYabyuQlzi.jpg',NULL,'Claire clashes with the Secretary of State over her involvement in negotiations with Russia. Dunbar must choose between her campaign and her ethics.'),(46,4,7,'Chapter 46','/A8PGgUxcCUUtXYMH3RiLhWRumLX.jpg',NULL,'Frank and Claire adjust to their new reality. The search for Frank\'s running mate begins. Frank starts a campaign to weaken Conway\'s strong support.'),(47,4,8,'Chapter 47','/A89VnVtJyD8NxdgYGwP0Nyw1zAv.jpg',NULL,'Formidable as ever, both Underwoods have their eyes on the big picture as they manipulate a potential running mate and push the gun bill.'),(48,4,9,'Chapter 48','/al9EvPl9huoVdAnTlYj9RlNAr4E.jpg',NULL,'At the convention, Frank and his team publicly push for Catherine Durant to be chosen as his running mate, but privately pursue a different agenda.'),(49,4,10,'Chapter 49','/pLarLmlsGWE0kgK7UWB2z3NCPl7.jpg',NULL,'As Frank deals with a new threat to his candidacy, Claire has doubts about their plan. Claire faces a difficult decision concerning her mother.'),(50,4,11,'Chapter 50','/2yqQTueyjgqW3khdVXuV9CtEWif.jpg',NULL,'Frank ups the ante on the war on terror to counter Conway\'s public show of strength. Tom joins Claire on the campaign trail.'),(51,4,12,'Chapter 51','/wcJuWSQ6kKNwHJAZgoczDXjX4lS.jpg',NULL,'Frank asks Will to help deal with extremists threatening to murder hostages. Hammerschmidt digs deeper into the allegations against Frank.'),(52,4,13,'Chapter 52','/6DOYZ0Fprg4TA1xGwRJ5gDPB07G.jpg',NULL,'As the hostage situation continues, Claire secretly negotiates with Yusuf al Ahmadi. Frank confronts Hammerschmidt.'),(53,5,1,'Chapter 53','/1Xn58CmmTOHnzxOUK1VvuoyYrjR.jpg',NULL,'As Congress debates investigating Frank, he and Claire attempt to stoke fear of terrorism. Tom Yates continues his stay in the White House.'),(54,5,2,'Chapter 54','/kXDHOaaJfZGITHckOvtiXAhNogm.jpg',NULL,'Frank and his team work to leverage support in key states by any means necessary. Claire learns some upsetting news about one of Frank\'s friends.'),(55,5,3,'Chapter 55','/A3SE9uT3RmdCUibnWU9LOkf9eB3.jpg',NULL,'The day before the election, Conway holds a 24-hour Skype session with voters, while Frank and Claire stump in key states and try to discredit him.'),(56,5,4,'Chapter 56','/fpDX6Z3ZP8FWMJsjsN1i1G1Hw41.jpg',NULL,'With a tight race and low voter turnout on Election Day, things look grim for Frank. But he\'s still got one more trick up his sleeve.'),(57,5,5,'Chapter 57','/pfFo1NJCKnoSugAgwqvjsRteX4t.jpg',NULL,'Nine weeks after Election Day, the Underwoods work to consolidate their power. Leann tries to track down a missing Aidan Macallan.'),(58,5,6,'Chapter 58','/jTry9NWJOrF33vBjJTmnmMHvDNZ.jpg',NULL,'In the midst of uncertainty, suspected Russian forces take over an American station in Antarctica. Meanwhile, a damaging news leak could hurt Frank.'),(59,5,7,'Chapter 59','/1Qf2vfDj2DVdAnexu6PMNsUji1e.jpg',NULL,'When a crisis forces White House personnel to take shelter in a bunker, Commerce Department official Jane Davis negotiates through back channels.'),(60,5,8,'Chapter 60','/iF36sfyjNGzVWBBMZ16hmOcWe8C.jpg',NULL,'While Frank attends an elite men\'s weekend gathering to firm up support, Claire deals with a stranded Russian ship and threats from Petrov.'),(61,5,9,'Chapter 61','/8MOQrYJzzq7kflbQibWCaPPm370.jpg',NULL,'Petrov tries to influence affairs in the U.S. Jane discusses her agenda with Claire. With her job at stake, Leann reaches out to a reporter for help.'),(62,5,10,'Chapter 62','/xFY41KgBD9tgrp9uXzWbQiXqamv.jpg',NULL,'The Underwoods and their team angle to undermine the revived committee investigating Frank. Hammerschmidt\'s investigation heats up.'),(63,5,11,'Chapter 63','/fFFuFSpMuAJKmYyjyWZq7X2By9G.jpg',NULL,'As the team tries to control fallout from damaging testimony and leaks, everyone is under suspicion and tensions flare between Frank and Claire.'),(64,5,12,'Chapter 64','/8QTtCMqMY5u9CMFNrTYSBlWgrNV.jpg',NULL,'Frank attempts to stop Cathy from testifying. With Hammerschmidt sniffing out the truth, the Underwoods throw someone close to them under the bus.'),(65,5,13,'Chapter 65','/mbQqlUn5sAggVOM4WdWEN060RaI.jpg',NULL,'In the wake of a surprising announcement, everything at the White House is shaken up. A decision must be made about whether to go to war.'),(66,6,1,'Chapter 66',NULL,NULL,''),(67,6,2,'Chapter 67',NULL,NULL,''),(68,6,3,'Chapter 68',NULL,NULL,''),(69,6,4,'Chapter 69',NULL,NULL,''),(70,6,5,'Chapter 70',NULL,NULL,'');
