INSERT INTO `jessica_jones` VALUES (1,1,1,'AKA Ladies Night','/8sdMBGwHYW7UWrPv8c39w7VHj83.jpg','80002312','Jessica Jones is hired to find a pretty NYU student who\'s vanished, but it turns out to be more than a simple missing persons case.'),(2,1,2,'AKA Crush Syndrome','/mmZXXJAEuDfid42mFotL3PGes41.jpg','80002313','Jessica vows to prove Hope\'s innocence, even though it means tracking down a terrifying figure from her own past.'),(3,1,3,'AKA It\'s Called Whiskey','/ynaolUGV5E3Cr0zxTb4UVQGVzIq.jpg','80002314','It won\'t be easy to acquire or deploy, but Jessica thinks she\'s found a weapon to use against Kilgrave. Luke and Jessica bond over their similarities.'),(4,1,4,'AKA 99 Friends','/8IjT1LCsvbfwTIkAtQNmlNgBenS.jpg','80002315','A new case demands attention as Jessica tries to find out who\'s spying on her for Kilgrave. Trish\'s radio show yields unexpected consequences.'),(5,1,5,'AKA The Sandwich Saved Me','/fmHRLGaCSTqBmwXZyEe9rhrTmfk.jpg','80002316','Despite Jessica\'s objections, Trish\'s new friend Simpson gets involved in the hunt for Kilgrave. Jessica recalls a pivotal moment in her life.'),(6,1,6,'AKA You\'re a Winner','/6KZu2xbcDZ6SZmhMCH64s0ZhCw4.jpg','80002317','Luke hires Jessica to help him find someone who may have skipped town, but she fears he\'ll learn too much about her history in the process.'),(7,1,7,'AKA Top Shelf Perverts','/d1Xk3ptFt8UYDBwgnqOJDyC23QV.jpg','80002318','Malcolm, Simpson and Trish go rouge to prevent Jessica from carrying out an extreme plan to outwit Kilgrave.'),(8,1,8,'AKA WWJD?','/x9k5ZuGjFQkI8y4bi1BNqtMnsQW.jpg','80002319','Jessica experiences a strange homecoming courtesy of Kilgrave. Hograth\'s conflict with her estranged wife reaches a tipping point.'),(9,1,9,'AKA Sin Bin','/rjRBAIoTWrbHbtBhBsLNtEzcz6J.jpg','80002320','Just when Jessica has Kilgrave right where she want\'s him, Hogarth\'s involvement complicates the situation. Details of Kilgrave\'s past emerge.'),(10,1,10,'AKA 1,000 Cuts','/xGb7NMYU5nAJhhbiRcZvl6qdjwJ.jpg','80002321','A discovery has the potential to change the entire game - if Jessica can refuse Kilgrave\'s offer.'),(11,1,11,'AKA I\'ve Got the Blues','/pWPXYgGnomxq0RSzjx75Wfitc76.jpg','80002322','Jessica searches morgues for clues. Trish goes all out to keep Simpson from getting in Jessica\'s way. Malcolm has an epiphany.'),(12,1,12,'AKA Take a Bloody Number','/2ltE326GvaUX6CkJAVcbio8MI0X.jpg','80002323','The hunt for Kilgrave reunites Jessica with Luke. Trish receives some unexpected information about Simpson and Jessica.'),(13,1,13,'AKA Smile','/nZytqi8HD2V0anKbAvNox9tAl5.jpg','80002324','Jessica and Luke get help from someone else in the neighborhood. Kilgrave gears up for a major test of powers against Jessica.'),(14,2,1,'AKA Start at the Beginning','/xgjcf62NYV7VzIYHJ5VlznbrWei.jpg',NULL,'While Jessica deals with a rival PI and a paranoid would-be client, Trish digs up a medical file that could unlock the mystery of Jessica\'s powers.'),(15,2,2,'AKA Freak Accident','/5JNL4bi0giB1dO6K0GcUxdWZ1aO.jpg','80130315','Jessica sets out to find Dr. Kozlov and makes a startling discovery. Trish recruits Malcolm for backup as she visits a figure from her past.'),(16,2,3,'AKA Sole Survivor','/8ZMOfOzv50HBXJRCuMSlupalSSq.jpg','80130316','As her visions intensify, Jessica visits an abandoned clinic, where she stumbles on a new lead. Jeri faces an ultimatum after her secret gets out.'),(17,2,4,'AKA God Help the Hobo','/ppf0YxTYXyPc69jNrO4xGPHUTqk.jpg','80130317','Between anger management classes and tabloid scandals, Jessica and Trish track down a third patient linked to IGH. Oscar extends an olive branch.'),(18,2,5,'AKA The Octopus','/q5O8qr6LJ1LUP3qc49la4fxW2lD.jpg','80130318','Backed into a corner, Jessica\'s forced to share her intel on the killer. A groggy Trish tries to pull herself together before an important meeting.'),(19,2,6,'AKA Facetime','/vGJADxZ7A3UvlFrogXpEXcNfwON.jpg','80130319','Jessica gate-crashes an exclusive country club on the hunt for the killer, and Trish\'s new addiction begins to spiral out of control.'),(20,2,7,'AKA I Want Your Cray Cray','/vs7y0higBxwtF4DINrNjBeKCvnr.jpg','80130320','Flashbacks shed new light on the aftermath of the family\'s car accident and reveal a painful turning point in Jessica\'s adult life.'),(21,2,8,'AKA Ain\'t We Got Fun','/nP4YQOfh1M8m3eHMuuwZpZLPPCm.jpg','80130321','While Jessica debates her next move, Malcolm confronts Trish about her erratic behavior, and Jeri makes contact with a healer.'),(22,2,9,'AKA Shark in the Bathtub, Monster in the Bed','/o0mFBCyMHGPYQCX3gIaomjXnlI6.jpg','80130322','The shooting forces Jessica to rethink her plans. Meanwhile, Oscar asks for help with a family crisis, and Trish\'s frustrations finally boil over.'),(23,2,10,'AKA Pork Chop','/lMUnNsQEA0VbpMYKc2SLMBZYf6c.jpg','80130323','Jeri finagles a deal for her new client in exchange for Karl\'s location. Trish forges ahead with her own investigation. A prison guard crosses a line.'),(24,2,11,'AKA Three Lives and Counting','/nt4LIayfHu7UPoGlfDLeVoBAqYi.jpg','80130324','Shocked by her own actions and haunted by visions of Kilgrave, Jessica worries she\'s turning into a monster. Trish\'s plans for Karl become clear.'),(25,2,12,'AKA Pray for My Patsy','/gN2baqZ7XYkDmClQMdR8kG3IXXN.jpg','80130325','As Jessica and Dorothy wait anxiously for updates on Trish, a call from Costa brings alarming news. Jeri hatches a plan to get her revenge.'),(26,2,13,'AKA Playland','/ko7tbYxiiDcWZcbmBfdPoPqS4Qy.jpg','80130326','Waking up in unfamiliar surroundings, Jessica once again finds herself torn between two worlds and facing an impossible choice.');
