nce of a planned mass casualty event in the city. As the SVU works with the joint-terrorism task force to find the suspects and the motive, Lt. Benson must also convince Barba to address allegations of rape and torture the boy\'s mother discloses.'),(391,18,2,'Making a Rapist','/7x43jgB6ecD5ifddgjYy4gK1dRT.jpg',NULL,'Newly tested DNA evidence leads to the exoneration of a prisoner who served 16 years for a rape conviction.  However, he\'s investigated again one day later in the wake of a shocking new crime.'),(392,18,3,'Imposter','/nFWKe1IAtDb4nI9G32rWWbzqVod.jpg',NULL,'When a man uses a false identity to lure a vulnerable married woman to bed, Barba thinks the evidence amounts to rape.'),(393,18,4,'Heightened Emotions','/2ArfUW5tU4OmMHbchAVkXvB9SkD.jpg',NULL,'A sexually assaulted athlete\'s double life could destroy her Olympic career and ruin the case against her attacker; Rollins sister is released from prison on parole.'),(394,18,5,'Rape Interrupted','/zt9Qb2W2Cy0QD1RU6u3rLJhalnZ.jpg',NULL,'A sergeant makes Benson choose between loyalty and duty when his son is accused of rape.'),(395,18,6,'Broken Rhymes','/dkbV8kTBm1iQUbaF3Q6cE8AZlRf.jpg',NULL,'A record label CEO and his protégé are questioned for their involvement in the assault of a transgender student.'),(396,18,7,'Next Chapter','/9t9BTDcaBEIPf9eMD0EWFk099TK.jpg',NULL,'The SVU team investigates a woman has been sexually assaulted by a masked man, but she believes the rapist is the same man who went to jail for stalking her. Meanwhile, Tucker contemplates retirement and a future with Benson.'),(397,18,8,'Chasing Theo','/yf4UR73vonklnVhbVq2vteCq186.jpg',NULL,'A 6 year-old boy disappears from his bed in the midst of a wild, drug-fueled party thrown by his mother. With a child\'s life on the line, the case causes Benson to scrutinize her own role as a mother.'),(398,18,9,'Decline and Fall','/7TspyMkIqjPGdCYxj4lQJZ9eKLh.jpg',NULL,'The powerful family of a retail empire closes ranks when a bartender accuses one of their own of rape.'),(399,18,10,'Motherly Love','/nR9YeinQLBIuLQBJ0juNEiUMoCO.jpg',NULL,'In the series 400th episode, a teenaged boy uses a rifle to stop an assault on his mother, but soon learns the target was someone he knows.'),(400,18,11,'Great Expectations','/xhuZOIu1ykp6VPgulV4A0jmzlAN.jpg',NULL,'The SVU investigates the players of a top youth hockey team after a vicious locker room hazing.'),(401,18,12,'No Surrender','/rGarFDxXRoKjr7BGp4QkBr1VHyE.jpg',NULL,'Fin revisits his military roots when a fellow Army Ranger struggles to recover from a sexual assault.'),(402,18,13,'Genes','/2Uq4oAsD11lG4Tv2MuGa8S1XMjL.jpg',NULL,'An investigation hits a nerve with Benson when a suspect claims his genetics causes him to commit rape.'),(403,18,14,'Net Worth','/vD2wcIgnTfK292RbKJgWRoKGKJO.jpg',NULL,'A top-level investment banker accuses her billionaire client of rape.'),(404,18,15,'Know It All','/hWb6Iopawxb0kKegVK9C1xkvroA.jpg',NULL,'A man under investigation for rape and murder threatens to expose the secrets of those working the case.'),(405,18,16,'The Newsroom','/6hSgDgjlkNf5Qlz8R8AvzlCg2K4.jpg',NULL,'Benson and Barba ask witnesses to put their jobs on the line after a news anchor makes an on-air disclosure of rape against her boss.'),(406,18,17,'Real Fake News','/8EqS8s3NiACCXmA1APAgg514M4w.jpg',NULL,'A fake news story leads the squad to a real child sex trafficking ring.'),(407,18,18,'Spellbound','/imcCPor3oPOHWi6UsF65JStiSgM.jpg',NULL,'A popular spiritual guru with a dark past is accused of rape.'),(408,18,19,'Conversion','/fTLARgBcnFHHLaDUglSkBxnrNhR.jpg',NULL,'A young woman visiting NYC with her church group is raped by a friend.'),(409,18,20,'American Dream (1)','/thvQuzBqPwdDO4wvzH1FBptfAch.jpg',NULL,'A hate crime is committed against a Muslim family, resulting in the death of their daughter. Things get complicated when a crucial witness in the case is deported, forcing Barba to drop the charges against a suspect.'),(410,18,21,'Sanctuary (2)','/wEdQ4a8p3jZZ355svuEClF5i2FS.jpg',NULL,'In the 18th-season finale, two families seek justice for their loved ones in the wake of a suspect\'s unexpected release. Soon, public protests on the matter escalate to violence, leading Benson to go to desperate lengths to make an arrest.'),(411,19,1,'Gone Fishin\'','/lnT8ggMw7d6OzARcc59jQdKaqk3.jpg',NULL,'Fin\'s decision to capture a fugitive rapist in a foreign country creates political complications for Barba\'s case, and an old friend returns with a shocking allegation against Benson.'),(412,19,2,'Mood','/ArGthbfgHWvXIw3Cpju3GXpqbBR.jpg',NULL,'The bizarre details of a woman\'s rape put the SVU at odds when Rollins and Carisi think her story is fabricated. Meanwhile, Benson goes on the offensive when her personal life is scrutinized.'),(413,19,3,'Contrapasso','/yn8UPXETlwZEDCUlP9sDDf4gY7T.jpg',NULL,'When a man is found castrated and left for dead, Rollins and Carisi uncover three female suspects with possible motives. Meanwhile, Langan brings devastating news for Benson.'),(414,19,4,'No Good Reason','/eDedMRZusAojemkKiCGlNQyyoSQ.jpg',NULL,'A teenager disappears after schoolmates make her the subject of a vicious cyberbullying attack.'),(415,19,5,'Complicated','/eMX3Ivc9n10U0r6vZqlvWh9w3lS.jpg',NULL,'A 10-year-old kidnapping case is reopened when a young woman is found wandering Central Park alone. Meanwhile, Carisi’s conversation with a newspaper reporter puts him in hot water.'),(416,19,6,'Unintended Consequences','/5XGCtOJaZIDEHScBzkycYwJfPTM.jpg',NULL,'When a teenaged girl is found dead, Rollins goes undercover at a high-end rehab center where the victim was last seen alive. Meanwhile, Benson tries to overcome her doubts about Sheila.'),(417,19,7,'Something Happened','/en1JOQmfmvBdkHDyKeISDGP14k3.jpg',NULL,'Benson must disclose the secrets of her past to help a rape victim recall the details of one terrible, traumatic night.'),(418,19,8,'Intent','/5TBn1AEgB42npUmG2xaPd9cmaP.jpg',NULL,'The cops get tangled in an elaborate online hoax that leads to the rape of a popular social media star; Benson sets firm ground rules with Sheila.'),(419,19,9,'Gone Baby Gone','/2wOdFRescKy2hAno8cwVKFto9PX.jpg',NULL,'Emotions run high as the SVU squad embarks on a frantic search for Benson’s missing son.'),(420,19,10,'Pathological','/uKHtG61SHFxoIGeNv5nSJZ4BVEW.jpg',NULL,'When the SVU investigates a case involving two students in a special needs school, Rollins discovers that one child\'s medical issues stem from a surprising source.'),(421,19,11,'Flight Risk','/z18EaPRs22W8lEBzu11NStM7rj.jpg',NULL,'When an airline pilot accuses her captain of sexual assault, Barba convenes a Grand Jury to determine their employer\'s complicity in the crime. Meanwhile, Fin takes steps to ensure Benson is protected at work.'),(422,19,12,'Info Wars','/xjPXsWmvSHDDhKNWqXOZTSSSh4A.jpg',NULL,'After a female pundit is assaulted during a protest, Benson and Barba struggle to put their political beliefs aside in order to help bring the attacker to justice.'),(423,19,13,'The Undiscovered Country','/vkqFdMhKCQCCkaBVuj4eLmEEZ4O.jpg',NULL,'When an infant goes missing, the SVU finds themselves taking sides in a family’s right-to-die court case. Meanwhile, Barba’s interference in the case puts the entire DA’s office in jeopardy.'),(424,19,14,'Chasing Demons','/sgigTDvbocdcOTfCTED6p13nwA0.jpg',NULL,'A doctor arrested for sexually abusing his patients is set free after Cassidy\'s testimony causes a mistrial.'),(425,19,15,'In Loco Parentis','/emG8Hu9gcUNlSlESztcvQURaTsJ.jpg',NULL,'Carisi opens a police investigation when his niece reports a classmate for sexual assault, and Stone learns there are no perfect witnesses when it comes to sex crimes.'),(426,19,16,'Dare','/f9WA6TDsipYFEAfayi0SIVEbgcY.jpg',NULL,'A girl\'s tragic death becomes a criminal case when a surgeon harvests her organs without parental consent.'),(427,19,17,'Send In the Clowns','/1e3p0pVgrvpKhjR4SvqZ3IrrvdK.jpg',NULL,'When a student disappears during a school trip to New York City, the cops race to find a mysterious masked man. Meanwhile, Fin and Stone both get visits from family.'),(428,19,18,'Service','/w10oWc7yuCwzNMzllhx0ENpYJmT.jpg',NULL,'The SVU must break through military red tape when a soldier is suspected of sexual assault. Starring Mariska Hargitay, Ice T, Kelli Giddish, Peter Scanavino and Philip Winchester.'),(429,19,19,'Sunk Cost Fallacy','/f6vPFArZfv7rgHyFt8pkFdrqn1F.jpg',NULL,'The search for an abducted woman and her young daughter leads Lt. Benson to cross paths with an old friend. Meanwhile, Stone must make a tough decision on behalf of his sister.'),(430,19,20,'The Book of Esther','/udi1cWsXHtOFiSf2yyAQOPuxaLD.jpg',NULL,'Rollins races to rescue a girl being held captive by her father.'),(431,19,21,'Guardian','/nJjQ2AcIb0PH6oSYVLsSDDIXzSD.jpg',NULL,'Fin investigates a man\'s claim that his sister was gang raped.'),(432,19,22,'Mama','/cySk599zC78eRZRujWNqBkB9mrA.jpg',NULL,'An Alzheimer\'s patient claims she was raped, but her illness casts doubt on the case. Meanwhile, Fin\'s sergeant orders come in. have been raped, her mental state brings her allegation into question.'),(433,19,23,'Remember Me','/pIpAneu8gBd2IkRYxg30KX9uL1B.jpg',NULL,'When a young woman takes a man hostage at gunpoint, Benson makes a dangerous attempt to defuse the situation. Meanwhile, the SVU discovers the shocking motive behind the abduction.'),(434,19,24,'Remember Me Too','/cH26yIWcCZCZarP5bkES94FQMPF.jpg',NULL,'In the conclusion of a 2-part season finale, Lieutenant Benson\'s suspicions about a kidnapping victim uncover a dangerous criminal network prepared to silence anyone who gets in their way.'),(435,20,1,'Man Up','/hfi2FHX17HuQ09wKsB3NwQbPfIC.jpg',NULL,'Teenager Sam Conway shows evidence of rape but refuses to name his attacker. Meanwhile, Benson and Rollins confess to some major life changes.'),(436,20,2,'Man Down','/aHAyVkQghaWnu6gIwD3PO6q4hIq.jpg',NULL,'In the conclusion to the season premiere, ADA Stone blames himself for the shocking verdict in Sam\'s case, and before Benson can offer help, Sam makes a tragic decision.'),(437,20,3,'Zero Tolerance',NULL,NULL,'After the rescue of a young girl from a sex trafficker, Benson and Stone must take drastic measures to reunite her with her mother. Meanwhile, Rollins decides to give her rocky relationship another chance.');
