INSERT INTO `master_of_none` VALUES (1,1,1,'Plan B','/701LIEKTJFN96RzrJCiXVFgabqW.jpg','80065723','A condom mishap and a kid\'s birthday party prompt Dev to consider the reality of having children.'),(2,1,2,'Parents','/boH8x8MzLk7kzsErilY9xH9PHDI.jpg','80065724','First-generationers Dev and Brian try to show their appreciation for their immigrant parents at a joint family dinner.'),(3,1,3,'Hot Ticket','/qBw5rJmCAVd8TkgS8ozGqMFEbGp.jpg','80065725','Dev\'s plan to score a date with a pretty waitress by inviting her to a concert doesn\'t have quite the result he wanted.'),(4,1,4,'Indians on TV','/gWVduw8wbsLqNx3kwcXPq5ZDN2v.jpg','80065730','Dev has a series of eye-opening experiences after he encounters some casual racism in TV auditions.'),(5,1,5,'The Other Man','/4wFm8JFJdzQFGPSV8DxtwP3RfJV.jpg','80065726','Dev has the chance to hook up with a woman he meets at a party, but the opportunity comes with a few complications.'),(6,1,6,'Nashville','/7hnvCTLPYDo7WvCCyULNuijHo7a.jpg','80065727','For his first official date with Rachel, Dev decides to go big and take her to Nashville for the weekend.'),(7,1,7,'Ladies & Gentlemen','/7v5t7NLiXUATGQipA5HJWdt7UNz.jpg','80065728','Rachel and Denise school Dev and Arnold about the difficulties of being a woman in a world of creepy dudes. Dev is inspired to embrace feminism.'),(8,1,8,'Old People','/6YTNk2lMrwcCk7Hvsf75mam9pWz.jpg','80065729','An unexpected death inspires Dev and Rachel to visit Rachel\'s grandmother, while Arnold contends with a strange inheritance.'),(9,1,9,'Mornings','/jNhysNohq3UrmiD2SREKJROf53N.jpg','80065730','Dev and Rachel discover that living together isn\'t always going to be a series of happy mornings free from conflict and dirty clothes on the floor.'),(10,1,10,'Finale','/tiNKLTPya6ZkopDbHg3l1XNCL3p.jpg','80065732','After attending a wedding and a movie premiere, Dev and Rachel have to face up to all kinds of issues between them.'),(11,2,1,'The Thief','/9cZotTzgzKTW27q0rsjqOFQDNiF.jpg','80124247','While studying pasta making in Italy, Dev makes a serendipitous connection on his birthday, only to have his plans upended by a thief.'),(12,2,2,'Le Nozze','/5GEYvSL3plASOIBsCdZPyEForGA.jpg','80124248','Arnold stops by on his way to a wedding to explore Modena with his Little Bud. But he hasn\'t told Dev the whole truth about his trip.'),(13,2,3,'Religion','/i0bwdWVIfAOVusZVWZKZJOWjEgB.jpg','80124249','Back in New York, a visit from observant Muslim relatives puts Dev in a tricky position. He introduces his cousin to a forbidden pleasure: pork.'),(14,2,4,'First Date','/mB7SXYS6gLRgMYR4HJeIC5PDQBD.jpg','80124250','Sucked into a popular dating app, Dev winds up on a string of awkward, fun and disorienting dates with very different women.'),(15,2,5,'The Dinner Party','/wF04eVuYZEBzTr72ba1kHXdVH7e.jpg','80124251','After welcoming the Jabbawockeez to his show, Dev struggles to find the right date to take to a dinner party thrown by his celebrity chef boss.'),(16,2,6,'New York, I Love You','/U27wIc8dfOJUnxjcdG835TMWXh.jpg','80124252','As Dev and friends head to a theater to see the hit movie \"Death Castle,\" the lives of several ordinary New Yorkers intersect in subtle ways.'),(17,2,7,'Door #3','/gz8HLc4hXvIJkMMZzQW6LqLlzgH.jpg','80124253','A sweet job offer forces Dev to take stock of his priorities. Brian helps his dad with a romantic dilemma. A cupcake competition judge gets cold feet.'),(18,2,8,'Thanksgiving','/19zHMIQRQGLvDmXCuBrWWpMEPc3.jpg','80124254','Over a series of Thanksgivings from the \'90s to the present, Denise settles into her sexuality and faces the challenge of coming out to her family.'),(19,2,9,'Amarsi Un Po','/kNOKBd1Bx8kSIlVmmtOklyMPdzi.jpg','80124255','When Francesca returns to New York for a month, Dev plays tour guide and finds himself caught in a whirlwind of confusing emotions.'),(20,2,10,'Buona Notte','/iLpGEsyT604SSutiXAttIz2fX1m.jpg','80065742','Just as Dev\'s personal life reaches a tipping point, disturbing revelations throw his professional life into turmoil, too.');
