INSERT INTO `narcos` VALUES (1,1,1,'Descenso','/yjzI0HIW6LCYdoT4XKJJ9Gse8ro.jpg',NULL,'Chilean drug chemist Cockroach brings his product to Colombian smuggler Pablo Escobar. DEA agent Steve Murphy joins the war on drugs in Bogota.'),(2,1,2,'The Sword of Simón Bolivar','/sjgSYABo4ugRiONcGNPYZeMKOAs.jpg',NULL,'Communist radical group M-19 makes a move against the narcos, while Murphy gets an education in Colombian law enforcement from his new partner Peña.'),(3,1,3,'The Men of Always','/qHo5EuiE7XOSIxXO5IAm0TBqN86.jpg',NULL,'Murphy encounters the depths of government corruption when he and Peña try to derail Escobar\'s political ambitions by proving he\'s a narco.'),(4,1,4,'The Palace in Flames','/6iV6dwdvYdEAeDXlgxGE2GN8bXQ.jpg',NULL,'Despite a new extradition treaty, the U.S. puts more money into fighting communism, creating new challenges for Murphy and Peña in the hunt for Pablo.'),(5,1,5,'There Will Be a Future','/bNVLra8arB4RjgmR6oPgifdKurc.jpg',NULL,'Pablo\'s extreme methods put the narcos on the brink of war with Carillo and  the government. Peña tries to protect his witness, Elisa.'),(6,1,6,'Explosivos','/zp9M06o1Q0fF3TswJyW1Gx72OeY.jpg',NULL,'Peña and Carillo close in on Gacha, while Murphy tries to protect pro-extradition candidate Gaviria from a notorious assassin connected to Pablo.'),(7,1,7,'You Will Cry Tears of Blood','/jciaP4kjTPJWGa1VCYFfwjkJt9p.jpg',NULL,'Pablo goes into hiding as the political tide turns against him, but he finds a way to strike back. Murphy and Peña finally get the CIA to help them.'),(8,1,8,'La Gran Mentira','/3Aet2wEAp3mFe6yKDN0GNwBmEEB.jpg',NULL,'A tragic mistake forces the government to change tactics in the fight against Pablo. But Pablo faces bigger threats from inside his empire.'),(9,1,9,'La Catedral','/92LZMtfuqiO8CQ26XhjCE74cG8z.jpg',NULL,'The hunt for Pablo seems to be over after he makes a deal with the government, but Murphy and Peña -- and the Cali Cartel -- have other plans.'),(10,1,10,'Despegue','/e8G5TXOzZC1QQSZcwm6VVLFZ1e1.jpg',NULL,'Pablo\'s activities in prison provoke the government into taking extreme action. Murphy and Peña face a situation of their own.'),(11,2,1,'Free at Last','/eOmlCz0pM6OArw9lt9HdHmEp6Q9.jpg',NULL,'In the aftermath of a massive military effort to take Pablo into custody, the family reunites while enemies worry. Steve and Connie fight about safety.'),(12,2,2,'Cambalache','/nRWoMAoJkfYGIlFnthH75a7zFoU.jpg',NULL,'Tata gets impatient with life on the run. Pablo responds to President Gaviria\'s reward offer. Steve and Javier meet their new boss.'),(13,2,3,'Our Man in Madrid','/xgz7SY7MVZmUs1LuedE6lKgMZpV.jpg',NULL,'President Gaviria has a new job for an old colleague. The Search Bloc\'s new tactics shake up Pablo, but also unsettle Steve and Javier.'),(14,2,4,'The Good, The Bad, and The Dead','/zd3mcwuzgpKKxyIztG9bcQJvJw8.jpg',NULL,'The Cali cartel discusses moving in on Pablo\'s territory. Limón proposes a plan to Maritza. Tata gets a gun for protection.'),(15,2,5,'The Enemies of My Enemy','/5qLQs2PrsFXbvZkLHsnd0gy0IdI.jpg',NULL,'The Search Bloc gets a new leader. Javier loses faith in the system. Pablo brings Tata\'s brother Carlos down from Miami to cheer her up.'),(16,2,6,'Los Pepes','/yfKAmux4HeZg7ICvzcx8IyRcQwB.jpg',NULL,'The newly-formed Los Pepes want to destroy Pablo and his empire. Tata\'s brother urges her to leave and seek safety with her children.'),(17,2,7,'Deutschland 93','/5jknBVhgNb0wbuX9VlNP7ZBplE1.jpg',NULL,'As the danger intensifies for the Escobars, Pablo sends his family to another country. Gaviria weighs the opportunity to use them as leverage.'),(18,2,8,'Exit El Patrón','/crd6TR2FEyFSGbbzk3tlTMLDaKw.jpg',NULL,'Colombia begins to turn on Escobar after his latest terrorist attack. Tata receives help from an unlikely ally. Quica gets increasingly anxious.'),(19,2,9,'Neuestra Finca','/tTRAqnVgDYQcgoL854TOIvom7DQ.jpg',NULL,'Pablo is reunited with an estranged family member. Judy Moncada\'s life is put in danger. The DEA and CIA clash over how to handle Los Pepes.'),(20,2,10,'Al Fin Cayó!','/kPRmRmja7VgxjREKzgaZd86zoJI.jpg',NULL,'Javier deals with the repercussions from Judy\'s interview. Tata tries to convince Pablo to surrender for the sake of his children.'),(21,3,1,'The Kingpin Strategy','/z95whSH4GDry3Nd8CKQt23HuXCs.jpg',NULL,'The Gentlemen of Cali gather their associates together for a big surprise announcement about the future of their business.'),(22,3,2,'The Cali KGB','/6o6Otbf4QZTD9JQCgA7snZ7l21H.jpg',NULL,'A gas incident threatens to disrupt the Cali-government deal and Jorge is asked to help out. Peña grapples with his former Los Pepes connection.'),(23,3,3,'Follow the Money','/rVE1GjNKDfmUvqvxgqfmqI5n6x9.jpg',NULL,'The Rodriguez brothers go into hiding during negotiations. Pacho meets with the Lord of the Skies in Mexico. Peña\'s new DEA team visits Cali.'),(24,3,4,'Checkmate','/rCQS1j2KjQctYpRFlPeKfEdPB2M.jpg',NULL,'Peña hatches a plan to try to capture Cali leader Gilberto Rodriguez. Amado proposes a business idea to Pacho.'),(25,3,5,'MRO','/ciOP9xkilGEmhW4ZZjur9YcPapM.jpg',NULL,'Paranoid about leaks, Miguel cracks down on his security. Pacho makes a decision about his new offer. Peña works on cultivating a witness.'),(26,3,6,'Best Laid Plans','/8kWJZvSw69tfH1UCWwsMpiu6Y9I.jpg',NULL,'Jorge takes a dangerous risk. An accident in New York threatens to expose Chepe. Peña travels to Curaçao to arrest a potential witness.'),(27,3,7,'Sin Salida','/31B5A3V2zMxYKcb08OPhqqD9NHp.jpg',NULL,'Peña plans another covert operation to take down a key Cali cartel member, but he risks running out of time during his search.'),(28,3,8,'Convivir','/9mMozFa5D1w2kllinK5FZjRumvr.jpg',NULL,'David seeks revenge on behalf of his father, putting Enrique in danger. Peña asks Don Berna for help on a rescue mission.'),(29,3,9,'Todos Los Hombres del Presidente','/oZjJQveN1jEHDN4ryQfZaf39zBX.jpg',NULL,'David follows his suspicions. Peña is shocked to discover the depth of corruption in the Colombian government. Miguel is sought after once again.'),(30,3,10,'Going Back to Cali','/7h9ZhFl5ymMefSjRv5vKDsAU4jH.jpg',NULL,'David and Peña are in a race against each other to find Pallomari. Peña makes a serious decision about the future of his career.');
