aYkf5C7.jpg',NULL,'The NCIS team has to babysit a 9-year-old son of a missing man, a survivalist who is somehow connected to a cold case murder. The investigation leads the team into the wilderness, where they discover a shocking truth about the man\'s past.'),(104,5,10,'Corporal Punishment','/urv8lLKY9ZX8nwdtWxRs20YueVx.jpg',NULL,'While trying to track down a delusional and violent Marine who thinks he\'s still in Iraq, the NCIS team will learn that the man has been the subject of a secret experiment - and it comes with a high price to pay.'),(105,5,11,'Tribes','/51I6lDKZdyQr5JhOSz25JciwxK7.jpg',NULL,'After a young Muslim Marine is murdered near his Mosque, Ducky refuses to perform autopsy due to his religious beliefs, so the NCIS team tries to talk to the father of the deceased, and they send McGee to plant a bug in the Mosque, only to discover that the FBI already planted their bug.'),(106,5,12,'Stakeout','/1OZDSQ2q7OknowZAAsZpgXSgODv.jpg',NULL,'The NCIS team goes on a stakeout in a warehouse to catch a suspected thief of a high-tech naval radar, but they accidentally end up witnessing a murder. Meanwhile, Ducky hides a secret from the rest of the team.'),(107,5,13,'Dog Tags','/cTW8LoijebnRrRxl835dHxr1pD7.jpg',NULL,'When a dog owner is found murdered, the NCIS team must determine if his dog committed the murder or not, and Abby decides to fight for the dog\'s life by trusting her instinct about the dog\'s innocence. Meanwhile, Gibbs learns about Jenny\'s secret.'),(108,5,14,'Internal Affairs','/9qT8OYQO7DiYGeA9D7snloYJ3ek.jpg',NULL,'The dead body of La Grenouille finally surfaces and the entire NCIS is put under the investigation by the FBI, with Jenny as the prime suspect for his murder.'),(109,5,15,'In The Zone','/2w6YsPp3UqLD6pjYjZjVOrBM3gB.jpg',NULL,'Two members of the NCIS team are sent to Baghdad to investigate a Mortar attack that turned into a murder investigation.'),(110,5,16,'Recoil','/jdzKTlafyCBw5n0dg6GdqORnscf.jpg',NULL,'While on an undercover mission, Ziva\'s life is put in grave danger when the serial killer she\'s been tracking becomes suspicious of her.'),(111,5,17,'About Face','/jfOETc4OCEHjTBkKzImN7yIKdHh.jpg',NULL,'Palmer is put in grave danger when he becomes the target of an anonymous murderer, whom only he can recognize.'),(112,5,18,'Judgment Day (1)','/o16JeMg9APffLA7i8VDJenLPHNs.jpg',NULL,'When a former NCIS agent is found dead, the entire team is put in danger as they hunt after the killer.'),(113,5,19,'Judgment Day (2)','/27s3yzeIFmTaP9XdAwT6vDDgfMl.jpg',NULL,'When one of their own is killed, the team must find the killer before they get to another member of the team, Gibbs. In an emotional investigation, the team tries to stay together, against the wishes of Assistant Director Vance.'),(114,6,1,'Last Man Standing','/kOwJQ0nRS3Tv92iYjPgQiu2fRTS.jpg',NULL,'When a petty officer is found murdered, Gibbs learns about the mysterious connection between the disbanding of his team and the case.'),(115,6,2,'Agent Afloat','/9X7kvMzP43607TTPiuF9I1browe.jpg',NULL,'DiNozzo\'s investigation into a Navy Lieutenant\'s apparent suicide takes a surprising and deadly turn when its seems that it might have a connection to a larger, deadly scheme.'),(116,6,3,'Capitol Offense','/5HQpkCHACOJWBb9gmLkvOmvUvb2.jpg',NULL,'A distinguished senator asks Gibbs for help in solving the murder of a young female Naval officer.'),(117,6,4,'Heartland','/ysDttbIr8PBwsVLmP6bMFbPI2Fs.jpg',NULL,'When a murder investigation leads the team to Gibbs\' hometown, secrets about his past are revealed.'),(118,6,5,'Nine Lives','/lXtUKv4d917jZ4AZVxeRaRxXcYK.jpg',NULL,'Gibbs\' hunt for the killer of a marine puts him on a collision course with an old friend.'),(119,6,6,'Murder 2.0','/n7Rl5JYgcXbZTHcTLCPnGrLIjUt.jpg',NULL,'Gibbs and his team are searching for a cyber serial killer who takes videos of his victims. The team quickly finds out that the video\'s of the dead victims are false.'),(120,6,7,'Collateral Damage','/hNZttdr51VwuN265OLrGuWeDNQK.jpg',NULL,'A Navy bank has been robbed. NCIS is responsible for the investigation. One of the new recruits assigned to the fraud unit, Special Agent Dwayne Wilson, joins the team to help.'),(121,6,8,'Cloak','/2gI7S7P08hr33UcqMQo5kzPN7TU.jpg',NULL,'A strange delivery in a box arrived at the Navy facilities: The delivery driver and a Navy MP officer discover it is a sailor\'s corpse.\n\nA shocking revelation comes to light after the team is forced into playing a dangerous war game.'),(122,6,9,'Dagger','/3TbG9mhWesSJGpTnZVkwqVXeNrE.jpg',NULL,'The team is forced to rely on information from questionable sources while trying to stop a criminal bent on stealing government secrets.'),(123,6,10,'Road Kill','/7EBa6qY0DxNKxHtG8GGJLb8fMfx.jpg',NULL,'The team investigates the death of a petty officer and discovers he may have been leading a violent secret life.'),(124,6,11,'Silent Night','/qXm0ktXApf2nR3z3FKjlx0MXHAh.jpg',NULL,'During the week of Christmas, The Team is Forced to work overtime when they discover their prime suspect had been dead for 17 years.'),(125,6,12,'Caged','/wbDrSWn59SjLbm33S2CoMLjMslr.jpg',NULL,'The NCIS team must reveal the truth behind the murder of a jail guard which resulted in a prison riot and McGee being held captive by the inmates.'),(126,6,13,'Broken Bird','/8cdQokfLusnanSReExBcELkR3mi.jpg',NULL,'Secrets from Ducky\'s clandestine past come to the forefront after he\'s attacked at a crime scene. The team uncovers disturbing secrets from the good doctor\'s past.'),(127,6,14,'Love and War','/mtpi5ak86PD3V6ARsHHXzdTOSak.jpg',NULL,'The team discovers a link between a sergeant\'s murder and his possibly treasonous private life.'),(128,6,15,'Deliverance','/7tJFgS3XPU4BBCohdqWsUwhziAE.jpg',NULL,'Demons of the past come back to haunt Gibbs when he finds a cryptic message waiting for him at a crime scene.'),(129,6,16,'Bounce','/lprn5kr9cGZkSr7kNwBEOXwl4Mz.jpg',NULL,'A murder prompts the reopening of one of Tony\'s old investigations, leading Gibbs and DiNozzo to reverse roles to solve the case.'),(130,6,17,'South by Southwest','/9TiQ9k3I6IjQ9eTzi5JByT7OJfg.jpg',NULL,'When a fellow agent is murdered, the NCIS teams heads into the desert to locate a woman who might hold the answer to the mystery murder.'),(131,6,18,'Knockout','/iEBzdURgex2xDg5DhcZiCSoS7n.jpg',NULL,'The death of a boxer leads Vance to borrow the NCIS team and start investigating his death, while Gibbs digs into Vance\'s past.'),(132,6,19,'Hide and Seek','/yyLNWOe6hHWuaErjIOEaOZ1Gz7u.jpg',NULL,'When a young boy finds a murder weapon, the team must trace ownership of the gun to find who used it last and who was murdered.'),(133,6,20,'Dead Reckoning','/pxkWIvOAC27iRLqlzJnboJzEBB.jpg',NULL,'Gibbs and the team must work with the shady Trent Kort to put away one of NCIS\'s most wanted.'),(134,6,21,'Toxic','/iNI6lCaR0g5CKkzFfLoJhkgpTbf.jpg',NULL,'When a government scientist goes missing, Abby is recruited to carry on his work, but the team worries that she may meet the same fate as her predecessor.'),(135,6,22,'Legend (1)','/z93AL1CX2rdzQ06PEiq0uTtfmCp.jpg',NULL,'The body of a Marine leads Gibbs and McGee to the NCIS OSP division in Los Angeles, where a murder investigation quickly climbs to a matter of national security in which the two offices must work together to resolve. Meanwhile, Tony begins to snoop into Ziva\'s personal life.'),(136,6,23,'Legend (2)','/vYrN9bgfkhAZBu0cObmH3b6MYSA.jpg',NULL,'With the appearance of Mossad agent Michael Rivkin, Tony is forced to question Ziva’s loyalty to NCIS. Meanwhile, in Los Angeles, Special Agent Callen goes undercover to try to catch a terrorist cell while OSP psychologist Nate Getz discovers the startling truth about Gibbs and Special Agent Lara Macy’s relationship.'),(137,6,24,'Semper Fidelis','/9AhPbuiZaYFURz7ocXhCSG3Z9GX.jpg',NULL,'After a security breach at the SecNav\'s residence leads to the death of an ICE agent, Gibbs and the team are forced to work with ICE and the FBI to find his killer. Meanwhile, Tony finally comes face-to-face with Michael Rivkin.'),(138,6,25,'Aliyah','/gTZgYUM8IZTPB0UHGaVnMCNpWdh.jpg',NULL,'Ziva\'s homecoming to Israel with Gibbs and the team is not a happy reunion with her father, the enigmatic and powerful head of Mossad. As tensions rise, Gibbs is forced to make a decision that sends shock waves through NCIS.'),(139,7,1,'Truth or Consequences','/5WZJspVtIThloQd8KTjVsvDIul9.jpg',NULL,'As the hunt for Ziva\'s replacement begins, Gibbs and his remaining team members must head back to work with the past still weighing heavily on their minds.'),(140,7,2,'Reunion','/8afO82loxMoYu51MoNBY20gTgQw.jpg',NULL,'The team discovers the bizarre death of a Marine and his two friends may be linked to their past, but its Gibbs who ends up taking a trip down memory lane.'),(141,7,3,'The Inside Man','/emRdBMFpbCgtFmMAGuOGt2pej0c.jpg',NULL,'The team must take a second look into the death of a lieutenant after the blogger who accused them of a cover-up ends up dead.'),(142,7,4,'Good Cop, Bad Cop','/e2QxPAtz8WJGyV1Ak1vkI5g6Jlj.jpg',NULL,'When a Marine\'s body surfaces halfway around the world, the investigation forces Ziva to dig up a buried chapter of her life.'),(143,7,5,'Code of Conduct','/c9r88mESch8ibUWyaicZRI8foHM.jpg',NULL,'When a Marine known for his practical jokes is found dead on Halloween Eve, the NCIS team discovers that the victim\'s \"good-natured\" pranks may have inspired ghoulish retribution. Meanwhile, Ziva tries to adjust to her new role on the team.'),(144,7,6,'Outlaws and In-Laws','/trYIp0yUP31z19jFCMXDDmke0aB.jpg',NULL,'A murder investigation prompts Gibbs and the team to play family counselor to his former mentor, Mike Franks, in the hopes of preventing a bloody international conflict.'),(145,7,7,'Endgame','/cR5pvpqOcOJREHydOVEtbAfeP3O.jpg',NULL,'With the team\'s help, Vance faces his demons while uncovering a complex relationship with a killer that puts his whole family in danger.'),(146,7,8,'Power Down','/sF8UM0Yf4ShobrevsOAWuOn4RAL.jpg',NUL