 team investigate the shooting of a Marine and uncovers more to his life than anyone would have ever imagined.'),(156,7,18,'Jurisdiction','/AbAsYOp6A12Ua32z0kmbKR3zwUe.jpg',NULL,'The team discovers striking similarities between themselves and their CGIS (Coast Guard Investigative Services) counterparts when a Navy diver seeking sunken treasure is found dead.'),(157,7,19,'Guilty Pleasure','/cbjizs6j6HhZ1sPrZnGNrQXJagk.jpg',NULL,'The death of a Navy officer leads Gibbs and the team into the world of high-priced call girls, relying on D.C. Madam Holly Snow to help them catch a killer.'),(158,7,20,'Moonlighting','/nEiBwYQ6HQ6PBsNzuJLyzoRC2a4.jpg',NULL,'When an NCIS polygraph specialist\'s night job takes a dangerous turn, Gibbs, Fornell and the team have to uncover the truth.'),(159,7,21,'Obsession','/oBu5JbYfgaPnK7oRvNpCYRIr9QM.jpg',NULL,'DiNozzo finds himself increasingly captivated by a woman he\'s never met while investigating the murder of her brother.'),(160,7,22,'Borderland','/b48DJjmAXk9cCtfWY0hBY71dgeH.jpg',NULL,'The team tries to track down a serial killer, while Abby heads south of the border to give a speech with McGee in tow.'),(161,7,23,'Patriot Down','/xpZHtMYvau4lyNhaxmgHItiM3RI.jpg',NULL,'When a colleague\'s murder sends shockwaves through the team, Gibbs uncovers a surprising link to the crime.'),(162,7,24,'Rule Fifty-One','/yIiOsgfTxNJlIX9k0Z581rj2AY3.jpg',NULL,'Gibbs heads to Mexico to face his demons and make a startling decision.'),(163,8,1,'Spider and the Fly','/jKNVBWjs2ARN8RdrCoUdSu1YGUZ.jpg',NULL,'Gibbs must take desperate measures to protect his loved ones with Paloma Reynosa still on the loose.'),(164,8,2,'Worst Nightmare','/pOsd7hK0EIG5VZhVfNppv58ZpAi.jpg',NULL,'The NCIS team has to find a young girl that was kidnapped, but their investigation turns into something else when her grandfather gets way too involved.'),(165,8,3,'Short Fuse','/iPB3COSiUFr6lmQZN7dnE6AXqRy.jpg',NULL,'The team investigates a bomb tech\'s guarded personal life after s