finds himself on a vessel that has been commandeered by pirates.'),(264,12,6,'Parental Guidance Suggested','/Andq6ZrcrfQXq5gEwxcIL406vk.jpg',NULL,'The NCIS team must determine if the murder of a Navy commander\'s wife is linked to her profession as a therapist or an act of terrorism after finding the commander\'s name on a Jihadist target list. Meanwhile, the team discusses Halloween costumes and Tony\'s recent dating habits.'),(265,12,7,'The Searchers','/eFTHZUiC4fkWxR9tQlVl81LbJg8.jpg',NULL,'After investigating the murder of a retired Master Sergeant, the NCIS team uncovers a fraudulent charity that preys on those searching for missing military personnel. Meanwhile, Bishop agonizes over the results of her probation evaluation, and Tony contemplates adopting stray cat that followed him home.'),(266,12,8,'Semper Fortis','/iWXQcDqzR2tybkgbWiF66FFBNf5.jpg',NULL,'While the NCIS team investigates the cause of a hit and run accident that resulted in the death of a Petty Officer, Gibbs searches for a way to clear a Navy Hospital Corpsman, who has served two medical tours in Afghanistan, after she\'s indicted for illegally providing medical aid to the victims of the crash, even though the surviving victims swear by her life-saving techniques.'),(267,12,9,'Grounded','/oNKBD323sP8x9LidmQzBLErPvLM.jpg',NULL,'While stuck at the Dulles airport due to inclement weather, DiNozzo, Bishop and her husband Jake work an NCIS case involving an elevated terrorist threat at Northeast airports during the Thanksgiving travel surge. Jamie Bamber guest stars.'),(268,12,10,'House Rules','/jy0XidJKXxy2L9e4KOvDE9JnIwA.jpg',NULL,'The NCIS team consults with three cyber-terrorists they imprisoned after a city-wide Internet shutdown the week before Christmas. Also, McGee reflects on the case and Gibbs\' infamous rules as he pens a heartfelt letter to his father.'),(269,12,11,'Check','/jixsKT6h1FiQdhBlySoFcRxGcuE.jpg',NULL,'The NCIS team investigates copy-cat crime scenes while Gibbs navigates two 