or group Delilah and the Department of Defense have been tracking.'),(277,12,19,'Patience','/wDNKlIu7KQ0pGczd0ZDQv7eTw4i.jpg',NULL,'The murder of a petty officer sparks a lead in a 40 year old airport bombing cold case that Gibbs and DiNozzo have been assigned to for the past two years.  Also, McGee is jealous that he was not previously briefed on the cold case.'),(278,12,20,'No Good Deed','/mEIMiEP34bMC86dkn6xnHdbA5gx.jpg',NULL,'DiNozzo is partnered with his girlfriend ATF Special Agent Zoé Keates after evidence reveals that the murder weapon in an NCIS case was originally purchased for the controversial ATF sting operation “Operation Fast and Furious.” Also, Anthony DiNozzo Sr. returns to town for a special dinner to meet his son’s girlfriend.'),(279,12,21,'Lost in Translation','/4ZdJNLwsbS30HJcfVJDr1y4ThGx.jpg',NULL,'Gibbs and Bishop travel to Afghanistan after the murder of a Marine in D.C. is linked to a terror group holding another Marine hostage overseas.  Also, DiNozzo is upset that McGee was chosen to be the new face of NCIS for all recruitment brochures,'),(280,12,22,'Troll','/pXOL9ghruQBjT1SG5NgzPm56uig.jpg',NULL,'Special Agent Ned Dorneget from NCIS cyber operations assists the team when a Navy ensign who worked in the Office of Naval Intelligence is murdered. Also, the team discovers that Jake and Gibbs have become good friends.'),(281,12,23,'The Lost Boys','/1TNTmApZT4Pr9FyT5rhKRQittwC.jpg',NULL,'The NCIS cyber case turns into a united global effort after evidence confirms “The Calling,” an international terrorist group that recruits children through the internet, has been purchasing S-bombs off the black market.'),(282,12,24,'Neverland','/r4EQ4UwbTSb3x0O5wsQ5QXPsCsz.jpg',NULL,'NCIS feverishly investigates a global terrorist group that is recruiting teens via the Internet, following a deadly bombing overseas that results in an emotional and surprising loss for the team.'),(283,13,1,'Stop the Bleeding','/nskddxxMoIE55RDAJk5zTcTDzs0.jpg',NULL,'After being shot, Gibbs fights for his life aboard a Navy hospital ship, while DiNozzo and Joanna travel to Shanghai to try and take down the Calling.'),(284,13,2,'Personal Day','/5MQkfVOuHhdXkJB1g0RuAYGvTCA.jpg',NULL,'Gibbs calls on the team to assist DEA Agent Luis Mitchell with a case that keeps going cold, but DiNozzo discovers there is more to Gibbs’ personal connection to the agent and his desire to help him succeed. Also, the team gossips about Gibbs’ new look after he replaces his standard military haircut and polo shirt for a modern cut and tailored dress shirt.'),(285,13,3,'Incognito','/k9iZl0BvOJoO1iMsLU4Mm7639KF.jpg',NULL,'After a Marine is found murdered in Quantico hours after calling Gibbs to discuss a possible case, Bishop and McGee go undercover as a married couple to run surveillance on a Marine Lieutenant and his wife.'),(286,13,4,'Double Trouble','/8CGCdVrr0noWHMzsErgxYVcRAmv.jpg',NULL,'Vance partners with Gibbs and returns to field duty when a murder case is connected to a former NCIS agent he locked up for stealing evidence.'),(287,13,5,'Lockdown','/qo0PS1f4DpjgTVCF9873TIResbR.jpg',NULL,'While visiting a pharmaceutical lab on a murder case, Abby is trapped with no communication to the outside world after armed men take over the building and hold everyone hostage.'),(288,13,6,'Viral','/fwekbpKNiVYVtTxggHdAUiZjI1t.jpg',NULL,'When a petty officer’s murder matches the M.O. of a local serial killer, the NCIS team must determine if this is the killer’s latest victim or the work of a copycat. Also, McGee and Delilah must learn to compromise before moving in together.'),(289,13,7,'16 Years','/5ZRHn7ldlnp0GD1uBWsIdk5GEwZ.jpg',NULL,'The NCIS murder case of a retired Navy Lieutenant Commander forces Ducky to reveal his participation in a secret society that solves cold cases.'),(290,13,8,'Saviors','/mNOS9Er9RrBhP85RzCcNtxDMegJ.jpg',NULL,'DiNozzo is reunited with his ex-girlfriend, Jeanne Benoit, when insurgents in Sudan attack a group of volunteer doctors, including her husband.  DiNozzo and McGee travel to the crime scene for the joint murder and kidnapping case and join the search for the missing doctors.'),(291,13,9,'Day in Court','/3teMktg1TjAgVztsxNw9vlM0TRJ.jpg',NULL,'In order to clear his name, a petty officer volunteers to be court martialed if NCIS agrees to conduct its own investigation after his murder case is dismissed due to a mishandled warrant. Also, Bishop and Jake discuss their marital problems.'),(292,13,10,'Blood Brothers','/gHN2mRym1pL56h1KnbrSvx8vsER.jpg',NULL,'The Secretary of Defense calls on NCIS to help a sailor who is battling leukemia to locate a donor for a bone marrow transplant, after two of his siblings are killed in the line of duty.  Meanwhile, Bishop returns home to Oklahoma for Thanksgiving.'),(293,13,11,'Spinning Wheel','/y6rEHwZVVum8l7G3jeKeB0UxR8n.jpg',NULL,'After Ducky is attacked by a man claiming to have information about his half-brother who died decades ago, the NCIS team searches for the perpetrator, as Ducky recalls the final emotional days he had with his sibling.  Also, with the holidays approaching, Bishop and Jake discuss the future of their relationship.'),(294,13,12,'Sister City: Part One','/fAphMArj4OdVKQyr2MFQC8pjTkR.jpg',NULL,'The passengers and crew of a private plane traveling from New Orleans to Washington, D.C., are poisoned and the evidence points to Abby\'s brother, the aircraft\'s missing chef. The episode concludes on \"NCIS: New Orleans.\"'),(295,13,13,'Déjà Vu','/lIZAp08RaZTA23Zla9cIqFjDQt8.jpg',NULL,'While investigating the murder of a seaman who was set to testify before a grand jury, the NCIS team uncovers the resurgence of an international human-trafficking ring.  Also, McGee hopes to spend the night at a colleague’s home after a storm causes massive power outages in the city.'),(296,13,14,'Decompressed','/ajc7O9K4yTJ0cepxJnKM7lN6lMw.jpg',NULL,'Four deep sea divers stay inside a diving chamber with a deceased body in order to decompress. The dead body belongs to a retired petty officer who died in mysterious circumstances. The NCIS team will try to crack the case from land while the divers spend four days with the body.'),(297,13,15,'React','/rNIo1JfupDc032tGLTjhN8MFwZS.jpg',NULL,'When Secretary of the Navy Sarah Porter learns her daughter has been kidnapped, the NCIS team partners with the FBI to track the case, determine a motive and bring her home. Also, McGee’s childhood friend, NCIS Special Agent Valerie Page is in town to assist the team with advance tactics training'),(298,13,16,'Loose Cannons','/4EQk4vDcGVkwrrkATVGcRg2R1cl.jpg',NULL,'Doctor Cyril Taft experiences the rush of an NCIS case after he is assigned surgical duty to Gibb’s suspect and finds key evidence. Also, Dinozzo pays Jeanne Benoit a visit as he chases a lead involving doctors in Sudan.'),(299,13,17,'After Hours','/o1rDtum2F6JzZaYGfSeiCY4I7oM.jpg',NULL,'The NCIS agents’ personal plans are interrupted when each of them catches errors in a seemingly cut-and-dried closed case. Also, McGee and Delilah argue over the importance of not discussing work during dinner, while DiNozzo bores his date with shop talk.'),(300,13,18,'Scope','/vVAJzB87Jul5YZcyq1qeDV7viYI.jpg',NULL,'The NCIS team re-examines an ambush on a group of Special Ops snipers in Iraq after an American couple is attacked in the same area six months later. When Gibbs discovers he needs the account of the lone survivor, Marine Gunnery Sergeant Aaron Davis, he tries to connect with the wounded warrior who is being treated for PTSD at Walter Reed Medical Center.'),(301,13,19,'Reasonable Doubts','/jOqtslt9LkKA0iLjcOUdCAziZ7X.jpg',NULL,'A Navy Public Affairs officer is murdered, and the victim\'s wife and mistress accuse each other of the crime. Meanwhile, Anthony DiNozzo Sr. helps a homeless woman who believes he is her father.'),(302,13,20,'Charade','/6o1N2wJYv89YSYtnzVOjJ0fZahs.jpg',NULL,'Tony\'s identity is stolen by multiple perpetrators who go on to blackmail politicians.'),(303,13,21,'Return to Sender','/7kWYd2QChCT5pjNIJRpW38DLKWk.jpg',NULL,'Gibbs and Senior FBI Agent T.C. Fornell unite after two British prisoners, including a former spy, escape and arrive stateside via a shipping container. Also, McGee is busy apartment hunting and determined to find out how DiNozzo purchased his lavish place.'),(304,13,22,'Homefront','/waYRubfNb8BUlziEcQ3rE4baFQ.jpg',NULL,'When a 14-year-old foils a home invasion, Gibbs suspects the teenager is withholding pertinent details. Also, Director Vance and Senior FBI Agent Fornell travel to London as part of the ongoing escaped British spy case.'),(305,13,23,'Dead Letter','/3x8eTGNbqqxyWGzs1mnFL0NXJOx.jpg',NULL,'The NCIS team, alongside the FBI and MI6, continue an international manhunt for an escaped British spy who has left one colleague fighting for their life in ICU.'),(306,13,24,'Family First','/jlmS4o9ulmmWtswQVMrZchM3xfo.jpg',NULL,'NCIS, FBI and MI6 continue an international manhunt for an escaped British spy who is targeting current and former agents.'),(307,14,1,'Rogue','/x6oHXYIJWyGbTq2mjcTdnmNOcxo.jpg',NULL,'The NCIS team investigates a deadly car explosion in D.C. that connects to NCIS Special Agent Nicholas “Nick” Torres, who disappeared six months ago while on a deep undercover assignment in Argentina. Also, Gibbs asks NCIS Special Agent Alexandra “Alex” Quinn to shadow his team after rejecting eight agents she instructed and referred for the open position.'),(308,14,2,'Being Bad','/6gsssI6cxfbLxCIUKUtBSqSUrlW.jpg',NULL,'NCIS uncovers a bomb plot and a long-running theft ring while investigating a death at a Quantico reunion. Also Torres and Quinn adjust to life on Gibbs’ team, including new seating arrangements in the squad room.'),(309,14,3,'Privileged Information','/1P5vGXq7ON0nJyzi1XsvOna9HIu.jpg',NULL,'When the NCIS team investigates a marine sergeant’s tragic fall from a building, her doctor, Grace Confalone, confides in Gibbs and suggests he treat it as a murder investigation. Also, Torres searches for a place to live.'),(310,14,4,'Love Boat','/n1E1LcadNZ3j2qDVa3J8Zjwf0g5.jpg',NULL,'After the body of a navy lieutenant is discovered aboard a destroyer during a tiger cruise, when civilian guests are allowed to spend the night on the ship, Gibbs, Quinn and Palmer travel out to sea to investigate. Also, McGee contemplates the perfect proposal for Delilah Fielding.'),(311,14,5,'Philly','/uqryu7kHVw6XdDVzx5d7t261Csp.jpg',NULL,'When a missing MI6 Officer is linked to a murdered petty officer, Gibbs sends Quinn and Bishop to Philadelphia to work with MI6 Officer Clayton Reeves. Also, Quinn painfully recounts the NCIS case that made her leave field work.'),(312,14,6,'Shell Game','/fCW5LAcuTRlhazDazfdoydsvvPZ.jpg',NULL,'After a kidnapped petty officer escapes her captor, NCIS uncovers a connection to her missing husband. Also, Abby knits the NCIS newbies personalized gifts.'),(313,14,7,'Home of the Brave','/ztqEgEHHQCv1zS6zj7nqjJ9M83g.jpg',NULL,'Torres boldly breaks protocol when he learns a witness in an NCIS case is wanted by U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement. Also, Abby, Bishop and McGee woo landlord Tony DiNozzo Sr. in the hope of subletting Tony’s apartment.'),(314,14,8,'Enemy Combatant','/cT7RxGdvYkoF7t772qH1GlF9NQW.jpg',NULL,'After NCIS Agent Bishop is sent to Gitmo to gather evidence for a Navy chaplain murder case, she questions her previous work at the NSA. Also, Bishop’s brothers, John and Robert, visit for the Thanksgiving holiday and pester her co-workers to find out who she is dating.'),(315,14,9,'Pay to Play','/lekPqr9BPGcBYhQ5G8EBPkxDhWJ.jpg',NULL,'The NCIS team investigates a series of escalating threats against congresswoman Jenna Flemming,  while Director Vance oversees her temporary protection detail.'),(316,14,10,'The Tie That Binds','/s4cR0tB3U9kTY0Xz8u1G00XqQH5.jpg',NULL,'After the NCIS team tracks evidence from the murder of a Navy captain to Ducky’s deceased mother, Ducky looks back and questions a pivotal life choice he made 37 years ago. Also, the team exchanges holiday gifts, and Gibbs spends Christmas dinner with Fornell.'),(317,14,11,'Willoughby','/pMsfwiS38OoGaG9lskyVbeBFurz.jpg',NULL,'NCIS searches for new leads after an undercover operation to apprehend a businessman who uses acts of terror to manipulate the stock market is compromised. Also, Bishop and Qasim find a break in the case together.'),(318,14,12,'Off The Grid','/8aNhqb92Jhi8edichieJaiusluC.jpg',NULL,'When Gibbs spots the brother of an \"NCIS Most Wanted\" suspect, he takes the opportunity to assume his former alias and go undercover with their infamous anti-government militia. This leaves the NCIS team to piece together where and what Gibbs is up to. Meanwhile, Bishop and Reeves partner up on an off-the-books investigation.'),(319,14,13,'Keep Going','/e2UZUre18T94XJUr4GgzO17dNID.jpg',NULL,'During an NCIS hit-and-run investigation, Palmer joins a stranger on the outside ledge of a building in an attempt to save his life.'),(320,14,14,'Nonstop','/qQ9O7OGFKv1cgdT1o1sf3ygTlEB.jpg',NULL,'The murder of a Petty Officer in a small town outside D.C. prompts NCIS to once again work with \"The Sherlocks,\" a privately funded investigative team that includes their newest member, Anthony DiNozzo, Sr.'),(321,14,15,'Pandora\'s Box (Part 1)','/cXXkn2Zdo8hsHEBpNEEacybvckL.jpg',NULL,'After Abby\'s homeland security think tank is compromised and she is found in possession of a real bomb, the NCIS team discovers the leader of the group has been murdered and a theoretical terror playbook has been stolen.'),(322,14,16,'A Many Splendored Thing','/sppsgPa5jHFoqvYFK8Lhdk4a1HE.jpg',NULL,'Bishop is more determined than ever to seek revenge for the murder of Qasim, her late boyfriend, after Gibbs and the team find a new lead in the Chen case. Also, Torres teaches the agents the art of pickpocketing.'),(323,14,17,'What Lies Above','/fmK5YuTEaCnpfNkqIGuq2q49BvC.jpg',NULL,'McGee discovers his apartment has been torn apart by a robber trying to locate an item of great value hidden somewhere by the convicted criminal who previously owned the unit. Also, Congresswoman Flemming (Mary Stuart Masterson) tries to persuade Director Vance to pursue a career in politics.'),(324,14,18,'M.I.A.','/pUXe4jQdzCIcHDKLfhzW3utNDrc.jpg',NULL,'To carry out a sailor\'s dying wish, Gibbs and the NCIS team reinvestigate a murder case that was originally ruled an accidental death. Also, the case reminds Torres of a tragic time from his past.'),(325,14,19,'The Wall','/aLR8LPI09gVLMiEncH8WZ4oZMxW.jpg',NULL,'The team must rely on an irritable Vietnam War veteran to solve a Marine\'s murder.'),(326,14,20,'A Bowl of Cherries','/1vS0NYHpekPLvcoTzHaOjZhGGnt.jpg',NULL,'A vice admiral tasks McGee with tracking down the hackers who infected his laptop with ransomware before the virus wipes out all his data. The cyberterrorism escalates when the virus spreads to the whole NCIS office. Quinn\'s family secret is revealed.'),(327,14,21,'One Book, Two Covers','/xm1xeEtd9KVpF2JQpQKQlZi7kwP.jpg',NULL,'A Marine\'s murder has connections to a dirt bike gang that Torres joined while on an old undercover operation.'),(328,14,22,'Beastmaster','/gUeTz15Y6FbEUaBLBTb1R6thDbI.jpg',NULL,'A gunnery sergeant\'s murder in a national park lead the team to join forces with the mounted police. While investigating the clues, they uncover a disturbing smuggling ring.'),(329,14,23,'Something Blue','/p30PD2B0aXGmitpabjpGOffOH2S.jpg',NULL,'The team suspects foul play when a healthy, young petty officer mysteriously dies in his sleep aboard a Navy destroyer. Wedding stress reaches its peak for McGee and his fiancée.'),(330,14,24,'Rendezvous','/6k3NEb94IrihOpZLQeOGgUheM5z.jpg',NULL,'When a Navy SEAL vanishes during  an unsanctioned trip, Gibbs, McGee and Torres travel to an unpopulated area in Paraguay that\'s teeming with violent rebels.'),(331,15,1,'House Divided','/vEIHwkaLAcyDpUF5bQTXVJtCmSK.jpg',NULL,'Season 15 begins with the NCIS team tirelessly searching for Gibbs and McGee two months after they were last seen fighting an elusive group of rebels in a Paraguay jungle. Meanwhile, Vance and Torres are summoned to a congressional hearing regarding the fallout from the Paraguay mission.'),(332,15,2,'Twofer','/pnHTGrWoXb4rExUuf5xcTq6GFzj.jpg',NULL,'NCIS investigates when the body of a murdered Navy lieutenant, who disappeared over a year ago, is found by a cemetery grounds crew while relocating caskets on the property. Meanwhile, Gibbs and McGee must pass a psych evaluation before they can officially resume working.'),(333,15,3,'Exit Strategy','/7NwA8BONml7kzTTZT0lDSJ6qx9i.jpg',NULL,'Torres\' partner mysteriously vanishes during a stakeout with Metro P.D. The investigation uncovers new evidence from a decade-old murder case. Meanwhile, Ducky\'s friend, Cadence Darwin, presents him with a new opportunity during his guest lecture series.'),(334,15,4,'Skeleton Crew','/rQcEq63U8qm21dLybSGm5HBdFuW.jpg',NULL,'NCIS Special Agent Jacqueline Sloane, a forensic psychologist, joins the team just as a horrific storm shuts down Washington, D.C. During the power outage, a sailor is kidnapped, and Torres and Bishop go out to sea to track evidence.'),(335,15,5,'Fake It ‘Till You Make It','/1lZzAOj1vomEhMlbHoNoNopZZfh.jpg',NULL,'Reeves sees his friend get kidnapped and the investigation reveals the primary suspect disappeared two days earlier with confidential military information. Meanwhile, an embarrassing photo from McGee’s teen years becomes a popular meme.'),(336,15,6,'Trapped','/aOX5dKraifXb2iYeWZUZ7JLmYkN.jpg',NULL,'A petty officer is found murdered on a golf course, and McGee spends hours on the victim’s ham radio trying to locate a key witness. Meanwhile, Palmer asks his co-workers to donate to a charity that builds playgrounds for kids of all abilities, and Torres surprises them with his generosity.'),(337,15,7,'Burden of Proof','/r6qvSdT2TeCkGT1z9ggU537rdX.jpg',NULL,'A convicted felon claims NCIS framed him for murder a decade ago, so Gibbs investigates and asks Ducky to conduct a new autopsy. Meanwhile, Senior FBI agent Fornell joins the probe, since he was the lead investigator in the original joint FBI and NCIS case.'),(338,15,8,'Voices','/2Dd7iuesmYj1xJEb84ph8MFWP47.jpg',NULL,'An NCIS person of interest in a bribery and fraud case is found murdered after a runner is led to his body by a strange voice. Also, McGee and Delilah disagree on whether to find out the baby’s sex or keep it a surprise.'),(339,15,9,'Ready or Not','/53FDo6hiAJDSclKtwvUJ9xRVDcI.jpg',NULL,'The team tracks an elusive international arms dealer who recently murdered an MI6 officer; Abby races Delilah to the hospital when her labor starts three weeks early.'),(340,15,10,'Double Down','/m2fRYlz4Ttsf4vb8rHGsikffliA.jpg',NULL,'As Torres and Sloane run protection detail for U.S. Senator John Phillips in Afghanistan for the holidays, they must urgently return to the states after hearing the senator’s son is in the ICU. Also, Gibbs and the team investigate the altercation that caused the life threatening injuries to the senator’s son.'),(341,15,11,'High Tide','/zuxBsnmZHJ5goGXUyQunyKmUKML.jpg',NULL,'Torres and Bishop go undercover as a criminal couple available for hire, during an NCIS sting operation tracking illegal drug-running out of the Norfolk civilian marina.'),(342,15,12,'Dark Secrets','/mkNP105pRXrjJnBKVXS0cdUt1KE.jpg',NULL,'After a seemingly happy and successful Navy lieutenant appears to have taken her own life, Gibbs and the team conduct a thorough investigation, interviewing family and friends from her past and present.'),(343,15,13,'Family Ties','/3z9cOOuJvxVEs1E9eu4rT2wHEsV.jpg',NULL,'After McGee and Torres visit the home of a high schooler who witnessed a hit-and-run, her parents, Christopher and Julie Bell, flee with their daughter, leaving NCIS in the lurch. Also, Vance’s daughter is arrested for shoplifting.'),(344,15,14,'Keep Your Friends Close','/qzyCE0EMorZ2WmVtvCXGgRTrlOJ.jpg',NULL,'After the body of a missing Navy commander is found, Vance orders Gibbs and the team to work with former FBI Agent Tobias \"T.C.\" Fornell, the private investigator who was hired to locate him. Also, Bishop and Torres interview convicted investment advisor Albert Hathaway when the victim is linked to his highly publicized trial.'),(345,15,15,'Keep Your Enemies Closer','/mtRAyDwVNQfUzVlwtT3krw62bKr.jpg',NULL,'NCIS strikes a deal with convicted murderer Paul Triff, giving him a 48-hour furlough at his former residence, now McGee\'s home, in exchange for information that can convict his former cellmate, Gabriel Hicks, the murderer who deceived Gibbs and Fornell.'),(346,15,16,'Handle With Care','/8XvpdgFIgXWpdrBEZwWCDw8SQ1o.jpg',NULL,'Gibbs and the team work to clear the name of retired Marine Sergeant John Ross when cyanide is found in one of the hundreds of care packages he sends to active-duty Marines.'),(347,15,17,'One Man\'s Trash','/5VV9diNZ0eaoAe0Jgzoab0HcNG4.jpg',NULL,'Gibbs and Ducky are watching TV when they see the host handling a 200-year-old war stick that could be a match from a decade-old cold case.'),(348,15,18,'Death From Above','/uENMgscW87NejwZ9xMk9eUseCNJ.jpg',NULL,'The NCIS headquarters are evacuated after the team discovers a body as well as bomb materials on the roof of the squad room. Also, the team reads the first draft of Ducky’s book.'),(349,15,19,'The Numerical Limit','/8whkVGxLQsjY8ky5OqtHPPauSUi.jpg',NULL,'Gibbs is granted protective custody of a 10-year-old orphaned refugee, Elena, when an NCIS case reveals she is the target of a violent gang.'),(350,15,20,'Sight Unseen','/vhbDQIg9y2DKWd11YmDF682wqSj.jpg',NULL,'NCIS searches for a petty officer suspected of assault who escapes when the sheriff transporting him crashes into a lake. Also, Torres works closely with Annie Barth, a key blind witness who heard vital evidence needed to solve the case.'),(351,15,21,'One Step Forward','/a8gCrqjgBKPnTXlSH0WK6Ot1mDi.jpg',NULL,'Sara Carter begs Gibbs to investigate her mother\'s murder; she believes the wrong man was convicted; Abby is awarded a dinner reservation for two to a new five-star restaurant in an igloo and has to decide which co-worker deserves to go with her.'),(352,15,22,'Two Steps Back','/gQ5BSNQj0VX2BGWK0DiGvjJWn9B.jpg',NULL,'When evidence reveals an NCIS team member is a hitman’s latest target, the team must search through old case files to determine who is seeking vengeance.'),(353,15,23,'Fallout','/xn0PqmqIHTU1xWSN5YKAKOgVxDz.jpg',NULL,'While Gibbs attends the memorial service for a friend who was lost at sea, he discovers that the deceased, Navy Captain Phillip Brooks, has been hiding in a fallout shelter after his boat was attacked and he swam to shore.'),(354,15,24,'Date with Destiny','/gcVM0cLfWTfKUcKX6ivu4VZmrbY.jpg',NULL,'Sloane is adamant that a man who held her hostage and tortured her years ago in Afghanistan, and was believed to have been killed following her rescue, is alive and in D.C. Also, Vance and Gibbs fear Sloane is willing to risk everything to destroy this man.'),(355,16,1,'Destiny\'s Child','/2OfDpRIiBnfdw1di5HU6Oj1hZMb.jpg',NULL,'One month after Director Vance was kidnapped, Gibbs is assigned the role of acting director in his absence while the team searches worldwide for his whereabouts.'),(356,16,2,'Love Thy Neighbor',NULL,NULL,'After a Navy lieutenant is found murdered in his hot tub, the team interviews several families in the victim’s peculiar neighborhood. Also, Torres must face the consequences after a volatile night out with Palmer.'),(357,16,3,'Boom',NULL,NULL,'One of the NCIS agents is starstruck after the team investigates an explosion outside the home of Navy Petty Officer First Class Todd Nicholas and his wife, popular reality TV star Sheba Nicholas. Also, Vance continues physical therapy for the injuries sustained when he was held hostage.'),(358,16,4,'Third Wheel',NULL,NULL,'');
