INSERT INTO `santa_clarita_diet` VALUES (1,1,1,'So Then a Bat or a Monkey','/whhpcClJgF1lPxVHXLqp0INdrv3.jpg',NULL,'Joel and Sheila\'s marriage gets a jumpstart when Sheila debuts a truly killer new personality and an anything-goes menu. And they used to be so normal.'),(2,1,2,'We Can\'t Kill People!','/3aa10qv3RztWAPhwD8GJe3gS9eK.jpg',NULL,'The Hammonds try to live their new truth, Abby comes to a hard realization while browsing comics, and Joel treats Sheila to a very expensive meal.'),(3,1,3,'We Can Kill People','/mrnMS1sHNrexvo49bv6IModYsuw.jpg',NULL,'Sheila\'s tummy is growling and Joel needs to find her someone tasty ASAP. Meanwhile, Abby embraces her inner badass and helps out a friend in need.'),(4,1,4,'The Farting Sex Tourist','/aUmj48Q6HVkLSgzf8NLmUMRfsbB.jpg',NULL,'Sheila inspires her friends and insults the principal. Joel bonds with Abby, and Dan makes a damning discovery while spraying for ants.'),(5,1,5,'Man Eat Man','/h1ODtjjc8GoC7jR5pudsiD7tBAk.jpg',NULL,'Abby discovers that parents can\'t be trusted (especially hers). Joel learns there might be a cure for Sheila, and Dan puts his cards on the table.'),(6,1,6,'Attention to Detail','/eQbl7uUAd2sLxJVcZJoyijzXJDO.jpg',NULL,'Joel and Sheila try dividing up the tasks, Eric and Abby stumble onto something big, and Dan learns that a realtor can only be pushed so far.'),(7,1,7,'Strange or Just Inconsiderate?','/pJVbpK5JZH7AmOOMDAuLCMYYU3j.jpg',NULL,'With the cops looking for Dan, Sheila dines on the evidence. But that\'s a lot of evidence. Meanwhile, Joel stops to smell the coffee.'),(8,1,8,'How Much Vomit?','/1zgrnxAT2dZwglHQRNuKJYPAkYh.jpg',NULL,'A new-look Loki takes Joel and Sheila by surprise while Abby and Eric learn the fine art of leaving well enough alone.'),(9,1,9,'The Book!','/e7kkvOC5g0z9EDQ0cvtl8AosRCW.jpg',NULL,'Joel and Eric seek out the mysterious Anton at a paranormal convention while Sheila and Abby bond over their shared love of bad behavior.'),(10,1,10,'Baka, Bile and Baseball Bats','/cTEfscZuL8ilsEiL7CuYGd3TNYv.jpg',NULL,'Dr. Wolf is ready to get down to work, but with Sheila growing more aggressive by the minute, Joel worries it may be too late.'),(11,2,1,'No Family is Perfect','/qR2KefZQzKflvLgVbq1AuXG4qu6.jpg',NULL,'OK, let’s see here: Joel’s stuck in an asylum, Sheila’s chained to a pole, and Abby’s on the hunt for Serbian bile. Yep, sounds about right.'),(12,2,2,'Coyote in Yoga Pants','/NCByE5K81wFrdy7LDck5hKfmIf.jpg',NULL,'Eager to secure a lucrative new listing, Joel and Sheila brainstorm how to knock rival realtors out of contention ... without resorting to murder.'),(13,2,3,'Moral Gray Area','/nNIDILGKn9qkvK23iLs7zAyCrYU.jpg',NULL,'After an old nemesis asks for a favor, Joel and Sheila find themselves neck deep in Nazis, raffle tickets and surprisingly stunning woodwork.'),(14,2,4,'The Queen of England','/5MINJ25Rs4Yz7tQyG7LpsoujZwo.jpg',NULL,'Eric\'s having girl problems, Abby\'s rage is showing, there\'s a talking head in the basement, and now -- sheesh -- the neighbor wants lasagna.'),(15,2,5,'Going Pre-med','/xoeYsfz1rHicb7f9CpDxEy1ViFK.jpg',NULL,'A snarky online review comes back to haunt Joel. Meanwhile, Sheila\'s new friendship proves problematic, and Abby leans into her new persona.'),(16,2,6,'Pasión','/uCrVOqJ0xYbdyxvauw1RhbNfLhR.jpg',NULL,'Is a colonel the clam connection? Joel’s on a stakeout to find out. Also, Abby has a date, and Sheila doesn\'t see eye to eye with her boss.'),(17,2,7,'A Change of Heart','/twqV1q5PJfBRcoCFM8WghKWjChq.jpg',NULL,'007, he ain’t. Eric’s plan to go undercover as a seafood distributor hits a snag. Meanwhile, Joel and Sheila worry Abby is getting out of control.'),(18,2,8,'Easels and War Paint','/rGjN6crWZxKkrlqIb6WqrsnIDVH.jpg',NULL,'Sheila and Joel piece together the previous night\'s events while dealing with a professional setback. Abby gets a bold new look, courtesy of Lisa.'),(19,2,9,'Suspicious Objects','/nXItFMswtGwOC0VXAfHW3cZN0aO.jpg',NULL,'Joel and Sheila learn that the clampocalypse may hit sooner than they thought. Anne accepts constructive criticism like a pro.'),(20,2,10,'Halibut!','/k7whGNk4wZwaR2PGtjIftoBhEMG.jpg',NULL,'With their options dwindling and their paranoia rising, Joel and Sheila consider making a move. Eric and Abby come up with a fracking good plan.');
