rrangements to take the club in a different direction.'),(66,5,13,'J\'ai Obtenu Cette','/icLm7Oo1DCW71nCSmbyklQr75Dc.jpg',NULL,'Season finale:'),(67,6,1,'Straw','/olMD14hKT9BNuh66rT1CIBhyPNf.jpg',NULL,'As Jax continues to push the club into more legitimate businesses he can’t escape the sins of SAMCRO’s past.'),(68,6,2,'One One Six','/zgsfyE6jT2PKcMFT9G1bgVRWOSv.jpg',NULL,'Jax deals with collateral damage as external pressure continue to stack up against SAMCRO.'),(69,6,3,'Poenitentia','/vKssMnqxfgTlv5xP9dRfC5sXkg9.jpg',NULL,'Jax secures a new alliance for the club while Clay makes moves inside for protection.'),(70,6,4,'Wolfsangel','/hYfCs7x1zycWBtOGpyTyt0GZy6T.jpg',NULL,'An attack at the compound leads SOA to seek revenge.'),(71,6,5,'The Mad King','/5NT3zkQCyS0H8NcNuvqOMcouXPY.jpg',NULL,'The club is forced to make an uneasy alliance with unforeseen consequences.'),(72,6,6,'Salvage','/hJE5Bo8DjTcWfn38f6sBdZPfo1U.jpg',NULL,'Jax and the MC must confront their past and choose their future.'),(73,6,7,'Sweet and Vaded','/pzxZv9Z8BIskEZqoDbXQUNEKPUW.jpg',NULL,'Triggers are pulled that strengthen the MC, but also threaten to destroy it.'),(74,6,8,'Los Fantasmas','/zBwFuy6iWDIt1HtZfaLRXde0XoV.jpg',NULL,'Pressure mounts on Jax as the sins of his club and family pull him in different directions.'),(75,6,9,'John 8:32','/v74bArZAKFje4efuq8WQfu8dOwW.jpg',NULL,'Jax learns new secrets that turn his world sideways.'),(76,6,10,'Huang Wu','/sgszDSvluxn8xhEX9R1OUAgxt8D.jpg',NULL,'Jax looks to push the club forward, but the Irish put another obstacle in his way.'),(77,6,11,'Aon Rud Persanta','/Asd4g154Wh14nn4eYsU4YqlXFxP.jpg',NULL,'Tension mounts as the club makes a bold move to finally get out of guns.'),(78,6,12,'You Are My Sunshine','/oggqBaJiu9QgcLAkUwNwvMBh8tq.jpg',NULL,'As the dust beings to settle Jax’s world is suddenly turned upside down.'),(79,6,13,'A Mother’s Work','/k2qQ5kFxg0vmuiMNnzk9EIgSuZJ.jpg',NULL,'The ramifications of Jax’s choices put his club and family in jeopardy.'),(80,7,1,'Black Widower','/w0COzxT0Q4U2EMkGRDWaTjFN6Zi.jpg',NULL,'In the wake of Tara’s death, Jax makes vengeance a club priority.'),(81,7,2,'Toil and Till','/em6jp2hlg23AjT4P3cUyeyJK30f.jpg',NULL,'SAMCRO solicits help from another Charter to get a messy job done.'),(82,7,3,'Playing with Monsters','/rCtcx5Slf6GCkLtMrB6P6tmoDmV.jpg',NULL,'SAMCRO exploits an opportunity to secure an important alliance.'),(83,7,4,'Poor Little Lambs','/oTetiRHLKLRU4aQ3eHct85FGoEF.jpg',NULL,'A past effort to help one ally leads to trouble with another.'),(84,7,5,'Some Strange Eruption','/coRet28yUEJi2s2YjfZF7TNojTZ.jpg',NULL,'Looking for the source of a betrayal leads to violence at the Stockton Ports.'),(85,7,6,'Smoke \'em if You Got \'em','/scLRbPLbgC5YD3M1PXSy9OVFKO4.jpg',NULL,'Jax settles a score by taking advantage of shifting alliances.'),(86,7,7,'Greensleeves','/pD2mcBnUQ7KITKJSSirhFjgvIM7.jpg',NULL,'SAMCRO forges an unlikely partnership in order to undermine a powerful enemy.'),(87,7,8,'The Separation of Crows','/7bMfIDIRT4ucXXlhtKiwo57vCfj.jpg',NULL,'With the search for a missing member at a standstill, focus shifts to flushing out an internal rat.'),(88,7,9,'What a Piece of Work Is Man','/bj3cacbceL8a8MtveZ4W6GLGgx6.jpg',NULL,'The club deals with heartache internally and conflict with the organization at large.'),(89,7,10,'Faith and Despondency','/sLjF9mGMu0EfssDxUP9kV7LiUDb.jpg',NULL,'SAMCRO members fall in love, but death is in the air.'),(90,7,11,'Suits of Woe','/8L6F49XHg0PyKviXG8USvM9uQsN.jpg',NULL,'The SOA organization bears down on SAMCRO and Jax comes face to face with an ugly truth.'),(91,7,12,'Red Rose','/1XitKgHHG7EjZh5Nh7QJy9TgRZR.jpg',NULL,'With tensions mounting and truths finally revealed, Jax must make the ultimate decision.'),(92,7,13,'Papa\'s Goods','/mbHsHNKHfc8xIq1naQ6rxXIaSdo.jpg',NULL,'Ghosts loom large as Jax makes the final moves to fulfill his father\'s legacy.');
