INSERT INTO `star_trek_the_next_generation` VALUES (1,1,1,'Encounter at Farpoint, Part 1','/wH6PiwAneCZp2S9JCrCsFl5761V.jpg','70177863','Stardate: 41153.7 \n\nThe new commander of the recently built U.S.S. Enterprise (NCC1701-D), Captain Jean- Luc Picard  takes the crew on their first mission to discover the secret of Farpoint Station. During their journey, they encounter an omnipotent being known as Q. Q accuses humanity of barbarism, and places humanity on trial. Jean-Luc must prove otherwise or the human race will be annihilated.'),(2,1,2,'Encounter at Farpoint, Part 2','/y5UXwnxTTSW8vPmIBwP0BffodQA.jpg','70177864','Stardate: 41153.7 \n\nConclusion. At the end of the trial, Q gives Picard 24 hours to prove the worthiness of the human race.'),(3,1,3,'The Naked Now','/mhDWO4T9GvrWKY95ZdyJX4oMd3g.jpg','70177865','Stardate: 41209.2 \n\nThe crew of the Enterprise are infected with a virus contracted by the away team while they were investigating  the mysterious deaths of the entire crew of the Starship Tsilkovsky.'),(4,1,4,'Code of Honor','/eoz9r9PW3Z5qIHLZZePsO5YnnfL.jpg','70177866','Stardate: 41235.25 \n\nTasha Yar must fight for her life and a vaccine to save a race of people when she is kidnapped and forced to battle with her abductor\'s wife.'),(5,1,5,'The Last Outpost','/f3JfVjO8FTXTipgPaRvEKIm1pJo.jpg','70177867','Stardate: 41386.4 \n\nA powerful entity disables the Enterprise and a Ferengi ship. Their only means of escape is if they can correctly answer the riddles he asks.'),(6,1,6,'Where No One Has Gone Before','/zj4j40p5OjaBRYsZH0nmKa0IvmF.jpg','70177868','Stardate: 41263.1 \n\nThe Enterprise is flung across space into a distant galaxy billions of light years away when a propulsion engineer and his mysterious companion, attempt to re-design the ship\'s engine systems.'),(7,1,7,'Lonely Among Us','/9gO5h7y4qrHlNMcfs3lwmQMZAmS.jpg','70177869','Stardate: 41249.3 \n\nPicard\'s mind is taken over by an energy field that the Enterprise passes through.'),(8,1,8,'Justice','/52Ec4HtLQHS5vsysk8rbN0Zm3Nz.jpg','70177870','Stardate: 41255.6  Picard is forced to choose between friendship and the Prime Directive when Wesley Crusher is sentenced to death for accidentally breaking the law on Rubicon III.'),(9,1,9,'The Battle','/yGJYLwuDiTwsOGgJTPiPqLkrgWH.jpg','70177871','Stardate: 41723.9 \n\nThe Ferengi hand over an old ship which Picard once captained, the U.S.S. Stargazer. The Ferengi have installed a mind altering device that alters Picard\'s mind to make him think that he is reliving a past battle, and the target is the Enterprise.'),(10,1,10,'Hide and Q','/iRaUlCplRFK7qi7NwweiwbqnsL4.jpg','70177872','Stardate: 41590.5 \n\nQ places the senior crew of the Enterprise in a war game that pits them against a boar-faced, Napoleonic enemy.'),(11,1,11,'Haven','/y9IwQKZFVi5uRrZcYLiZH0yqyxj.jpg','70177873','Stardate: 41294.6 \n\nThe mother of Deanna Troi, Lwaxana,  pays a surprise visit to the Enterprise and announces the prearranged marriage of Deanna to the son of her Mother\'s late husband\'s best friend.'),(12,1,12,'The Big Goodbye','/xS6hEGtePgnUf35PbstoMQQInar.jpg','70177874','Stardate: 41997.7\n\nPicard, Dr. Crusher and Data are placed in great danger when the holodeck malfunctions while they are running a Dixon Hill program, which pits them against 1940\'s mobsters.'),(13,1,13,'Datalore','/rCTtAQaHRMPDFNft1UgiXJHPNeo.jpg','70177875','Stardate: 41242.4\n\nThe crew of the Enterprise find android parts that are identical to Data\'s while they are exploring his homeworld. When assembled, an \'evil\' twin of Data is created and named \'Lore\'.'),(14,1,14,'Angel One','/j4IjJD4yHNf20UcS3SuRLeCU3jr.jpg','70177876','Stardate: 41636.9\n\nThe Enterprise discovers the male crew of a crashed Federation freighter are hiding as fugitives on the planet Angel One, which is dominated and ruled by women.'),(15,1,15,'11001001','/4aWS6A0rcRa6yRL0uFtoZhj7Zpz.jpg','70177877','Stardate: 41365.9\n\nWhile undergoing repairs, the Bynar Engineers steal the Enterprise to save their planet from destruction.'),(16,1,16,'Too Short a Season','/2Q2MtGi0kvLBRU5df9kP5bIuXH4.jpg','70177878','Stardate: 41309.5\n\nThe aging and terminally ill Starfleet Admiral Mark Jameson, who is negotiating the release of hostages, suddenly begins growing younger through an unexplained phenomenon.'),(17,1,17,'When the Bough Breaks','/vHzIvtb0CR940AwqhW8OOxmHVlO.jpg','70177879','Stardate: 41509.1\n\nThe children of the Enterprise, including Wesley Crusher, are abducted by a race of sterile people who are unable to have children of their own.'),(18,1,18,'Home Soil','/wLox8Y2tFlovR7Bw0CozEGDuWau.jpg','70177880','Stardate: 41463.9\n\nThe members of an away team investigating the death of an engineer encounter vengeful microscopic life forms.'),(19,1,19,'Coming of Age','/2cX9KPzYyM1U6dCZYJ7lf86jLTe.jpg','70177881','Stardate: 41416.2\n\nWhile Wesley takes the entrance exam to Starfleet Academy, the Enterprise is investigated by the Inspector General\'s office and Picard\'s competency is questioned.'),(20,1,20,'Heart of Glory','/A28hj2UKPb7M5lILNATSxTa9XQO.jpg','70177882','Stardate: 41503.7\n\nTwo Klingons, rescued by the Enterprise, try to take over the ship.'),(21,1,21,'The Arsenal of Freedom','/pFt8l7JEyvPkbHsFnW2ay0Jjjx7.jpg','70177883','Stardate: 41798.2\n\nThe crew encounters bizarre phenomena while searching for the missing U.S.S. Drake.'),(22,1,22,'Symbiosis','/5DVtT0ccUasu49e5TktnNYXDWZZ.jpg','70177884','Stardate: Unknown\n\nPicard attempts to break an ancient co-dependency between two species on one planet without violating the Prime Directive.'),(23,1,23,'Skin of Evil','/aQr5EfTGpN7LmOcHWqTRRRuyDYn.jpg','70177885','Stardate: 41601.3\n\nWhen Troi\'s shuttle crashes on an alien planet, a new being is discovered: an entity that thrives on the suffering of others.'),(24,1,24,'We\'ll Always Have Paris','/bvE3r0nCqidOrnGe7DWTyINxpHo.jpg','70177886','Stardate: 41697.9\n\nPicard meets an old flame, whose husband has created a haywire dimensional experiment.'),(25,1,25,'Conspiracy','/79yjiw04w1wIvwOGtkTEzkSAjJK.jpg','70177887','Stardate: 41775.5\n\nThe strange behavior of high-ranking officers leads Picard to uncover a twisted alien conspiracy within Starfleet.'),(26,1,26,'The Neutral Zone','/q9BlKXTKDBUhAkMc8H8BQSQ9TDU.jpg','70177888','Stardate: 41986.0\n\nA derelict satellite is found with cryonically frozen humans aboard as the USS Enterprise is sent to investigate the destruction of outposts near Romulan space.'),(27,2,1,'The Child','/o3alsv4VRVcw9HNQUDWGAY8SWBw.jpg','70177889','Stardate: 42073.1\n\nTroi undergoes a mysterious pregnancy when the Enterprise tries to escape from a system that has recently fallen victim to a deadly plague.'),(28,2,2,'Where Silence Has Lease','/y3V2r5hRV9LvRcTSaHMaTaa820L.jpg','70177890','Stardate: 42193.6\n\nA mysterious life form known as the \'Nagilum\' threatens the life of the crew in his attempt to understand humanity.'),(29,2,3,'Elementary, Dear Data','/iZ6AbNrEjkats5dQn1HF2eKRBjT.jpg','70177891','Stardate: 42286.3\n\nData and Geordi become involved with a holodeck program about Sherlock Holmes and his investigations, when they create Sherlock\'s arch nemesis, Moriarty; however, modifications to the Moriarty character include the capability of out-smarting Data, which leads to some unexpected consequences.'),(30,2,4,'The Outrageous Okona','/kCegnPbVZZeb1z3zPSEnwBu24vG.jpg','70177892','Stardate: 42402.7\n\nThe Enterprise is placed in a compromising situation when the captain of a disabled starship places the crew in the middle of a love triangle.'),(31,2,5,'Loud as a Whisper','/nlwGs3gDXqwI9LE8cx9UNeJlMWI.jpg','70177893','Stardate: 42477.2\n\nA deaf-mute mediator meets with disaster while being escorted by the Enterprise.'),(32,2,6,'The Schizoid Man','/q2UnbvUvJbwRg19ii9YAS9M8UT4.jpg','70177894','Stardate: 42437.5\n\nData is possessed by the consciousness of a brilliant scientist. However, it has a disturbing impact on Data\'s personality.'),(33,2,7,'Unnatural Selection','/dsTNveqfKA8fQVc2miQCMtMUj4T.jpg','70177895','Stardate: 42494.8\n\nA mysterious hyper-ageing sickness kills the crew of a Federation cargo ship, and Dr. Pulaski must race against time to find a cure.'),(34,2,8,'A Matter of Honor','/40yRSBTJPPHakPfWSPa6FyOdt0V.jpg','70177896','Commander Riker participates in an officer\'s exchange program which lands him an assignment on a Klingon Bird-of-Prey.  Meanwhile, a Bezite ensign has trouble assimilating to the routines of the Enterprise.'),(35,2,9,'The Measure of a Man','/wXgjvhI3XLtQP9dqkuUIsd6dedD.jpg','70177897','Stardate: 42523.7\n\nWhen Data\'s rights as a sentient individual are placed under trial, Starfleet forces Riker into a position where he must prove that Data is only an Android.'),(36,2,10,'The Dauphin','/lKeRpPXCC2naT4dmUkb3RROBKY8.jpg','70177898','Stardate: 42568.8\n\nWesley falls in love with a passenger the Enterprise is escorting, who has the secret ability to shape-shift.'),(37,2,11,'Contagion','/d6kozBwFu6E5HXjvPr11UcUhUx3.jpg','70177899','Stardate: 42609.1\n\nA strange power source disables the Enterprise\'s computer systems, damages Data\'s programming and leaves the ship and crew vulnerable to a Romulan attack.'),(38,2,12,'The Royale','/8XF6ML1bQy7u7WESAC2DL0Uaj3s.jpg','70177900','Stardate: 42625.4\n\nAn away team is trapped in an alien environment based around a novel entitled \'The Hotel Royale.\''),(39,2,13,'Time Squared','/wq6ehoKfbdEvZZp2NIMO0GRU1xb.jpg','70177901','Stardate: 42679.2\n\nPicard encounters his double from six hours in the future, whose Enterprise had been destroyed.'),(40,2,14,'The Icarus Factor','/w0ivktoGOOvUUvbyOpmS2mQL55j.jpg','70177902','Stardate: 42686.4\n\nRiker is promoted to Captain of another Federation ship. Worf must confront his past and his Klingon heritage.'),(41,2,15,'Pen Pals','/1e5pFuVsGvjWTYPM0Z6MmaQ6okn.jpg','70177903','Stardate: 42695.3\n\nWesley must investigate the causes of strange tectonic activity on the planet where Data\'s pen pal lives.'),(42,2,16,'Q Who','/xuisNlLNyxo4ZneU3vUZwnArr7e.jpg','70177904','Stardate: 42761.3\n\nQ hurls the Enterprise into the Delta Quadrant and introduces the Federation to a powerful new enemy that may destroy the Alpha Quadrant: The Borg.'),(43,2,17,'Samaritan Snare','/gIZxWUoyMX99Zfd4zD45CCZl6J2.jpg','70177905','Stardate: 42779.1\n\nA race known as the Pakleds kidnap Geordi La Forge. Picard must face surgery when he is left in a near-dead state.'),(44,2,18,'Up the Long Ladder','/9spCPwsVegTCuk6jSHFi5coYg9Q.jpg','70177906','Stardate: 42823.2\n\nPicard must convince two dying civilizations that they must co-exist on the same planet to survive, however, they have other plans to ensure their survival: in the form of clones of the Enterprise crew.'),(45,2,19,'Manhunt','/8keiLQIUvvv6bq46tk0y9NUgtsy.jpg','70177907','Stardate: 42859.2\n\nWhile being escorted to a Federation conference by the Enterprise, Lwaxana hunts for a man to satisfy her needs when her sex-drive is quadrupled during a natural mid-life cycle.'),(46,2,20,'The Emissary','/pXBRddJP1VyTsgfRT8jNd7GIeJ.jpg','70177908','Stardate: 42901.3\n\nWorf is re-united with his former lover, K\'Ehleyr, while the Enterprise is ordered to intercept a Klingon ship whose crew has been in stasis for a century.'),(47,2,21,'Peak Performance','/lUh97fn3jhYPEj1LTctg9RubNc4.jpg','70177909','Stardate: 42923.4\n\nTrouble begins when a Ferengi warship stumbles over a war simulation between Riker and Picard, each on different ships, and begins attacking them.'),(48,2,22,'Shades of Gray','/qYjx9QHWuB45CF0ejyv8aGcYXyU.jpg','70177910','Stardate: 42976.1\n\nRiker is infected with an alien organism that takes over his mind. Dr. Pulaski must force Riker\'s mind back to a state where it can access primitive survival skills.'),(49,3,1,'Evolution','/kWIIOHqVbEzMuICQqqGBLVjqdfF.jpg','70177911','Stardate: 43125.8\n\nA system-wide computer malfunction places the crew of the U.S.S. Enterprise in grave danger while they are escorting a scientist to a star in the process of exploding.'),(50,3,2,'The Ensigns of Command','/mHAYgbbasoza8EU4hOA26pGnats.jpg','70177912','Stardate: 43133.3\n\nA human colony is forced to evacuate a planet when the original inhabitants return and threaten the colonists with annihilation if they do not leave within four days.'),(51,3,3,'The Survivors','/t1GdRU25J7OyLl6vFhrXCBnuI7L.jpg','70177913','Stardate: 43152.4\n\nThe Enterprise discovers a planet that has had all life eradicated, except for two mysterious residents and their home, which has been left in perfect condition.'),(52,3,4,'Who Watches the Watchers','/tgQqHppFYEwseLIIRWIPgKuCZT4.jpg','70177914','Stardate: 43173.5\n\nAn away team inadvertently breaks the Prime Directive and reveal themselves to a primitive culture on Mintaka III, causing the inhabitants believe that Captain Picard is a God.'),(53,3,5,'The Bonding','/iinXqjsTSbS1rZtcpteDsYpHdZb.jpg','70177915','Worf and Wesley must help a 12 year old boy cope with the death of his mother; an archaeologist killed during an away mission to a deserted planet.'),(54,3,6,'Booby Trap','/oj9vfNJw2n2ecPCa3B46wkcvzww.jpg','70177916','Stardate: 43205.6\n\nWhile investigating an ancient ship left adrift in space, the Enterprise accidentally trips the ancient booby trap that disabled the old vessel over 1000 years ago.'),(55,3,7,'The Enemy','/lAqIzKjiLPEmLCsPYXYO1pA081h.jpg','70177917','Stardate:43349.2\n\nA blind Geordie is trapped on a hazardous planet with a paranoid and severely injured Romulan. In orbit, a Romulan Warbird is preventing the Enterprise from attempting a rescue mission.'),(56,3,8,'The Price','/cQ0fdsqxZDsrZjn8ijZBpmyjB2u.jpg','70177918','Stardate: 43385.6\n\nThe Enterprise hosts the negotiations for the rights to a newly discovered, stable wormhole to the Delta Quadrant. One of the negotiators, Devinoni Ral, becomes attracted to Deanna Troi, but he holds a dubious secret.'),(57,3,9,'The Vengeance Factor','/hYJDU91VHpB2vcrDCcejikMKWdF.jpg','70177919','Stardate: 43421.9\n\nThe Enterprise crew tries to mend the relationship between a race known as the Acamarians and a faction known as the Gatherers.'),(58,3,10,'The Defector','/n01XSdotXV12SlcD3X4PvV9dYC2.jpg','70177920','Stardate: 43462.5\n\nA defecting Romulan warns the Federation about an impending attack by the Romulans, who are secretly establishing bases within the Neutral Zone.'),(59,3,11,'The Hunted','/lIdUQcoVmRl9l2prIGwuxQssBTk.jpg','70177921','Stardate: 43489.2\n\nA potentially new member of the Federation enlists the help of the Enterprise to track down a wanted criminal who has a reputation for his excessive violence. However, the fugitive\'s actions may not be of his own will.'),(60,3,12,'The High Ground','/h5PLDx787ECkRcmV3RDHgejk64S.jpg','70177922','Stardate: 43510.7\n\nDr. Crusher is abducted by a group of terrorists while delivering crucial medical supplies to a planet ravaged by civil war.'),(61,3,13,'Déjà Q','/VA2A3MtJ9WvJihSVAa6sGAXXl6.jpg','70177923','Stardate: 43539.1\n\nA Calamarian starts attacking the Enterprise while seeking revenge on a powerless Q.'),(62,3,14,'A Matter of Perspective','/8EOijfpyAwUQCGf2W0USrcw3XRY.jpg','70177924','Stardate: 43610.4\n\nRiker is accused of murder when a scientist is killed in an explosion. Picard must recreate the recent events in the holodeck to prove his commander\'s innocence.'),(63,3,15,'Yesterday\'s Enterprise','/sTRT5d2ZeYsB67hDvRm3vWpDGuY.jpg','70177925','Stardate: 43625.2\n\nA rift in the space/time continuum brings the U.S.S. Enterprise - C forward into the 24th Century, and alters the timeline. In this future, the Federation is at war with the Klingons, Tasha Yar is on the bridge, Worf did not join the Federation, and only Guinan\'s unique perception of reality may restore the timeline.'),(64,3,16,'The Offspring','/wTDL05cVu2JMEp76sASCxdStigj.jpg','70177926','Stardate: 43657.0\n\nData becomes a father when he creates a Soong-type android in the form of a daughter named Lal. Issues are complicated when Lal starts showing signs of a more evolved consciousness, including the ability to feel emotions, which attracts the attention of Starfleet scientists who want to take her away from Data and examine her advanced systems.'),(65,3,17,'Sins of the Father','/sFU0E10PK6Ltm0NNwzw1S1l5Ugy.jpg','70177927','Stardate: 43685.2\n\nWorf is reunited with his long-lost brother when their father is charged with treason for helping the Romulans. Together they make an appeal to the Klingon High Council to challenge the charges, and have them revoked.'),(66,3,18,'Allegiance','/mqMOrwEBSYKjXoAPqItsEY2GpYU.jpg','70177928','Stardate: 43714.1\n\nPicard is secretly abducted and switched with an alien double. The crews\' suspicions are raised when he starts exhibiting unusual behaviour, and is relieved of command.'),(67,3,19,'Captain\'s Holiday','/4fbf8GBZmgVQmUTRNWDgLQ2W9sU.jpg','70177929','Stardate: 43745.2\n\nWhile on vacation on Risa, Captain Picard encounters two Vorgons from the 27th Century who claim they are searching for a powerful weapon hidden somewhere on the planet.'),(68,3,20,'Tin Man','/wGij04f9RBqpmyeEwXMYcNOAKJo.jpg','70177930','Stardate: 43779.3\n\nThe Enterprise encounters a \'living\' ship in the Neutral Zone, and risks breaking the Romulan Federation alliance in order to bring it into contact with a Betazoid emissary.'),(69,3,21,'Hollow Pursuits','/g9jbamFK4I5VJl4kQveSQu3bjKO.jpg','70177931','Stardate: 43807.4\n\nA nervous and insecure officer, Lt. Reginald Barclay, places the Enterprise in great danger when he neglects his duties in Engineering, and instead spends his time acting out his fantasies on the holodeck.'),(70,3,22,'The Most Toys','/xca8yGi9IP5THWR4tLGJaehJuJ0.jpg','70177932','Stardate: 43872.2\n\nThe crew are shattered by the apparent death of Data in a shuttle explosion, and are prevented from carrying out a detailed investigation when Starfleet gives them orders for a new mission elsewhere. However, the crew don\'t realize that he was actually abducted and placed on display as part of a collection of rare and valuable items held by a disreputable character.'),(71,3,23,'Sarek','/w2F7kAV1g2WuTmCC4NC8d61hkbW.jpg','70177933','Stardate: 43917.4\n\nSpock\'s Vulcan father, Sarek, boards the Enterprise to negotiate political relations with the Legaran. However, Sarek has contract Bendii syndrome, which causes a Vulcan to gradually lose control, and become overpowered with emotions.'),(72,3,24,'Ménage à Troi','/sIPRYkuaL3R8LaVmsR0PL6dq7NE.jpg','70177934','Riker and Deanna, both on shoreleave, are unexpectedly joined by Deanna\'s mother, Lwaxana, on Betazed. Shortly, all three are kidnapped by the Ferengi who want to study Lwaxana\'s telepathic abilities.'),(73,3,25,'Transfigurations','/bVA8PtWGL8SOMIvfwTvEQiBFgNi.jpg','70177935','Stardate: 43957.2 Dr. Crusher becomes attracted to an injured alien with mysterious powers, who is being tracked down by his government like a wanted criminal.'),(74,3,26,'The Best of Both Worlds (1)','/knPRS77hGm0RcKL1Q8Ih1HYEHpo.jpg','70177936','Stardate: 43989.1 An Starfleet expert on the Borg, Lt. Cmdr. Shelby, is assigned to the Enterprise to investigate the disappearance of a Federation colony. Picard is abducted by the Borg and assimilated into the Collective, which forces Riker to attempt a rescue mission.'),(75,4,1,'The Best of Both Worlds (2)','/knPRS77hGm0RcKL1Q8Ih1HYEHpo.jpg','70177937','Riker must pull out all the stops in order to save Earth from a Borg invasion being lead by none other than Locutus - otherwise known as Captain Jean-Luc Picard.'),(76,4,2,'Family','/uOSTR9aQqRK2CLnguMUugEl2Le9.jpg','70177938','Picard meets with his older brother in France, and contemplates resigning his Starfleet commission after his ordeal with the Borg. Worf\'s adoptive parents spend time with their son on the Enterprise, and succeed in embarrassing him in front of his crewmates.'),(77,4,3,'Brothers','/hRNDreyhcfn0hsmTjW7atfQfGzs.jpg','70177939','While escorting a seriously ill boy to the closest Federation Starbase for treatment, Data mysteriously takes control of the Enterprise and takes it to a distant planet. He learns that his creator has summoned him for an important meeting that could change his life. However, Dr. Soong unknowingly summoned Data\'s twin brother Lore, into the bargain.'),(78,4,4,'Suddenly Human','/qmRcafsIPv9xxBCQCL27xomsXt.jpg','70177940','A custody battle between Picard and a child\'s adoptive father arises when a boy showing evidence of abuse is discovered.'),(79,4,5,'Remember Me','/19KEYYrhFPKQkk3SJr7cvirIuce.jpg','70177941','Dr. Crusher begins to question her sanity when members of the crew start disappearing one by one, and all evidence of their existence is erased.'),(80,4,6,'Legacy','/onczGt45EOGx9U5Ufn6eGzuBgQg.jpg','70177942','The Enterprise is caught in the middle of a civil war when they encounter Tasha Yar\'s long-lost younger sister, Ishara.'),(81,4,7,'Reunion','/maUPSTYUzfVrfGtnFip83Rn9TTn.jpg','70177943','Picard is asked to choose between two candidates to succeed the current Chancellor of the Klingon High Council as the new ruler of the Empire. Worf is disturbed by unexpected news when he is paid a visit by his former lover.'),(82,4,8,'Future Imperfect','/7XQRWHlaRalnkXDVUJCqDEV8Ruv.jpg','70177944','Riker awakens one morning to discover he is suddenly 16 years in the future as the captain of the Enterprise, and negotiating a peace treaty with the Romulans with no recollection of how he arrived at that point in time, or of any recent events.'),(83,4,9,'Final Mission','/v1prSavfjiw3J4Vr7toGq640xbE.jpg','70177945','Wesley must keep Captain Picard alive on the eve of his entrance exam to Starfleet Academy when their shuttle crashes on a barren moon.'),(84,4,10,'The Loss','/6vfZBsAPNVNlH314a4D1djqqPNp.jpg','70177946','Troi loses her empathic abilities when the Enterprise is caught in the gravitational pull of a black hole.'),(85,4,11,'Data\'s Day','/4hMq40QO7kdw82R8YBzVlzPp6Bz.jpg','70177947','A Vulcan Ambassador being escorted by the Enterprise starts exhibiting suspicious behavior. Miles O\'Brien marries his fiancée, Keiko Ishikawa in Ten-Forward.'),(86,4,12,'The Wounded','/7aBQ44UrwBeimECSkXMACiEfLeQ.jpg','70177948','When the Cardassians start re-arming themselves, a Federation Captain takes it upon himself to remove a potential threat before it escalated. Now, Picard must fight for the Cardassians and stop the renegade from slaughtering innocents.'),(87,4,13,'Devil\'s Due','/mq27dufrluSxjwPsHTqCofJWybL.jpg','70177949','The crew of the Enterprise must defend the planet Ventax from a mythological Devil who re-appears when a 1000 year long era of peace comes to an end.'),(88,4,14,'Clues','/mHRqo6VwBPYKzNUQ1R8K5sHlRNx.jpg','70177950','Picard orders a secret investigation when the crew suspects Data of lying about the discovery of a wormhole.'),(89,4,15,'First Contact','/vlJyACAoDmMJgLlMV0Kgof5rJne.jpg','70177951','Riker is abducted by a xenophobic race of aliens during a first contact mission. They believe the Enterprise is a scout for an invasion.'),(90,4,16,'Galaxy\'s Child','/aC7hMcIyfU8OGz4PlaMNmASdg11.jpg','70177952','Geordi must work with the real Leah Brahms when she arrives on the Enterprise when a space-borne alien life form thinks the ship is its mother. Tensions rise when she learns that Geordi created a holographic version of her several months before in order to save the ship from danger.'),(91,4,17,'Night Terrors','/jgl1zzUE3Lfb6nMtz5DoxvDCeFL.jpg','70177953','Troi faces a recurring nightmare when the Enterprise is caught in a rift in space. Soon, the crew begins to slip into insanity through dream deprivation.'),(92,4,18,'Identity Crisis','/ceelCOiqEADk5g0Pu2ZttX1tSZT.jpg','70177954','Geordi and a former crew mate begin evolving into bizarre creatures when they return to a planet both of them were on during an Away Mission five years earlier.'),(93,4,19,'The Nth Degree','/awC4PR6zRgPbKEVcsHNw5Y5GeZ9.jpg','70177955','An alien probe transforms Barclay from a shy, awkward character into an arrogant super-genius who is able to interface with the Enterprise\'s computer through the holodeck.'),(94,4,20,'Qpid','/8HehljNNHVBwASQZBX5MYICjH1z.jpg','70177956','Q places Vash and the senior Enterprise crew in a recreation of Robin Hood and his merry men.'),(95,4,21,'The Drumhead','/esBnpBXW2U9RODm6zUYwyKvhL5C.jpg','70177957','Picard is accused of treason when an explosion aboard the Enterprise is investigated by a ruthless and paranoid Starfleet Admiral.'),(96,4,22,'Half a Life','/hjHiJT1AjtELePTrQzG1M1EMhWU.jpg','70177958','Lwaxana Troi falls in love with a man who must return home to commit suicide, as is customary for their race when they reach a certain age.'),(97,4,23,'The Host','/tpqmbYOvkskLy4gDq85045dOCOB.jpg','70177959','Dr. Crusher falls in love with a Trill Ambassador, until she discovers the Trill\'s symbiotic relationship.'),(98,4,24,'The Mind\'s Eye','/nPfrLLDXRbcWNlmjDRRA5nFoGA4.jpg','70177960','While en route to Risa for shore leave, Geordi is abducted by the Romulans and brainwashed into becoming an assassin.'),(99,4,25,'In Theory','/7Jui72z2Copq44kco4IRWDhlQN.jpg','70177961','Data experiences the complexities of love when a fellow crewmate becomes attracted to him.'),(100,4,26,'Redemption (1)','/nTSOFWYGN44bpqDUSjlGFoioqZI.jpg','70177962','Worf must choose between his people and the Federation when a civil war threatens to destroy the Klingon Empire.'),(101,5,1,'Redemption (2)','/nTSOFWYGN44bpqDUSjlGFoioqZI.jpg','70177963','Stardate: 45020.4 - Picard suspects a Romulan influence in the recent Klingon civil war, and must force the Federation to intervene before the Empire collapses.'),(102,5,2,'Darmok','/avY6Ie8Etarp8TZ5grBSONHCh85.jpg','70177964','Stardate: 45047.2 - Picard must find a way to communicate with the newly discovered Tamarians, who speak entirely in metaphors, when a Tamarian Captain is brutally killed.'),(103,5,3,'Ensign Ro','/pfFqM3ZJU2I6hGdLCkgjRuaAEJj.jpg','70177965','Stardate: 45076.3 - Picard exposes a planned genocidal attack on the Bajorans with the help of a new officer, Ensign Ro Laren.'),(104,5,4,'Silicon Avatar','/nuZbeaNLUHZYeieKOxElLdfbCPh.jpg','70177966','Stardate: 45122.3 - Picard attempts communications with the Crystalline Entity - a life form responsible for hundreds of deaths throughout the Alpha Quadrant. However, a scientist on board the Enterprise has plans of revenge over the death of her only son at the hands of the Entity.'),(105,5,5,'Disaster','/bXbc80g0zB49aR752mvZfJZADeo.jpg','70177967','Stardate: 45156.1 - A natural disaster leaves Troi in command of the Enterprise, Picard stuck in a turbo lift with three small children and Keiko O\'Brien stuck in Ten-Forward giving birth with an anxious Worf.'),(106,5,6,'The Game','/99FrwyhdbMsVzVAXVIoqhYBsZu0.jpg','70177968','Stardate: 45208.2 - An addictive game is distributed among the crew of the Enterprise, however, it appears that this game interferes with a person\'s logic and reason, which leaves the crew open to manipulation. Only a young Ensign and a vacationing Wesley Crusher are able to think for themselves, and must find a way to reverse the damage before the ship falls into the wrong hands.'),(107,5,7,'Unification (1)','/waZwpqkqaGUmkS58APzHdELCSob.jpg','70177969','Ambassador Spock has dissapeared and intelligence finds him on Romulus.  Captain Picard is sent to Romulus to find Spock.  Meanwhile Riker and the rest of the crew investigate the fragments of a Vulcan ship discovered in the wreck of a Ferengi vessel.'),(108,5,8,'Unification (2)','/waZwpqkqaGUmkS58APzHdELCSob.jpg','70177970','Stardate: 45245.8 - Picard and Data find Spock and discover the reason behind the secret meetings. However, a darker scheme planned by the Romulans is also uncovered in the process.'),(109,5,9,'A Matter of Time','/86UVSzg7Vo4JrgznlbbI4jkErLC.jpg','70177971','Stardate: 45349.1 - While on a mission to help a planet recently struck by an asteroid, the Enterprise is payed a visit by a man who claims to be from the future.'),(110,5,10,'New Ground','/pBr