identally stumbles over a terrorist group who plan on destroying the ship. He only has a short time to stop their attempts before the ship is swept by a beam of radiation to remove the particles that is lethal to all forms of life.'),(145,6,19,'Lessons','/qO2s0p3kFfaynTArhQuTP4zpBAw.jpg','70178007','Stardate: 46693.1 - Picard must choose between love and command when he must make a decision that could place the woman he loves in a potentially deadly and high-risk mission.'),(146,6,20,'The Chase','/twygxaNEfQFG6YVMypSdg0pauMU.jpg','70178008','Stardate: 46731.5 - Picard\'s old archaeology professor is found murdered, the crew try to complete his research. Soon, the crew must compete with Romulans and Klingons and Cardassians to uncover the truth behind his discoveries.'),(147,6,21,'Frame of Mind','/7w0ad6UMo5NN16coCB59ZrC99Pz.jpg','70178009','Stardate: 46778.1 - Riker questions his sanity when his reality seems to shift between an alien psychiatric hospital and a play he is performing with other members of the crew.'),(148,6,22,'Suspicions','/7zNSGcvfAuaDt0Jk0GXEFui8Scm.jpg','70178010','Stardate: 46830.1 - Dr. Crusher puts her career on the line when she tries to clear the name of a murdered scientist whose invention could allow starships to pass through a sun\'s corona.'),(149,6,23,'Rightful Heir','/7C2okwJL6aPOsFNXavuwe7mncP5.jpg','70178011','Stardate: 46852.2 - While on a quest to summon a vision of Kahless, Worf questions his faith when the real Kahless rises from the dead to lead the Empire.'),(150,6,24,'Second Chances','/8Niq3pN1l5wZGO39HqbpZwaEqzH.jpg','70178012','Stardate: 46915.2 - Riker discovers that eight years ago, an exact clone of him was created when he beamed through a planet\'s surface while returning to his starship. This clone, named Thomas Riker, has secretly remained on the planet for the past eight years, and still has romantic feelings for Troi.'),(151,6,25,'Timescape','/kc0qzC8Zn0oB1pnIOhfkOGoyPEk.jpg','70178013','Stardate: 46944.2 - Picard, G