INSERT INTO `stranger_things` VALUES (1,1,1,'Chapter One: The Vanishing of Will Byers','/AdwF2jXvhdODr6gUZ61bHKRkz09.jpg','80077368','On his way home from a friend\'s house, young Will sees something terrifying. Nearby, a sinister secret lurks in the depths of a government lab.'),(2,1,2,'Chapter Two: The Weirdo on Maple Street','/8iA56ugQyHZmX81wSsNqwXjCE6F.jpg','80077369','Lucas, Mike and Dustin try to talk to the girl they found in the woods. Hopper questions an anxious Joyce about an unsettling phone call.'),(3,1,3,'Chapter Three: Holly, Jolly','/5snULpWQWp7aqFto7UbRcEkEyyS.jpg','80077370','An increasingly concerned Nancy looks for Barb and finds out what Jonathan\'s been up to. Joyce is convinced Will is trying to talk to her.'),(4,1,4,'Chapter Four: The Body','/60wmC1e20HV8gu688GAhsWxqxPx.jpg','80077371','Refusing to believe Will is dead, Joyce tries to connect with her son. The boys give Eleven a makeover. Nancy and Jonathan form an unlikely alliance.'),(5,1,5,'Chapter Five: The Flea and the Acrobat','/exT4NW9EdXG1qLZHKJnRpq3gh1H.jpg','80077372','Hopper breaks into the lab while Nancy and Jonathan confront the force that took Will. The boys ask Mr. Clarke how to travel to another dimension.'),(6,1,6,'Chapter Six: The Monster','/lNS6qycyucewz3duTr1tf1LU688.jpg','80077373','A frantic Jonathan looks for Nancy in the darkness, but Steve\'s looking for her, too. Hopper and Joyce uncover the truth about the lab\'s experiments.'),(7,1,7,'Chapter Seven: The Bathtub','/mkZzUTNWYfGwRH2f1TzlRgouypa.jpg','80077374','Eleven struggles to reach Will, while Lucas warns that \"the bad men are coming.\" Nancy and Jonathan show the police what Jonathan caught on camera.'),(8,1,8,'Chapter Eight: The Upside Down','/1teJ5dbuepfqOOs9uYhYTUjr2qs.jpg','80077375','Dr. Brenner holds Hopper and Joyce for questioning while the boys wait with Eleven in the gym. Back at Will\'s, Nancy and Jonathan prepare for battle.'),(9,2,1,'Chapter One: MADMAX','/5SeMRXWGSkHgd9HXReLJ07MP1w2.jpg','80117716','As the town preps for Halloween, a high-scoring rival shakes things up at the arcade, and a skeptical Hopper inspects a field of rotting pumpkins.'),(10,2,2,'Chapter Two: Trick or Treat, Freak','/3gzPnRilyASmcoSyUKXhaD5ofhr.jpg','80144892','After Will sees something terrible on trick-or-treat night, Mike wonders whether Eleven\'s still out there. Nancy wrestles with the truth about Barb.'),(11,2,3,'Chapter Three: The Pollywog','/792NQjFydcr5ucb1sga55LS6Vt3.jpg','80144893','Dustin adopts a strange new pet, and Eleven grows increasingly impatient. A well-meaning Bob urges Will to stand up to his fears.'),(12,2,4,'Chapter Four: Will the Wise','/b2bkxXuYRZGSP0ckPxRooU7tZKH.jpg','80144894','An ailing Will opens up to Joyce -- with disturbing results. While Hopper digs for the truth, Eleven unearths a surprising discovery.'),(13,2,5,'Chapter Five: Dig Dug','/westZSpDwRPjxG2eBWIT7utDcnL.jpg','80144895','Nancy and Jonathan swap conspiracy theories with a new ally as Eleven searches for someone from her past. “Bob the Brain” tackles a difficult problem.'),(14,2,6,'Chapter Six: The Spy','/y3Npi32SQZ6hGM0LnSQ9ONJyNJY.jpg','80144896','Will\'s connection to a shadowy evil grows stronger, but no one\'s quite sure how to stop it. Elsewhere, Dustin and Steve forge an unlikely bond.'),(15,2,7,'Chapter Seven: The Lost Sister','/kgOaaTbAutwAoA7tkVzYCfTjPXn.jpg','80144897','Psychic visions draw Eleven to a band of violent outcasts and an angry girl with a shadowy past.'),(16,2,8,'Chapter Eight: The Mind Flayer','/vuLea0DA9rYc9Y4M2Ic28CXL4Al.jpg','80144898','An unlikely hero steps forward when a deadly development puts the Hawkins Lab on lockdown, trapping Will and several others inside.'),(17,2,9,'Chapter Nine: The Gate','/cxCf7O5WPHfyXb7PLSJCG6EvXc3.jpg',NULL,'Eleven makes plans to finish what she started while the survivors turn up the heat on the monstrous force that\'s holding Will hostage.');
