INSERT INTO `the_crown` VALUES (1,1,1,'Wolferton Splash','/8JKsglmOt1BDvSs3ZZT30eV4YnN.jpg',NULL,'A young Princess Elizabeth marries Prince Philip. As King George VI’s health worsens, Winston Churchill is elected prime minister for the second time.'),(2,1,2,'Hyde Park Corner','/5HtiL9isJkLsbE4wnZPYIf852lX.jpg',NULL,'With King George too ill to travel, Elizabeth and Philip embark on a four-continent Commonwealth tour. Party leaders attempt to undermine Churchill.'),(3,1,3,'Windsor','/g6AACHbM1JCGs8lUKUJu6aDg34S.jpg',NULL,'With Elizabeth in a new role, Philip tries to assert some power. Churchill wants to delay the coronation. King George’s disgraced brother arrives.'),(4,1,4,'Act of God','/tYwcQoXHZmT5hfmvB3mu8ppt9Fx.jpg',NULL,'When dense smog cripples London for days and creates a serious health hazard, Churchill’s inaction leaves him vulnerable to his political enemies.'),(5,1,5,'Smoke and Mirrors','/rlcURXQqGqGEAZhvL4QNHT1hmwi.jpg',NULL,'Elizabeth rejects protocol by appointing Philip to coordinate her coronation, but his ideas create conflict. The Duke of Windsor returns to London.'),(6,1,6,'Gelignite','/kU4DsZzPpuybnOUuSQzxDwP61od.jpg',NULL,'Margaret and Peter come to Elizabeth with a request. With a royal scandal about to break in the newspapers, the Queen Mother intervenes.'),(7,1,7,'Scientia Potentia Est','/6bM6lLb9xXF2Mo1zySbr5mBF5oq.jpg',NULL,'As the Soviets test the H-bomb, both Churchill and Eden have major health crises. Angry about her inadequate education, Elizabeth hires a tutor.'),(8,1,8,'Pride & Joy','/aj2RFO0K5Sl8oKh6HynpI1Npuew.jpg',NULL,'Elizabeth and Philip go on an exhausting world journey. Margaret takes over some of her sister’s official duties and tries to liven things up.'),(9,1,9,'Assassins','/xldHIJFSrEo3VymDnBHTVPZxdvY.jpg',NULL,'As tensions with Philip increase, Elizabeth spends time with her old friend Porchey. Churchill’s portrait is painted for his 80th birthday.'),(10,1,10,'Gloriana','/t2W1ihcSJIYVTcDtQGg8ecJW5xF.jpg',NULL,'Margaret and Peter are reunited, but another obstacle stands in their way. Elizabeth is torn between her duty as Queen and her love for her sister.'),(11,2,1,'Misadventure','/7p5eCDvzakNIrAZs4Bi7TKUXNT0.jpg',NULL,'As Philip leaves for a long tour, Elizabeth makes an upsetting discovery. Prime Minister Eden wants to strike back after Egypt seizes the Suez Canal.'),(12,2,2,'A Company of Men','/lKaBlcR7aPC8Hjqu0R6nZd8iHF8.jpg',NULL,'Elizabeth feels disconnected from Philip. Eden copes with international pressure and ill health. An interview stirs up harrowing memories for Philip.'),(13,2,3,'Lisbon','/jpGUFzwT17cC31qbF0nasCmUGgH.jpg',NULL,'Palace insiders try to prevent a scandal that could reflect poorly on Philip. Eden faces censure from his cabinet and the press.'),(14,2,4,'Beryl','/fAV15BIYxeJYgXViU09QFhYQYeJ.jpg',NULL,'When Elizabeth and Philip throw a grand party for their 10th anniversary, both Margaret and the new Prime Minister experience romantic tribulations.'),(15,2,5,'Marionettes','/gG6whrFDDZBf3l8wCMBQMLq1TS1.jpg',NULL,'After Elizabeth makes a tone-deaf speech at a Jaguar factory, she and the monarchy come under public attack from an outspoken lord.'),(16,2,6,'Vergangenheit','/pQEYSAMU2zuHuv1VsyAJmoMJ6dY.jpg',NULL,'A secret World War II document opens Elizabeth\'s eyes to grim realities about a family member. The Duke of Windsor campaigns to re-enter public life.'),(17,2,7,'Matrimonium','/PAQrAXEpMx5iniL8DOOkffwN3u.jpg',NULL,'A letter from Peter Townsend spurs Margaret to make a bold proposal. Elizabeth has good news that causes complications for Margaret.'),(18,2,8,'Dear Mrs. Kennedy','/hMly5RjTDmLIXu3mA7zRjdkciUS.jpg',NULL,'Inspired by Jackie Kennedy and against her government\'s wishes, Elizabeth takes an unconventional approach to resolving an issue with Ghana.'),(19,2,9,'Paterfamilias','/2lzNVZ34cSIz514WxwRhOTwqpTC.jpg',NULL,'Philip insists that Prince Charles attend his alma mater in Scotland and reminisces about the life-changing difficulties he experienced there.'),(20,2,10,'Mystery Man','/5dzJtIc3fhNVsjUzUPsoRRaR9dH.jpg',NULL,'A salacious government scandal hits close to home for Elizabeth and Philip. Elizabeth retreats to Scotland for rest during a difficult pregnancy.'),(21,3,1,'Episode 1','/5Iy3NPJw62263LPCmyQQj6BgoTG.jpg',NULL,''),(22,3,2,'Episode 2','/9A89gVpNAqjufndFzqCTvWQ3a91.jpg',NULL,''),(23,3,3,'Episode 3','/lIJOBL95jxVDGzDYdrYnQ8n55Tj.jpg',NULL,''),(24,3,4,'Episode 4','/vhdBTkgncJYbjkDf2vl6korECy9.jpg',NULL,'');
