INSERT INTO `the_ranch` VALUES (1,1,1,'Back Where I Come From','/sK2R5chl9NLjNfpp2e869w3ki9x.jpg',NULL,'When Colt Bennett returns home from Canada to try out for a semipro Denver team, he learns that his family\'s ranch has fallen on hard times.'),(2,1,2,'Some People Change','/r1mB2DQxq90DNJK7EFn7qlTlSnf.jpg',NULL,'Colt runs into an ex at Maggie\'s bar and reminisces with Rooster over a bottle of whiskey. Getting back in Beau\'s good graces is a losing battle.'),(3,1,3,'The Boys of Fall','/1cWkIz1BDkgWvBF0LjFLN1JtHXt.jpg',NULL,'When his inflated ego lands him in hot water, Colt realizes he\'s not the big man on campus anymore. Beau\'s doctor makes him trade in steak for salad.'),(4,1,4,'Got a Little Crazy','/9P0vvxxXYxe5b2ljfvXO81EmGxO.jpg',NULL,'Colt smooths things over with Abby. When Maggie drags Beau to the Marriott for a romantic evening, the guys have some fun back at the house.'),(5,1,5,'American Kids','/18HjDYZlPQZD3cPmNk4TMjOZc7r.jpg',NULL,'Rooster and Colt\'s long-simmering rivalry comes to a head on the first day of hunting season. But their bickering has an upside for Beau and Maggie.'),(6,1,6,'Better as a Memory','/sV51qiqG1YaYgfOCi7SzlZShlfy.jpg',NULL,'Abby gets a taste of her own medicine after a hazy night of drinking. Beau warms to the idea of mending fences with Maggie.'),(7,1,7,'I Can\'t Go There','/lAdEhqzFMklbYvM8aohn5ESxXQq.jpg',NULL,'Colt figures out what he wants from Heather. A sick calf gives Beau an excuse to avoid dealing with his feelings -- and creates some unexpected bonds.'),(8,1,8,'Til It\'s Gone','/szBdAU9wkOCxgN7qN0FWudWPxhY.jpg',NULL,'The ranch\'s dwindling finances drive a wedge between Beau and the boys, and Colt goes behind his father\'s back to ask Maggie for help.'),(9,1,9,'There Goes My Life','/djWMKBXOulYi7vqeaLG6WtsLTYX.jpg',NULL,'Heather sets up Rooster with her sister, but Colt\'s afraid he\'ll ruin a good thing. Maggie and Beau air their dirty laundry at marriage counseling.'),(10,1,10,'Down the Road','/eqtv6qQkJIoacXij8vXx5KAsqDm.jpg',NULL,'Colt and Rooster worry when Beau has a change of heart about the calves. But that\'s just the beginning of the surprises that await the Bennett clan.'),(11,1,11,'Gone as a Girl Can Get','/lxTJr2HZGTLGetiYaszophIRe2I.jpg',NULL,'An angry Beau clears Maggie\'s things out of the house. Colt tries to sort out his feelings for Abby and Heather.'),(12,1,12,'Living and Living Well','/uB97jlfS9nIwqlzAd6z9w4wS8NZ.jpg',NULL,'Colt struggles to keep his relationship with Abby under wraps. The boys make a big purchase and try to sell Beau on a business opportunity.'),(13,1,13,'Sittin\' on the Fence','/jHsprJbhvulGTZHzJ1klPsiTpUy.jpg',NULL,'Beau\'s depressed over Maggie, so Mary tries to fix him up with a friend. Colt wonders when Abby\'s going to follow through on her promise.'),(14,1,14,'Let\'s Fall to Pieces Together','/yVGwAIh2fnNBiSzBKYWp1pVNhpD.jpg',NULL,'While Rooster tries to broker peace between Beau and Maggie, Colt apologizes to Heather -- but his timing couldn\'t be worse.'),(15,1,15,'I Know She Still Loves Me','/eio7EFsS7oV5fW00QJWkwFfBRFo.jpg',NULL,'Beau and Maggie come to a decision about their relationship, but they don\'t see eye to eye about the ranch. The boys take Kenny out drinking.'),(16,1,16,'Easy Come, Easy Go','/8cf0bhhKU3hohg0jwKbObuBz0DH.jpg',NULL,'Rooster and Colt try to prove themselves to Beau, but he doesn\'t have much faith in them. Colt gets jealous when he sees Abby and Kenny together.'),(17,1,17,'I\'ve Come to Expect It from You','/nACTWRth9dr9oAKqxjqGVbSX89k.jpg',NULL,'Colt plans a special date with Abby. Rooster vents his frustrations to Maggie, while Joanne gives Beau some sage advice.'),(18,1,18,'The Cowboy Rides Away','/uH34nb52pPJbySP9pC3NIGneAO1.jpg',NULL,'Beau tries to make amends with the boys, but it may be too little, too late. A job offer drives a wedge between Rooster and Colt.'),(19,1,19,'Leavin\'s Been Comin\' (For a Long, Long Time)','/3C8OViho9qUyAOYvm9mCiqY6y9B.jpg',NULL,'Maggie stands up for Rooster when Beau kicks him out of the house. Meanwhile, Colt is torn between his brother and his father.'),(20,1,20,'Merry Christmas (Wherever You Are)','/vbPwbfXBW4Bv5xju3hSMnMyGjUt.jpg',NULL,'Colt realizes what he wants for his future, Beau and Maggie find some closure, and the gang celebrates Christmas at the bar.'),(21,2,1,'My Next Thirty Years','/8VYQzbJXyj3JDc6SSOpnjtNrNTX.jpg',NULL,'After Heather drops a bombshell, a visit from Abby\'s parents is the last thing Colt needs -- and they all end up at church together on Christmas Eve.'),(22,2,2,'Things Change','/f7EiPY8vJhFRQ21vJd2xcpqLm0p.jpg',NULL,'Heather makes a decision about the pregnancy. Mary reads Rooster the riot act for keeping it a secret, and Colt struggles with how to tell Abby.'),(23,2,3,'Take Me Away from Here','/edi5UPtiokkPevOWf78RwUTbyVV.jpg',NULL,'After a heart-to-heart with Maggie, Colt steps up and supports Heather. Meanwhile, the tension between Rooster and Beau takes a toll on Maggie.'),(24,2,4,'She\'ll Have You Back','/oIZQyaLPVErn6Riv8mvgeRbXaXt.jpg',NULL,'Abby agrees to give Colt a chance, but her father isn\'t as forgiving. Beau and Rooster go to a cattle auction. Maggie thinks about selling the bar.'),(25,2,5,'My Best Friend','/uyxMwsXCQYRmd4g6CrlSH2TRjMH.jpg',NULL,'The guys wind up in hot water after an ice fishing trip. Beau takes Brenda out to dinner, but Maggie\'s not far from his mind.'),(26,2,6,'Find Out Who Your Friends Are','/1AbKv9sTuuJ2URER4Y4viuHfV24.jpg',NULL,'Emotions run high when Abby and Heather fight, leaving Colt caught in the middle. Rooster faces the consequences of blowing off work.'),(27,2,7,'One of Those Nights','/kzxYfOJXQNJjAz1AvKvklfBKXvU.jpg',NULL,'During a snowstorm, Colt and Abby head out of town, Beau and Joanne get cozy at the ranch, and Maggie meets a charming stranger.'),(28,2,8,'I Didn\'t Ask and She Didn\'t Say','/pfww4Qm3Xfr8NIJwCsl3Gf4fa89.jpg',NULL,'Colt gets possessive when Heather starts dating a teacher. Abby gives Beau relationship advice. Maggie has a business proposition for Rooster'),(29,2,9,'Last Dollar (Fly Away)','/2hvwWkOn0AS4KMdeD20QoNlNRBU.jpg',NULL,'As Heather\'s medical bills roll in, Colt realizes how expensive it is having a baby. A surprise visitor at the bar sweeps Maggie off her feet.'),(30,2,10,'Can\'t Be Really Gone','/iHW4Yl1qQHDIXBrg5HPk17Gb1X8.jpg',NULL,'Colt\'s new responsibilities keep him away from Abby. After a memorable night, Maggie ponders what she wants for her future.'),(31,2,11,'Learning to Live Again','/wXbwWq0gU8ZpHzVhkS3Qz2pES3u.jpg',NULL,'Colt wants to buy Sam Peterson\'s ranch -- with or without his family\'s blessing. Colt and Heather have a heart-to-heart about their loss.'),(32,2,12,'Wrapped Up in You','/bdlQOdlzcW1P70rOa2nBDXqmrRS.jpg',NULL,'Wondering if he\'s ready to marry Abby, Colt seeks romantic advice from an unlikely source: Beau. Rooster hires a flaky new waitress.'),(33,2,13,'Rodeo and Juliet','/4S2IbJGa1pY7CxFXILDv2pZx9o7.jpg',NULL,'Beau ponders a lucrative business offer. Rooster runs afoul of the liquor board. Colt tries to make peace with Abby\'s dad.'),(34,2,14,'Much Too Young (To Feel This Damn Old)','/hqK4EYdkWTtHTl0xEbbHJp2LAta.jpg',NULL,'Colt and Abby start planning their wedding, but they don\'t see eye to eye. Joanne confesses she still has feelings for Beau.'),(35,2,15,'More Than a Memory','/pvVKEVuVPwd6659VUB8SfbxAE9j.jpg',NULL,'Abby moves in with Colt and Beau when she learns she’s losing her job. Rooster and Jen the engineer bond over getting dumped.'),(36,2,16,'When You Come Back to Me Again','/anpkpoaBGgv8n2urjjYiKGReemc.jpg',NULL,'Back in town, Maggie frets about how Rooster\'s been running the bar. Abby considers a career change.'),(37,2,17,'Do What You Gotta Do','/u85RBkKlmYsZOEdKUDr4KZkamDt.jpg',NULL,'A job opportunity in Denver threatens to drive a wedge between Colt and Abby. Maggie pushes back about the pipeline.'),(38,2,18,'Big Money','/yT3nsrx4ki2HKXHRcB8OoovEI5z.jpg',NULL,'Maggie takes a stand that lands her in hot water. Colt and Rooster come up with a plan to buy the Peterson ranch, but they need Beau\'s buy-in.'),(39,2,19,'Ain\'t Goin\' Down (\'Til the Sun Comes Up)','/yYGiIvioE2jKqkPvfwA106Kv7IF.jpg',NULL,'Beau shrugs off the doctor\'s orders and resists the family\'s efforts to help him. Meanwhile, Colt lashes out at Maggie.'),(40,2,20,'If Tomorrow Never Comes','/j6vDwR3TvzejdQTnrqXdEvVGZCj.jpg',NULL,'Beau leaves the boys hanging about the Peterson ranch. Rooster takes Jen on a date. Colt and Abby fight about their future.'),(41,3,1,'Starting Over Again','/fyephsQiaT9hImbWMnIMhNBs3s.jpg',NULL,'In the wake of his heart attack, Beau vows to stop sweating the small stuff -- but Colt and Rooster\'s latest blunder makes him lose his cool.'),(42,3,2,'It\'s All Wrong, But It\'s All Right','/n2DgybruSuZifPa8zVhHUt4VvYZ.jpg',NULL,'Maggie fights to keep the ranch afloat as she reaches a breaking point with the boys. Easter dinner with Abby\'s parents takes a surprising turn.'),(43,3,3,'A Gamble Either Way','/ytYcxOhKYoQcb6mFCxDe1Br0M4t.jpg',NULL,'Torn between the ranch and a job opportunity, Colt wonders what\'s best for his family\'s future. Mary offers to work at Maggie\'s bar.'),(44,3,4,'Baby I\'m Burning','/zU5Csp69gyAmqvkOT39xJZDePqi.jpg',NULL,'Four months later, wildfires rage in Colorado. Abby wants to postpone the wedding, but her parents don\'t approve. Joanne stands up to a stubborn Beau.'),(45,3,5,'Travelin\' Prayer','/jwv72qWbGsoDg7jUUIakRLgCon9.jpg',NULL,'Fires force the town to evacuate. While Maggie takes charge, Beau feels hopeless. Colt runs into Heather, and Rooster meets Mary\'s boyfriend, Nick.'),(46,3,6,'Tie Our Love (In a Double Knot)','/glALcLTKanooB7ORWVTNClQuBJX.jpg',NULL,'Colt and Mr. Phillips search for Abby. Heather warns Rooster about Nick. An unexpected celebration brings everyone together.'),(47,3,7,'Telling Me Lies','/38GVJo1SNEleVrgD3O9OVZRgzX1.jpg',NULL,'The Bennetts return to the ranch. Beau gets a business proposition from Neumann\'s Hill. A face from Maggie\'s past arrives with news.'),(48,3,8,'Fresh Out of Forgiveness','/zq7M2Cm1u5Ive5QBtoW8ofC8e1d.jpg',NULL,'When Colt lands in trouble covering for Rooster, he tries to cash in a favor. Beau invites Joanne to stay at the ranch. Colt plans a surprise for Abby.'),(49,3,9,'It Ain\'t Fair that It Ain\'t Right','/8ShVIjLEI0ptKKPZUm25NGckfIU.jpg',NULL,'Beau\'s at the end of his rope and decides to teach Colt and Rooster a lesson. Mary realizes she needs to choose between Rooster and Nick.'),(50,3,10,'Change','/dlWGhTVEn4hZG15iVZgqiaHxo5L.jpg',NULL,'Nick confronts Rooster. Running out of options, Colt reaches out to Lisa Neumann. Joanne urges Beau to make peace with Colt.');
