INSERT INTO `trailer_park_boys` VALUES (1,1,1,'Take Your Little Gun and Get Out of My Trailer Park','/71swC4M8cnSVCRvmgeQU8Li26kL.jpg',NULL,'After 18 months in jail, our Trailer Park Boys, Ricky and Julian , head back home to Sunnyvale Trailer Park aiming to get their lives back together again. The problem is that neither Ricky\'s fiancee Lucy nor his dad Ray will let him back into their homes, and some guy named Cyrus has moved into Julian\'s trailer, having crowned himself the new \"King of the Park.\"'),(2,1,2,'Fuck Community College, Let\'s Get Drunk and Eat Chicken Fingers','/pX527p1ttaBooxb2u2gLYrInV2W.jpg',NULL,'Fed up with all their demands and complaints, Julian tells everyone that he is leaving the trailer park. Ricky, who has been living in Julian\'s car on his front lawn, has one week to find a new place to live. Mr. Lahey, the trailer park supervisor, is thrilled to hear of Julian\'s imminent departure but when he hears that Ricky won\'t be leaving too, his worst nightmare seems about to come true.'),(3,1,3,'Mr. Lahey\'s Got My Porno Tape!','/n2Lvt8bw1oypsrUObDjHlk63yeK.jpg',NULL,'In desperate need of $2,000 to buy some hydroponics gear for his dope-growing business, Ricky reluctantly agrees to star in one of J-Rock\'s amateur porn films to be shot in J-Rock\'s trailer. Ricky, however, isn\'t quite up to the task, and the video, entitled \"From Russia With The Love Bone\", eventually winds up in Mr. Lahey\'s possession. Julian must convince Lahey that using the tape against Ricky would not be in Lahey\'s best interest.'),(4,1,4,'Mrs. Peterson\'s Dog Gets Fucked Up','/iqGZEHID3wpDuTZ6bjIXAfXqJ2w.jpg',NULL,'While babysitting both Trinity and Mrs. Peterson\'s dog, Ricky accidentally gets shot and the dog devours a tray of hash brownies. A vet treats both the dog and Ricky. In order to pay the vet, Ricky and Julian must repossess a lawn tractor owned by a former patient who hasn\'t paid the vet\'s bill. The Boys successfully recover the tractor -- but not before Ricky gets shot for the second time that day.'),(5,1,5,'I\'m Not Gay, I Love Lucy... Wait a Second, Maybe I am Gay','/AcC7OIDlZQKbJ5uUSoeBOL6VSQp.jpg',NULL,'With Ricky\'s life still a mess, Julian tries to convince him that it\'s time to marry Lucy. Reluctant at first, Ricky changes his mind when Julian suggests that people will always think that Ricky is gay unless he marries Lucy. Julian\'s engagement present to Ricky is the \'76 New Yorker, which for weeks was up on blocks in his front yard, and is now made operational thanks to a few purloined replacement parts.'),(6,1,6,'Who the Hell Invited These Idiots to My Wedding?','/mZWPOlGdyPu6Z0yOlfGHRyCAyzi.jpg',NULL,'Lucy insists that Julian take over the job of organizing her wedding: which is odd since Julian isn\'t the groom, Ricky is. She wants lots of people and lots of food. The people part will be easy but getting that much food will be difficult on a tight budget. Julian\'s plan to hit a local grocery store runs into a snag when Ricky unexpectedly shows up in the middle of the heist. Shots are fired. The next day, the cops show up uninvited to the wedding.'),(7,2,1,'What in the Fuck Happened to Our Trailer Park?','/677q8DZWoqak3fjMxNQG5N7Q29T.jpg',NULL,'When Ricky gets a job as a mall security guard, he puts Julian\'s dope-growing operation at risk and tries to arrest Bubbles for stealing shopping carts.'),(8,2,2,'Jim Lahey Is a Drunk Bastard','/zhyDwWoD4sxvgSRoAyBijGQPwp2.jpg',NULL,'Julian and Ricky have to make sure that Jim Lahey wins the election for trailer park supervisor over their archrival Sam Losco.'),(9,2,3,'I\'ve Met Cats and Dogs Smarter Than Trevor and Cory','/91TqdnHNMVWWPN6GsR8apxuDoEm.jpg',NULL,'Needing extra cash to expand their dope operation, Julian and Ricky open a bar and casino in J-ROC\'s trailer.'),(10,2,4,'A Dope Trailer Is No Place for a Kitty','/fjDPrPQedVXQM4LYZGRZxxmRuru.jpg',NULL,'When their dope plants become infested with insects, Ricky and Julian quarantine the surviving crop in Bubbles\' shed, leading to a fiery conclusion.'),(11,2,5,'The Bible Pimp','/5iOhmgoekbSnreRnN1fDocOEwzp.jpg',NULL,'Ricky\'s worst suspicions are realized when Julian falls for the daughter of a traveling Bible Salesman.'),(12,2,6,'Never Trust a Man with No Shirt On','/sA8kI6O4zccJfO6QZFnMyBIqdtX.jpg',NULL,'After a big blowout with his boss, Randy quits his job and joins Julian and Ricky in their life of crime.'),(13,2,7,'The Bare Pimp Project','/pAguWPcR9fRzPlgXG4M8xkXvnP6.jpg',NULL,'With their dope-filled Airstream trailer in tow, Julian, Ricky and Bubbles lead a convoy of police cars in a long chase through the countryside as a police helicopter circles overhead.'),(14,3,1,'The Kiss of Freedom','/r3zhueM2Iqv0Ui8wKRFzJegFxxC.jpg',NULL,'Ricky and Julian get out of prison rich men but Ricky kisses it all away in the end.'),(15,3,2,'Temporary Relief Assistant Trailer Park Supervisor','/zvg86Cp0yWMh9NdPC3xFrU2Drzn.jpg',NULL,'Ricky\'s job as Temporary Relief Assistant Trailer Park Supervisor threatens to blow the cover on Julian\'s bootleg vodka operation.'),(16,3,3,'If I Can\'t Smoke and Swear, I\'m Fucked','/5UY6SPi4Pervcz9mS6z9HV5I7dq.jpg',NULL,'Ricky defends himself, Julian and Bubbles in court on charges of operating an illegal gas station'),(17,3,4,'Who\'s the Microphone Assassin?','/ux3vgCZBEgIkgsGe4om5EE7UWhO.jpg',NULL,'Caught jacking more than just tunes, J-ROC tries to redeem himself by MC\'ing a rap concert in the park.'),(18,3,5,'Closer to the Heart','/j7mTEheflSW2Jt5SpbwlVc07L6w.jpg',NULL,'Bubbles is so devastated about not getting tickets to the RUSH concert that Ricky decides to bring Alex Lifeson (Alex Lifeson) to the park to perform a private concert.'),(19,3,6,'Where the Fuck is Randy\'s Barbeque?','/d45qNK02AfbAc1SygkoKzqBvGQa.jpg',NULL,'Julian comes up with a plan to \"\"remarket\"\" barbeques.  Ricky thinks it\'s a good idea to get his daughter, Trinity, and her friends in the Junior Achievers\' Program to steal the barbeques since they are minors and won\'t go to jail.'),(20,3,7,'The Delusions of Officer Jim Lahey','/cX1qd8RUEk79i8nlx6gwrfTg5Pd.jpg',NULL,'Lahey looses his mind on the anniversary of his dismissal from the police force.  He puts on his old police uniform and tells everyone in the park that he is a police officer again.  He shoots at Ricky and ultimately imprisons Ricky and Julian in a homemade shed-jail.'),(21,3,8,'A Shit Leopard Can\'t Change Its Spots','/tcC5VcAs4q3QjuMhxZfqQFKTa82.jpg',NULL,'Ricky gets pissed off at Julian for inviting Officer Erica Miller on the cruise.'),(22,4,1,'Never Cry Shitwolf','/jbFhnfoGSpATt7JiIWzY3tFisOA.jpg',NULL,'Julian gets out of jail only to discover that Ricky is the new supervisor of Sunnyvale Trailer Park. Ricky and his assistant, Bubbles, have been carrying out various illegal activities.'),(23,4,2,'Man\'s Gotta Eat','/AmZ6b64FDRvbBuhMC8lHFG5SANN.jpg',NULL,'Broke, trailerless and without rum, Julian decides to leave the park and ends up living in his car in an alley. Meanwhile, Randy will do anything for a store-bought cheeseburger.'),(24,4,3,'Rub \'N Tiz\'zug','/8QipXRnFMulmoVIODLuSKMKsqXS.jpg',NULL,'Julian, Ricky and Bubbles open a massage parlour in the park. J-Roc and DVS (Detroit Velvet Smooth) attempt to get J-Roc arrested to increase his \"\"street cred.\"\"'),(25,4,4,'The Green Bastard','/ztNRABqqxlxMNSSOcl6WPrbyt3D.jpg',NULL,'On a family fun day in the Park, Mr. Lahey plans to get his old supervisor job from Ricky. Bubbles wrestles under the alias, \"\"The Green Bastard\"\".'),(26,4,5,'Conky','/hPCk2KsfKeNkIBIBjVdYDgRXB4y.jpg',NULL,'Bubbles has an infected tooth and the only way to get him to a hospital is with the help of his old childhood friend: a ventriloquist doll named Conky.'),(27,4,6,'If You Love Something, Set It Free','/zJtRHP7ulE6umPQbq0lRvx1QQ6S.jpg',NULL,'Bubbles befriends a dope-addicted mountain lion that has been eating weed from the Boys\' marijuana fields..'),(28,4,7,'Propane, Propane (1)','/dFOfMsOLDZDg08NeCU0kazDsFrF.jpg',NULL,'The Boys are finally ready to harvest and sell their dope. Barb proposes to Ricky. Mr. Lahey goes off the deep end.'),(29,4,8,'Workin\' Man (2)','/bpj8AzdlW0Sne0klZuWvKZjr3L4.jpg',NULL,'The Trailer Park Boys race to harvest their dope field while Jim Lahey slowly goes crazy.'),(30,5,1,'Give Peace a Chance','/ukJNH3fbxP8AooTjd4dVModse7.jpg',NULL,'The boys get out of jail only to find that Cory and Trevor messed up againâ€”they don\'t own the park after all. Ray is hooked on VLTs.'),(31,5,2,'The Shit Puppets','/41U2Sy6kuqDNaXueQnttveqfnc7.jpg',NULL,'Cory and Trevor start to work for Julian. The boys steal drugs from Cyrus and hatch a plan to hide it all until they can find a buyer.'),(32,5,3,'The Fuckin\' Way She Goes','/k8FnVoYyv718BgQqjmgvFqcQJIY.jpg',NULL,'The boys hide all of the hash by using it to pave Ray\'s driveway. Ray\'s addiction to gambling and liquor gets worse. Ricky barbecues for his family with devastating effects.'),(33,5,4,'You Got To Blame The Thing Up Here','/5gTgeOtpM9htzCwPqA0H9e2bxx0.jpg',NULL,'The boys find ways to help Ray now that his trailer has burned down. Bubbles realizes that the fire was not his fault.'),(34,5,5,'Jim Lahey Is A Fuckin\' Drunk And He Always Will Be','/7bayzjHDVodaw99uFlufFPzM3Fw.jpg',NULL,'Bubbles pretends to be a spaceman when the boys buy a rocket set. Ray reveals Lahey\'s secret and Lahey goes off the deep end.'),(35,5,6,'Don\'t Cross the Shit Line','/uBM9C3PRWiyH9FDiryf3ihCfxoI.jpg',NULL,'The boys star in another one of J-Roc\'s greasy porn films. Randy and Lahey manage to get Ray arrested for disability fraud.'),(36,5,7,'The Winds of Shit','/y2NvXFlUyp0hrzLjxvGtZKRbyAP.jpg',NULL,'Julian devises a clever plan to sell part of their driveway in order to earn extra cash. Ricky gets a job as a janitor at a local vocational school.'),(37,5,8,'Dressed All Over & Zesty Mordant','/h5eavxOY9RdPCiYCkjKn2J3e2ya.jpg',NULL,'Julian\'s biggest money-making scheme yet involves smuggling drugs in shopping carts. Ricky lets